quot;\">\r\n			<div class=\"a-fixed-left-grid-col a-col-left\" style=\"margin:0px 0px 0px -100px;padding:0px;\">\r\n				<span class=\"a-text-bold\" style=\"font-weight:700 !important;\">Answer:</span> \r\n			</div>\r\n			<div class=\"a-fixed-left-grid-col a-col-right\" style=\"margin:0px;padding:0px;\">\r\n				<span>Yes, ours is. The solar unit powers a small battery pack which has its own stand, a stake for the ground and a slot to attach it.<br />\r\nJay</span>&nbsp;<br />\r\n<span class=\"a-color-tertiary\" style=\"color:#767676 !important;\">By Jay Fluck on November 17, 2015</span><span class=\"askInlineAnswers\" id=\"Tx1RES7WTLUKQR3\"> \r\n				<div id=\"askInlineAnswersPage-Tx1RES7WTLUKQR3-1\" class=\"a-section a-spacing-none\" style=\"margin:0px;padding:0px;\">\r\n					<div class=\"a-section a-spacing-none a-spacing-top-small\" style=\"margin:0px;padding:0px;\">\r\n						<span>Supposed to be. Yes</span>&nbsp;<br />\r\n<span class=\"a-color-tertiary\" style=\"color:#767676 !important;\">By Jay Fluck on November 18, 2015</span> \r\n					</div>\r\n				</div>\r\n</span> \r\n			</div>\r\n		</div>\r\n	</div>\r\n	<div id=\"question-Tx1X53JCIJQTJHA\" class=\"a-fixed-left-grid a-spacing-small\" style=\"margin:0px;padding:0px;font-size:13.3333px;\">\r\n		<div class=\"a-fixed-left-grid-inner\" style=\"margin:0px;padding:0px 0px 0px 100px;font-family:HelveticaNeue, &quot;\">\r\n			<div class=\"a-fixed-left-grid-col a-col-left\" style=\"margin:0px 0px 0px -100px;padding:0px;\">\r\n				<span class=\"a-text-bold\" style=\"font-weight:700 !important;\">Question:</span> \r\n			</div>\r\n			<div class=\"a-fixed-left-grid-col a-col-right\" style=\"margin:0px;padding:0px;\">\r\n				How large are the flowers?\r\n			</div>\r\n		</div>\r\n	</div>\r\n	<div class=\"a-fixed-left-grid a-spacing-base\" style=\"margin:0px;padding:0px;font-size:13.3333px;\">\r\n		<div class=\"a-fixed-left-grid-inner\" style=\"margin:0px;padding:0px 0px 0px 100px;font-family:HelveticaNeue, &quot;\">\r\n			<div class=\"a-fixed-left-grid-col a-col-left\" style=\"margin:0px 0px 0px -100px;padding:0px;\">\r\n				<span class=\"a-text-bold\" style=\"font-weight:700 !important;\">Answer:</span> \r\n			</div>\r\n			<div class=\"a-fixed-left-grid-col a-col-right\" style=\"margin:0px;padding:0px;\">\r\n				<span>About the size of a quarter.</span>&nbsp;<br />\r\n<span class=\"a-color-tertiary\" style=\"color:#767676 !important;\">By Marc Morency on March 8, 2017</span><span class=\"askInlineAnswers\" id=\"Tx1X53JCIJQTJHA\"> \r\n				<div id=\"askInlineAnswersPage-Tx1X53JCIJQTJHA-1\" class=\"a-section a-spacing-none\" style=\"margin:0px;padding:0px;\">\r\n					<div class=\"a-section a-spacing-none a-spacing-top-small\" style=\"margin:0px;padding:0px;\">\r\n						<span>They are on the small side, I\'d say less than an inch diameter. Also, mine only worked twice, and I waited too long to return them.</span>&nbsp;<br />\r\n<span class=\"a-color-tertiary\" style=\"color:#767676 !important;\">By Alicia Davis on March 9, 2017</span> \r\n					</div>\r\n					<div class=\"a-section a-spacing-none a-spacing-top-small\" style=\"margin:0px;padding:0px;\">\r\n						<span>1.5 inch diameter</span>&nbsp;<br />\r\n<span class=\"a-color-tertiary\" style=\"color:#767676 !important;\">By maoyuma on March 7, 2017</span> \r\n					</div>\r\n				</div>\r\n				<div id=\"askInlineAnswersPage-Tx1X53JCIJQTJHA-2\" class=\"a-section a-spacing-none\" style=\"margin:0px;padding:0px;\">\r\n					<div class=\"a-section a-spacing-none a-spacing-top-small\" style=\"margin:0px;padding:0px;\">\r\n						<span>I haven\'t measured them but they look to be about an inch in diameter. Hope that helped.</span>&nbsp;<br />\r\n<span class=\"a-color-tertiary\" style=\"color:#767676 !important;\">By Susan K. Davis on March 7, 2017</span> \r\n					</div>\r\n					<div class=\"a-section a-spacing-none a-spacing-top-small\" style=\"margin:0px;padding:0px;\">\r\n						<span>The flowers are about 3/4 of an inch in diameter.</span>&nbs