"color:#767676 !important;\">By Wally on December 10, 2016</span> \r\n					</div>\r\n					<div class=\"a-section a-spacing-none a-spacing-top-small\" style=\"margin:0px;padding:0px;\">\r\n						<span>It isn\'t on box it has a six hour timer automatic.</span>&nbsp;<br />\r\n<span class=\"a-color-tertiary\" style=\"color:#767676 !important;\">By Sharon Renee Gray on December 10, 2016</span> \r\n					</div>\r\n				</div>\r\n</span> \r\n			</div>\r\n		</div>\r\n	</div>\r\n	<div id=\"question-Tx2TLROOHKWQQG8\" class=\"a-fixed-left-grid a-spacing-small\" style=\"margin:0px;padding:0px;font-size:13.3333px;\">\r\n		<div class=\"a-fixed-left-grid-inner\" style=\"margin:0px;padding:0px 0px 0px 100px;font-family:HelveticaNeue, &quot;\">\r\n			<div class=\"a-fixed-left-grid-col a-col-left\" style=\"margin:0px 0px 0px -100px;padding:0px;\">\r\n				<span class=\"a-text-bold\" style=\"font-weight:700 !important;\">Question:</span> \r\n			</div>\r\n			<div class=\"a-fixed-left-grid-col a-col-right\" style=\"margin:0px;padding:0px;\">\r\n				Can you program lights when to go on for 6 Hours\r\n			</div>\r\n		</div>\r\n	</div>\r\n	<div class=\"a-fixed-left-grid a-spacing-base\" style=\"margin:0px;padding:0px;font-size:13.3333px;\">\r\n		<div class=\"a-fixed-left-grid-inner\" style=\"margin:0px;padding:0px 0px 0px 100px;font-family:HelveticaNeue, &quot;\">\r\n			<div class=\"a-fixed-left-grid-col a-col-left\" style=\"margin:0px 0px 0px -100px;padding:0px;\">\r\n				<span class=\"a-text-bold\" style=\"font-weight:700 !important;\">Answer:</span> \r\n			</div>\r\n			<div class=\"a-fixed-left-grid-col a-col-right\" style=\"margin:0px;padding:0px;\">\r\n				<span>yes, you can do that</span>&nbsp;<br />\r\n<span class=\"a-color-tertiary\" style=\"color:#767676 !important;\">By Alfonso Pena on December 8, 2016</span><span class=\"askInlineAnswers\" id=\"Tx2TLROOHKWQQG8\"> \r\n				<div id=\"askInlineAnswersPage-Tx2TLROOHKWQQG8-1\" class=\"a-section a-spacing-none\" style=\"margin:0px;padding: