 a-spacing-top-small\" style=\"margin:0px;padding:0px;\">\r\n						<span>No, but they have the obligatory blinking lights and then the light show begins. I keep my all blue balcony lights on \"strobe\" And then my window lights on a crazy blinking mode. You can go up and down the settings to see which one you like.</span>&nbsp;<br />\r\n<span class=\"a-color-tertiary\" style=\"color:#767676 !important;\">By CMAC on February 11, 2017</span> \r\n					</div>\r\n					<div class=\"a-section a-spacing-none a-spacing-top-small\" style=\"margin:0px;padding:0px;\">\r\n						<span>Yes. I believe they call it chasing mode on this string of lights.</span>&nbsp;<br />\r\n<span class=\"a-color-tertiary\" style=\"color:#767676 !important;\">By Amazon Customer on February 11, 2017</span> \r\n					</div>\r\n				</div>\r\n</span> \r\n			</div>\r\n		</div>\r\n	</div>\r\n	<div id=\"question-Tx2WWLDCWPP5VIY\" class=\"a-fixed-left-grid a-spacing-small\" style=\"margin:0px;padding:0px;font-size:13.3333px;\">\r\n		<div class=\"a-fixed-left-grid-inner\" style=\"margin:0px;padding:0px 0px 0px 100px;font-family:HelveticaNeue, &quot;\">\r\n			<div class=\"a-fixed-left-grid-col a-col-left\" style=\"margin:0px 0px 0px -100px;padding:0px;\">\r\n				<span class=\"a-text-bold\" style=\"font-weight:700 !important;\">Question:</span> \r\n			</div>\r\n			<div class=\"a-fixed-left-grid-col a-col-right\" style=\"margin:0px;padding:0px;\">\r\n				can these be steady on without the timer turning them off?\r\n			</div>\r\n		</div>\r\n	</div>\r\n	<div class=\"a-fixed-left-grid a-spacing-base\" style=\"margin:0px;padding:0px;font-size:13.3333px;\">\r\n		<div class=\"a-fixed-left-grid-inner\" style=\"margin:0px;padding:0px 0px 0px 100px;font-family:HelveticaNeue, &quot;\">\r\n			<div class=\"a-fixed-left-grid-col a-col-left\" style=\"margin:0px 0px 0px -100px;padding:0px;\">\r\n				<span class=\"a-text-bold\" style=\"font-weight:700 !important;\">Answer:</span> \r\n			</div>\r\n			<div class=\"a-fixed-left-grid-col a-col-right\" style=\"margin:0px;padding:0px;\">\r\n				<span>YES eight settings, steady on is one of them</span>&nbsp;<br />\r\n<span class=\"a-color-tertiary\" style=\"color:#767676 !important;\">By J. Brandfas on December 7, 2016</span> \r\n			</div>\r\n		</div>\r\n	</div>\r\n</div>', '200 LED 8 Modes Purple Fairy Lights with Timer,Glowing Starry String Lights,Battery   Operated，8 Working Modes, 50ft Cable Length - Qedertek', 'glowing starry string lights,small lights for decoration,battery xmas lights for sale,purple fairy lights, battery powered 200 LED fairy lights', 'Search for glowing starry fairy light, you are just right here, our purple 200 LED starry fairy lights, battery powered, 8 lighting modes optional, widely use for your home, garden, window, gazebo, deck railing dance hall, stage etc.', 'https://www.amazon.com/dp/B01HHODL3Y/', '', '0', '0.00', 'http://images.qedertek.com/593531ec6fade', '{\"593531ec9a455\":\"http:\\/\\/images.qedertek.com\\/593531ec9a455\",\"593531ecb6d67\":\"http:\\/\\/images.qedertek.com\\/593531ecb6d67\",\"593531ecd732d\":\"http:\\/\\/images.qedertek.com\\/593531ecd732d\",\"593531ed0426b\":\"http:\\/\\/images.qedertek.com\\/593531ed0426b\",\"593531ed2204f\":\"http:\\/\\/images.qedertek.com\\/593531ed2204f\"}', '0', '1', '0', '0.00', '1', '1491465925', '1496658413', '', '0');
INSERT INTO `qe_product` VALUES ('25', '4', 'Battery Powered Fairy String Lights 200 LED Cool White with Timer', '<div class=\"disclaim\" style=\"font-size:small;color:#888888;margin:0px 0px 1em;font-family:verdana, arial, helvetica, sans-serif;background-color:#FFFFFF;\">\r\n	Color Name:<span style=\"font-weight:700;\">Cool White</span> \r\n</div>\r\n<p style=\"margin-left:1em;color:#333333;font-family:Arial, sans-serif;font-size:small;background-color:#FFFFFF;\">\r\n	<span style=\"font-weight:700;\">Battery Powered String Lights</span>&nbsp;<br />\r\nNew LED string lights powered by 3D batteries (not included), no power cord or socket required, you can decorate anywhere especially some places without power supply&nbsp;<br />\r\n<span style=\"font-weight:700;\">Multi Modes Enrich Your Life</span>&nbsp;<br />\r\n8 Lighting Modes Optional: Combination, Waves, Sequential, Slo-Glo, Chasing/Flash, Slow fade, Twinkle/Flash, Steady on. Switch the mode button to convert between these 8 kinds modes, no visual fatigue, no dull any more&nbsp;<br />\r\n<span style=\"font-weight:700;\">Automatic Timer Function</span>&nbsp;<br />\r\nThe lights have been pre-programmed with timing sequence, auto cycle of 6 hours on and then 18 hours off everyday, no need of manual operation, super convenient.&nbsp;<br />\r\n<span style=\"font-weight:700;\">Endless Application</span>&nbsp;<br />\r\nPlacement options have no limitation. those mini led lights will create a starry fairy scene for your home, garden, window, gazebo, deck railing, stairs, wedding, Christmas, Halloween, showcase, party, dance hall, stage and so on.&nbsp;<br />\r\nThere\'s no place it can\'t be applied to decorate, but only place you can\'t think of&nbsp;<br />\r\n<span style=\"font-weight:700;\">Warranty</span>&nbsp;<br />\r\nFor any problem, please contact us first, we will offer you a replacement or refund you.&nbsp;<br />\r\n<span style=\"font-weight:700;\">Specifications</span>&nbsp;<br />\r\nLight Color: Cool White&nbsp;<br />\r\nBattery: 3 x D size&nbsp;<br />\r\nCable length: Total length 15.7M/50ft, lead length: 30CM/0.98ft, lamp spacing: 7.7CM/0.25ft&nbsp;<br />\r\nLED Quantity: 200pcs, 200 LED at 7.7CM/0.25ft spacing&nbsp;<br />\r\n<span style=\"font-weight:700;\">What\'s in the box</span>&nbsp;<br />\r\n1 x Qedertek Battery Powered 200LED String Lights&nbsp;<br />\r\n1 x User Instruction\r\n</p>', '<ul class=\"a-unordered-list a-vertical a-spacing-none\" style=\"color:#949494;font-family:Arial, sans-serif;font-size:13.3333px;background-color:#FFFFFF;\">\r\n	<li>\r\n		<span class=\"a-list-item\" style=\"color:#111111;\">Ideal for Indoor and Outdoor Decor: The outdoor string lights illuminate during night, add warm and charming atmosphere to your garden, patio, lawn, porch, gate, yard, etc</span> \r\n	</li>\r\n	<li>\r\n		<span class=\"a-list-item\" style=\"color:#111111;\">Battery Powered String Lights: 200 bright cool white LEDs lights on the 50ft light strand (0.98ft lead cable included), powered by 3 x D batteries (not included), high-brightness but not dazzling</span> \r\n	</li>\r\n	<li>\r\n		<span class=\"a-list-item\" style=\"color:#111111;\">Timer Function: Auto ON/OFF for all lighting modes, 6 hours \"ON\" and 18 hours \"OFF\"</span> \r\n	</li>\r\n	<li>\r\n		<span class=\"a-list-item\" style=\"color:#111111;\">Easy to Operate &amp; Install: Easy operation with only one switch, 8 lighting modes</span> \r\n	</li>\r\n	<li>\r\n		<span class=\"a-list-item\" style=\"color:#111111;\">Waterproof: IP65 waterproof rate for the lights string, and IP44 for the battery box, which is suitable for indoor &amp; outdoor decorations</span> \r\n	</li>\r\n</ul>', '<div id=\"question-Tx2YCXEHZ0R6PT6\" class=\"a-fixed-left-grid a-spacing-small\" style=\"margin:0px;padding:0px;font-family:verdana, arial, helvetica, sans-serif;color:#111111;font-size:13.3333px;background-color:#FFFFFF;\">\r\n	<div class=\"a-fixed-left-grid-inner\" style=\"margin:0px;padding:0px 0px 0px 100px;font-family:HelveticaNeue, &quot;\">\r\n		<div class=\"a-fixed-left-grid-col a-col-left\" style=\"margin:0px 0px 0px -100px;padding:0px;font-family:HelveticaNeue, &quot;\">\r\n			<span class=\"a-text-bold\" style=\"font-weight:700 !important;\">Question:</span> \r\n		</div>\r\n		<div class=\"a-fixed-left-grid-col a-col-right\" style=\"margin:0px;padding:0px;font-family:HelveticaNeue, &quot;\">\r\n			Specifically on the qedertek battery operated christmas string lights that use 3 d batteries, how many days do the batteries last with 6 hrs on?\r\n		</div>\r\n	</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div class=\"a-fixed-left-grid a-spacing-base\" style=\"margin:0px;padding:0px;font-family:verdana, arial, helvetica, sans-serif;color:#111111;font-size:13.3333px;background-color:#FFFFFF;\">\r\n	<div class=\"a-fixed-left-grid-inner\" style=\"margin:0px;padding:0px 0px 0px 100px;font-family:HelveticaNeue, &quot;\">\r\n		<div class=\"a-fixed-left-grid-col a-col-left\" style=\"margin:0px 0px 0px -100px;padding:0px;font-family:HelveticaNeue, &quot;\">\r\n			<span class=\"a-text-bold\" style=\"font-weight:700 !important;\">Answer:</span> \r\n		</div>\r\n		<div class=\"a-fixed-left-grid-col a-col-right\" style=\"margin:0px;padding:0px;font-family:HelveticaNeue, &quot;\">\r\n			They use (3) three D batteries and I can them about every 6 to 8 weeks&nbsp;<br />\r\n<span class=\"a-color-tertiary\" style=\"color:#767676 !important;\">By Tawney Hale on November 19, 2016</span><span class=\"askInlineAnswers\" id=\"Tx2YCXEHZ0R6PT6\"> \r\n			<div id=\"askInlineAnswersPage-Tx2YCXEHZ0R6PT6-1\" class=\"a-section a-spacing-none\" style=\"margin:0px;padding:0px;\">\r\n				<div class=\"a-section a-spacing-none a-spacing-top-small\" style=\"margin:0px;padding:0px;\">\r\n					I put the first batteries in and they last about 1 week. I tried with 3 other batteries and now these have lasted since the weekend after Thanksgiving. It is Jan 15 now and the lights are just starting to look less bright. So, I think 6-8 weeks is about ri