ss=\"a-section a-spacing-none a-spacing-top-small\" style=\"margin:0px;padding:0px;\">\r\n						Yes. Plus you have the protection of Amazon no hassle returns&nbsp;<br />\r\n<span class=\"a-color-tertiary\" style=\"color:#767676 !important;\">By John T. on December 1, 2016</span> \r\n					</div>\r\n					<div class=\"a-section a-spacing-none a-spacing-top-small\" style=\"margin:0px;padding:0px;\">\r\n						Yes, I bought these lights last year and they still work wonderful, so I bought more for this year. I really like them.&nbsp;<br />\r\n<span class=\"a-color-tertiary\" style=\"color:#767676 !important;\">By Kimberly U. on December 2, 2016</span> \r\n					</div>\r\n				</div>\r\n</span> \r\n			</div>\r\n		</div>\r\n	</div>\r\n	<div id=\"question-Tx17R9RDQC0BEPV\" class=\"a-fixed-left-grid a-spacing-small\" style=\"margin:0px;padding:0px;font-family:HelveticaNeue, &quot;font-size:13.3333px;\">\r\n		<div class=\"a-fixed-left-grid-inner\" style=\"margin:0px;padding:0px 0px 0px 100px;font-family:HelveticaNeue, &quot;\">\r\n			<div class=\"a-fixed-left-grid-col a-col-left\" style=\"margin:0px 0px 0px -100px;padding:0px;font-family:HelveticaNeue, &quot;\">\r\n				<span class=\"a-text-bold\" style=\"font-weight:700 !important;\">Question:</span> \r\n			</div>\r\n			<div class=\"a-fixed-left-grid-col a-col-right\" style=\"margin:0px;padding:0px;font-family:HelveticaNeue, &quot;\">\r\n				How does the timer work? There is a \"timer\" sticker but when I scroll through it does not light up.\r\n			</div>\r\n		</div>\r\n	</div>\r\n	<div class=\"a-fixed-left-grid a-spacing-base\" style=\"margin:0px;padding:0px;font-family:HelveticaNeue, &quot;font-size:13.3333px;\">\r\n		<div class=\"a-fixed-left-grid-inner\" style=\"margin:0px;padding:0px 0px 0px 100px;font-family:HelveticaNeue, &quot;\">\r\n			<div class=\"a-fixed-left-grid-col a-col-left\" style=\"margin:0px 0px 0px -100px;padding:0px;font-family:HelveticaNeue, &quot;\">\r\n				<span class=\"a-text-bold\" style=\"font-weight:700 !important;\">Answer:</span> \r\n			</div>\r\n			<div class=\"a-fixed-left-grid-col a-col-right\" style=\"margin:0px;padding:0px;font-family:HelveticaNeue, &quot;\">\r\n				The timer is one of the top two...I believe one is for 6 hrs and the other is for 13 hrs. Just press the one you want&nbsp;<br />\r\n<span class=\"a-color-tertiary\" style=\"color:#767676 !important;\">By Tawney Hale on December 7, 2016</span><span class=\"askInlineAnswers\" id=\"Tx17R9RDQC0BEPV\"> \r\n				<div id=\"askInlineAnswersPage-Tx17R9RDQC0BEPV-1\" class=\"a-section a-spacing-none\" style=\"margin:0px;padding:0px;\">\r\n					<div class=\"a-section a-spacing-none a-spacing-top-small\" style=\"margin:0px;padding:0px;\">\r\n						Did you check if your batteries are good? Mine do not have a sticker, but a raised button to turn them on.&nbsp;<br />\r\n<span class=\"a-color-tertiary\" style=\"color:#767676 !important;\">By Amazon Customer on December 6, 2016</span> \r\n					</div>\r\n				</div>\r\n</span> \r\n			</div>\r\n		</div>\r\n	</div>\r\n	<div id=\"question-Tx19H30957L1AZQ\" class=\"a-fixed-left-grid a-spacing-small\" style=\"margin:0px;padding:0px;font-family:HelveticaNeue, &quot;font-size:13.3333px;\">\r\n		<div class=\"a-fixed-left-grid-inner\" style=\"margin:0px;padding:0px 0px 0px 100px;font-family:HelveticaNeue, &quot;\">\r\n			<div class=\"a-fixed-left-grid-col a-col-left\" style=\"margin:0px 0px 0px -100px;padding:0px;font-family:HelveticaNeue, &quot;\">\r\n				<span class=\"a-text-bold\" style=\"font-weight:700 !important;\">Question:</span> \r\n			</div>\r\n			<div class=\"a-fixed-left-grid-col a-col-right\" style=\"margin:0px;padding:0px;font-family:HelveticaNeue, &quot;\">\r\n				Are these solar lights or battery lights?\r\n			</div>\r\n		</div>\r\n	</div>\r\n	<div class=\"a-fixed-left-grid a-spacing-base\" style=\"margin:0px;padding:0px;font-family:HelveticaNeue, &quot;font-size:13.3333px;\">\r\n		<div class=\"a-fixed-left-grid-inner\" style=\"margin:0px;padding:0px 0px 0p