33333;font-family:&quot;font-size:small;background-color:#FFFFFF;\">Warranty</span><span style=\"color:#333333;font-family:&quot;font-size:small;background-color:#FFFFFF;\">&nbsp;</span><br />\r\n<span style=\"color:#333333;font-family:&quot;font-size:small;background-color:#FFFFFF;\">For any problem, please contact us, we will offer you a replacement or refund you.&nbsp;</span><br />\r\n<br />\r\n<span style=\"font-weight:700;color:#333333;font-family:&quot;font-size:small;background-color:#FFFFFF;\">What\'s in the box</span><span style=\"color:#333333;font-family:&quot;font-size:small;background-color:#FFFFFF;\">&nbsp;</span><br />\r\n<span style=\"color:#333333;font-family:&quot;font-size:small;background-color:#FFFFFF;\">1 x Qedertek 200 LED Solar String Lights&nbsp;</span><br />\r\n<span style=\"color:#333333;font-family:&quot;font-size:small;background-color:#FFFFFF;\">1 x Solar Panel with Ground Stake&nbsp;</span><br />\r\n<span style=\"color:#333333;font-family:&quot;font-size:small;background-color:#FFFFFF;\">1 x User Instruction</span>', '<ul class=\"a-unordered-list a-vertical a-spacing-none\" style=\"color:#949494;font-family:&quot;font-size:13px;background-color:#FFFFFF;\">\r\n	<li>\r\n		<span class=\"a-list-item\" style=\"color:#111111;\">Solar Powered String lights: 200 bright red LEDs on the 72ft light strand (6.5ft lead cable included), powered by built-in 1800mA NI-MH batteries</span>\r\n	</li>\r\n	<li>\r\n		<span class=\"a-list-item\" style=\"color:#111111;\">Long Working Time: Solar panel convert sunshine into electricity during the day, and it lights up automatically at night. Lights for more than 8 hours at night if solar panel absorbs enough sunlight during day.</span>\r\n	</li>\r\n	<li>\r\n		<span class=\"a-list-item\" style=\"color:#111111;\">Easy to Operate &amp; Install: Solar panel with garden stakes stand, 2 switches, On/Off and Mode switch</span>\r\n	</li>\r\n	<li>\r\n		<span class=\"a-list-item\" style=\"color:#111111;\">IP 65 Waterproof: Be able to withstand all kinds of weather, including heavy rain and snow, being perfect for indoor and outdoor decoration</span>\r\n	</li>\r\n	<li>\r\n		<span class=\"a-list-item\" style=\"color:#111111;\">Perfect Decorative Festival String Lights: The outdoor string lights illuminate during night, creating a warm and charming atmosphere to your home, garden, patio, lawn, porch, gate, party, yard, etc</span>\r\n	</li>\r\n</ul>', '<div id=\"question-Tx24JDHNLX8C0I2\" class=\"a-fixed-left-grid a-spacing-small\" style=\"color:#111111;font-family:verdana, arial, helvetica, sans-serif;font-size:13px;background-color:#FFFFFF;\">\r\n	<div class=\"a-fixed-left-grid-inner\" style=\"padding:0px 0px 0px 100px;\">\r\n		<div class=\"a-fixed-left-grid-col a-col-left\" style=\"margin-left:-100px;\">\r\n			<span style=\"font-weight:700;\">Question:</span>\r\n		</div>\r\n	</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div class=\"a-fixed-left-grid a-spacing-base\" style=\"color:#111111;font-family:verdana, arial, helvetica, sans-serif;font-size:13px;background-color:#FFFFFF;\">\r\n	<p>\r\n		<p>\r\n			<div id=\"question-Tx24JDHNLX8C0I2\" class=\"a-fixed-left-grid a-spacing-small\" style=\"color:#111111;font-family:verdana, arial, helvetica, sans-serif;font-size:13px;background-color:#FFFFFF;\">\r\n				<div class=\"a-fixed-left-grid-inner\" style=\"padding:0px 0px 0px 100px;\">\r\n					<div class=\"a-fixed-left-grid-col a-col-right\">\r\n						<a class=\"a-link-normal\" href=\"https://www.amazon.com/forum/-/Tx24JDHNLX8C0I2/ref=ask_dp_dpmw_al_hza?asin=B01EHPO3SS\">Would like to know if the battery is replaceble</a>\r\n					</div>\r\n				</div>\r\n			</div>\r\n			<div class=\"a-fixed-left-grid a-spacing-base\" style=\"color:#111111;font-family:verdana, arial, helvetica, sans-serif;font-size:13px;background-color:#FFFFFF;\">\r\n				<div class=\"a-fixed-left-grid-inner\" style=\"padding:0px 0px 0px 100px;\">\r\n					<div class=\"a-fixed-left-grid-col a-col-left\" style=\"margin-left:-100px;\">\r\n						<span class=\"a-text-bold\" style=\"font-weight:700 !important;\">Answer:</span>\r\n					</div>\r\n					<div class=\"a-fixed-left-grid-col a-col-right\">\r\n						<span>Yes the batteries are replaceable.</span>&nbsp;\r\n					</div>\r\n				</div>\r\n			</div>\r\n			<div id=\"question-Tx1JTLX33K9VDBR\" class=\"a-fixed-left-grid a-spacing-small\" style=\"color:#111111;font-family:verdana, arial, helvetica, sans-serif;font-size:13px;background-color:#FFFFFF;\">\r\n				<div class=\"a-fixed-left-grid-inner\" style=\"padding:0px 0px 0px 100px;\">\r\n					<div class=\"a-fixed-left-grid-col a-col-left\" style=\"margin-left:-100px;\">\r\n						<span class=\"a-text-bold\" style=\"font-weight:700 !important;\">Question:</span>\r\n					</div>\r\n					<div class=\"a-fixed-left-grid-col a-col-right\">\r\n						<a class=\"a-link-normal\" href=\"https://www.amazon.com/forum/-/Tx1JTLX33K9VDBR/ref=ask_dp_dpmw_al_hza?asin=B01EHPO3SS\">How Long do I need to charge the battery before first use? Does it comes with instruction?</a>\r\n					</div>\r\n				</div>\r\n			</div>\r\n			<div class=\"a-fixed-left-grid a-spacing-base\" style=\"color:#111111;font-family:verdana, arial, helvetica, sans-serif;font-size:13px;background-color:#FFFFFF;\">\r\n				<div class=\"a-fixed-left-grid-inner\" style=\"padding:0px 0px 0px 100px;\">\r\n					<div class=\"a-fixed-left-grid-col a-col-left\" style=\"margin-left:-100px;\">\r\n						<span class=\"a-text-bold\" style=\"font-weight:700 !important;\">Answer:</span>\r\n					</div>\r\n					<div class=\"a-fixed-left-grid-col a-col-right\">\r\n						<span class=\"askExpanderContainer askExpanderExpanded\">My lights lit up as soon as I peeled the covering from the solar charger, but I placed them during the day. This would lead me to believe that, even if charging were necessary, it wouldnt take long. Instructions were included, the not extremely detailed. There\'s not much to it - just place and secure the lights and place the solar panel where sunlight can reach it. :) It also comes with a stake to place the solar panel at ground level, should you choose to. Hope this helps!</span>\r\n					</div>\r\n				</div>\r\n			</div>\r\n			<div id=\"question-Tx1HHJET6LF0HCT\" class=\"a-fixed-left-grid a-spacing-small\" style=\"color:#111111;font-family:verdana, arial, helvetica, sans-serif;font-size:13px;background-color:#FFFFFF;\">\r\n				<div class=\"a-fixed-left-grid-inner\" style=\"padding:0px 0px 0px 100px;\">\r\n					<div class=\"a-fixed-left-grid-col a-col-left\" style=\"margin-left:-100px;\">\r\n						<span class=\"a-text-bold\" style=\"font-weight:700 !important;\">Question:</span>\r\n					</div>\r\n					<div class=\"a-fixed-left-grid-col a-col-right\">\r\n						<a class=\"a-link-normal\" href=\"https://www.amazon.com/forum/-/Tx1HHJET6LF0HCT/ref=ask_dp_dpmw_al_hza?asin=B01EHPO3SS\">Are the leds interchangeable? Can I buy two different colored strands and exchange the leds?</a>\r\n					</div>\r\n				</div>\r\n			</div>\r\n			<div class=\"a-fixed-left-grid a-spacing-base\" style=\"color:#111111;font-family:verdana, arial, helvetica, sans-serif;font-size:13px;background-color:#FFFFFF;\">\r\n				<div class=\"a-fixed-left-grid-inner\" style=\"padding:0px 0px 0px 100px;\">\r\n					<div class=\"a-fixed-left-grid-col a-col-left\" style=\"margin-left:-100px;\">\r\n						<span class=\"a-text-bold\" style=\"font-weight:700 !important;\">Answer:</span>\r\n					</div>\r\n					<div class=\"a-fixed-left-grid-col a-col-right\">\r\n						<span>Sorry to note you that the leds on different strands are not exchangeable. If you want different color, we do sell multi-color strands.</span>&nbsp;\r\n					</div>\r\n				</div>\r\n			</div>\r\n			<div id=\"question-Tx1INAXHNXBLVRJ\" class=\"a-fixed-left-grid a-spacing-small\" style=\"color:#111111;font-family:verdana, arial, helvetica, sans-serif;font-size:13px;background-color:#FFFFFF;\">\r\n				<div class=\"a-fixed-left-grid-inner\" style=\"padding:0px 0px 0px 100px;\">\r\n					<div class=\"a-fixed-left-grid-col a-col-left\" style=\"margin-left:-100px;\">\r\n						<span class=\"a-text-bold\" style=\"font-weight:700 !important;\">Question:</span>\r\n					</div>\r\n					<div class=\"a-fixed-left-grid-col a-col-right\">\r\n						<a class=\"a-link-normal\" href=\"https://www.amazon.com/forum/-/Tx1INAXHNXBLVRJ/ref=ask_dp_dpmw_al_hza?asin=B01EHPO3SS\">can the solar panel be detached for charginf?</a>\r\n					</div>\r\n				</div>\r\n			</div>\r\n			<div class=\"a-fixed-left-grid a-spacing-base\" style=\"color:#111111;font-family:verdana, arial, helvetica, sans-serif;font-size:13px;background-color:#FFFFFF;\">\r\n				<div class=\"a-fixed-left-grid-inner\" style=\"padding:0px 0px 0px 100px;\">\r\n					<div class=\"a-fixed-left-grid-col a-col-left\" style=\"margin-left:-100px;\">\r\n						<span class=\"a-text-bold\" style=\"font-weight:700 !important;\">Answer:</span>\r\n					</div>\r\n					<div class=\"a-fixed-left-grid-col a-col-right\">\r\n						<span>Mine can\'t be detached</span>&nbsp;\r\n					</div>\r\n				</div>\r\n			</div>\r\n		</p>\r\n	</p>\r\n</div>', '72ft 200 LED Solar Fairy Party Lighting Festive Lights Red - Qedertek', '', '', 'https://www.amazon.com/dp/B01EHPO3SS/', '', '0', '0.00', 'http://images.qedertek.com/59367452c7a9a', '{\"59367452ecded\":\"http:\\/\\/images.qedertek.com\\/59367452ecded\",\"593674531d98b\":\"http:\\/\\/images.qedertek.com\\/593674531d98b\",\"5936745342faf\":\"http:\\/\\/images.qedertek.com\\/5936745342faf\",\"5936745364928\":\"http:\\/\\/images.qedertek.com\\/5936745364928\",\"593674539161a\":\"http:\\/\\/images.qedertek.com\\/593674539161a\"}', '0', '0', '0', '0.00', '1', '1496740947', '1496740947', '', '0');
