INSERT INTO `qe_product` VALUES ('69', '2', 'Solar Powered Butterfly String Lights 40 LED Cool White', '<div class=\"disclaim\" style=\"font-size:10px;color:#888888;margin:0px 0px 1em;font-family:verdana, arial, helvetica, sans-serif;background-color:#FFFFFF;\">\r\n	Color Name:<span style=\"font-weight:700;\">Cool White</span>\r\n</div>\r\n<p style=\"margin-left:1em;color:#333333;font-family:&quot;font-size:small;background-color:#FFFFFF;\">\r\n	<span style=\"font-weight:700;\">Features</span>&nbsp;<br />\r\nSolar Powered LED: No need of any external wire, no utility electricity costs, eco-friendly.<br />\r\nBeautiful butterfly appearance makes your environment fantastic.<br />\r\nLength of 24.6ft (7.5m) with 40 LED could be expanded to cover a wide area, bundle it up when not use, taking little space.<br />\r\n<br />\r\n<span style=\"font-weight:700;\">Working principle about the solar panel</span>&nbsp;<br />\r\n1. The solar panel collects sunlight during daytime, then converts solar energy to electrical energy to store in the rechargeable battery.&nbsp;<br />\r\n2. The battery converts the stored energy into power to lighting it up in darkness.&nbsp;<br />\r\n<br />\r\n<span style=\"font-weight:700;\">Specifications</span>&nbsp;<br />\r\nLight color: Cool White&nbsp;<br />\r\nLED Quantity: 40 LED&nbsp;<br />\r\nRechargeable Ni-MH Battery: 1.2V 600mA&nbsp;<br />\r\nSwitch: Power ON/OFF, MODE&nbsp;<br />\r\nLighting Mode: Steady and 7 Blinking modes&nbsp;<br />\r\nSolar Panel: 2V 100mA&nbsp;<br />\r\nCharging Time: 6 hours&nbsp;<br />\r\nLight Length: 24.6ft (7.5m)&nbsp;<br />\r\nLength between 2 blubs: 0.5ft (0.15m)&nbsp;<br />\r\nLength from Solar panel to first stake: 4.9ft (1.5m)&nbsp;<br />\r\nSolar panel with ground stake (8in) for easy positioning&nbsp;<br />\r\n<br />\r\n<span style=\"font-weight:700;\">What\'s in the box&nbsp;</span><br />\r\n1 x Qedertek Solar String Lights&nbsp;<br />\r\n1 x Solar Panel with Ground Stake&nbsp;<br />\r\n1 x User Manual\r\n</p>', '<ul class=\"a-unordered-list a-vertical a-spacing-none\" style=\"color:#949494;font-family:&quot;font-size:13px;background-color:#FFFFFF;\">\r\n	<li>\r\n		<span class=\"a-list-item\" style=\"color:#111111;\">LIGHTING SENSOR TECHNOLOGY - Solar panels and rechargeable battery, charge under sunshine and turn on automatically at dusk</span>\r\n	</li>\r\n	<li>\r\n		<span class=\"a-list-item\" style=\"color:#111111;\">SUPER LONG WORKING TIME - Up to 8 hours of continuous lighting with a single battery fully charged</span>\r\n	</li>\r\n	<li>\r\n		<span class=\"a-list-item\" style=\"color:#111111;\">2 SWITCH BUTTONS - Power ON/OFF &amp; Mode switches (8 different modes), easily operate &amp; install</span>\r\n	</li>\r\n	<li>\r\n		<span class=\"a-list-item\" style=\"color:#111111;\">WATERPROOF LIGHTS - Can withstand all kinds of weather, including heavy rain and snow, perfect for Indoor and outdoor decorations</span>\r\n	</li>\r\n	<li>\r\n		<span class=\"a-list-item\" style=\"color:#111111;\">SUITABLE FOR ALL DECORATIONS - These wonderful string lights illuminate during night, creating warm and charming atmosphere in your gardens, patio, lawn, porch, gate, yard, etc</span>\r\n	</li>\r\n</ul>', '<div id=\"question-Tx11KNV57FVP0YE\" class=\"a-fixed-left-grid a-spacing-small\" style=\"color:#111111;font-family:verdana, arial, helvetica, sans-serif;font-size:13px;background-color:#FFFFFF;\">\r\n	<div class=\"a-fixed-left-grid-inner\" style=\"padding:0px 0px 0px 100px;\">\r\n		<div class=\"a-fixed-left-grid-col a-col-left\" style=\"margin-left:-100px;\">\r\n			<span class=\"a-text-bold\" style=\"font-weight:700 !important;\">Question:</span> \r\n		</div>\r\n		<div class=\"a-fixed-left-grid-col a-col-right\">\r\n			So far I have not gotten them to turn on. I hung them indoors and placed the solar panel at the window. Can they only be used outside?\r\n		</div>\r\n	</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div class=\"a-fixed-left-grid a-spacing-base\" style=\"color:#111111;font-family:verdana, arial, helvetica, sans-serif;font-size:13px;background-color:#FFFFFF;\">\r\n	<div class=\"a-fixed-left-grid-inner\" style=\"padding:0px 0px 0px 100px;\">\r\n		<div class=\"a-fixed-left-grid-col a-col-left\" style=\"margin-left:-100px;\">\r\n			<span class=\"a-text-bold\" style=\"font-weight:700 !important;\">Answer:</span> \r\n		</div>\r\n		<div class=\"a-fixed-left-grid-col a-col-right\">\r\n			<span>They don\'t work indoors because I tried that first. Once I put them outside in the sun on my porch they turn on automatically at dusk every nite. I love them very pretty.</span>&nbsp;<br />\r\n<span class=\"a-color-tertiary\" style=\"color:#767676 !important;\">By colleen w on May 7, 2017</span><span class=\"askInlineAnswers\" id=\"Tx11KNV57FVP0YE\"> \r\n			<div id=\"askInlineAnswersPage-Tx11KNV57FVP0YE-1\" class=\"a-section a-spacing-none\">\r\n				<div class=\"a-section a-spacing-none a-spacing-top-small\">\r\n					<span class=\"askExpanderContainer askExpanderExpanded\"><span class=\"askLongText\">They are solar powered, but if you put the solar panel at the widow, it should work, but you\'d better make sure that the lights in your room do not illuminate the solar panel(solar panel should be covered), cause the solar panel is light sensor, if it were light up at night, the lights strands will not work. Hope this help, thanks!&nbsp;</span></span><br />\r\n<span class=\"a-color-tertiary\" style=\"color:#767676 !important;\">By Holigoo Direct&nbsp;on May 12, 2017</span> \r\n				</div>\r\n				<div class=\"a-section a-spacing-none a-spacing-top-small\">\r\n					<span>Mine are outside and so fine</span>&nbsp;<br />\r\n<span class=\"a-color-tertiary\" style=\"color:#767676 !important;\">By Amazon Customer on May 7, 2017</span> \r\n				</div>\r\n			</div>\r\n			<div id=\"askInlineAnswersPage-Tx11KNV57FVP0YE-2\" class=\"a-section a-spacing-none\">\r\n				<div class=\"a-section a-spacing-none a-spacing-top-small\">\r\n					<span>no, they can be used indoors and outdoors. There is a switch on the bottom of the solar panel part to turn on</span>&nbsp;<br />\r\n<span class=\"a-color-tertiary\" style=\"color:#767676 !important;\">By Sheri B Lodel on May 7, 2017</span> \r\n				</div>\r\n				<div class=\"a-section a-spacing-none a-spacing-top-small\">\r\n					<span>Mine work indoors, but only if it is almost completely dark, otherwise they shut off after a few seconds.</span>&nbsp;<br />\r\n<span class=\"a-color-tertiary\" style=\"color:#767676 !important;\">By L. Hamilton on May 7, 2017</span> \r\n				</div>\r\n			</div>\r\n</span> \r\n		</div>\r\n	</div>\r\n	<div id=\"question-Tx307GRHY6LIRI9\" class=\"a-fixed-left-grid a-spacing-small\" style=\"color:#111111;font-family:verdana, arial, helvetica, sans-serif;font-size:13px;background-color:#FFFFFF;\">\r\n		<div class=\"a-fixed-left-grid-inner\" style=\"padding:0px 0px 0px 100px;\">\r\n			<div class=\"a-fixed-left-grid-col a-col-left\" style=\"margin-left:-100px;\">\r\n				<span class=\"a-text-bold\" style=\"font-weight:700 !important;\">Question:</span>\r\n			</div>\r\n			<div class=\"a-fixed-left-grid-col a-col-right\">\r\n				Is the solar panel waterproof like it says the lights are?\r\n			</div>\r\n		</div>\r\n	</div>\r\n	<div class=\"a-fixed-left-grid a-spacing-base\" style=\"color:#111111;font-family:verdana, arial, helvetica, sans-serif;font-size:13px;background-color:#FFFFFF;\">\r\n		<div class=\"a-fixed-left-grid-inner\" style=\"padding:0px 0px 0px 100px;\">\r\n			<div class=\"a-fixed-left-grid-col a-col-left\" style=\"margin-left:-100px;\">\r\n				<span class=\"a-text-bold\" style=\"font-weight:700 !important;\">Answer:</span>\r\n			</div>\r\n			<div class=\"a-fixed-left-grid-col a-col-right\">\r\n				<span>I have 3 mounted to the roof over my patio. They are exposed to all the elements, so yes.</span>&nbsp;<br />\r\n<span class=\"a-color-tertiary\" style=\"color:#767676 !important;\">By G. Hults on May 14, 2017</span><span class=\"askInlineAnswers\" id=\"Tx307GRHY6LIRI9\">\r\n				<div id=\"askInlineAnswersPage-Tx307GRHY6LIRI9-1\" class=\"a-section a-spacing-none\">\r\n					<div class=\"a-section a-spacing-none a-spacing-top-small\">\r\n						<span>Yes mine are outside have been in heavy rains. It is an ambiance of light . I have the all clear ones I have had many compliments on them.</span>&nbsp;<br />\r\n<span class=\"a-color-tertiary\" style=\"color:#767676 !important;\">By Limee49 on May 14, 2017</span>\r\n					</div>\r\n				</div>\r\n</span>\r\n			</div>\r\n		</div>\r\n	</div>\r\n	<div id=\"question-Tx3Q91521N0C6CI\" class=\"a-fixed-left-grid a-spacing-small\" style=\"color:#111111;font-family:verdana, arial, helvetica, sans-serif;font-size:13px;background-color:#FFFFFF;\">\r\n		<div class=\"a-fixed-left-grid-inner\" style=\"padding:0px 0px 0px 100px;\">\r\n			<div class=\"a-fixed-left-grid-col a-col-left\" style=\"margin-left:-100px;\">\r\n				<span class=\"a-text-bold\" style=\"font-weight:700 !important;\">Question:</span>\r\n			</div>\r\n			<div class=\"a-fixed-left-grid-col a-col-right\">\r\n				Is their an automatic feature on these lights or do they automatically shut off during the day if you leave on?\r\n			</div>\r\n		</div>\r\n	</div>\r\n	<div class=\"a-fixed-left-grid a-spacing-base\" style=\"color:#111111;font-family:verdana, arial, helvetica, sans-serif;font-size:13px;background-color:#FFFFFF;\">\r\n		<div class=\"a-fixed-left-grid-inner\" style=\"padding:0px 0px 0px 100px;\">\r\n			<div class=\"a-fixed-left-grid-col a-col-left\" style=\"margin-left:-100px;\">\r\n				<span class=\"a-text-bold\" style=\"font-weight:700 !important;\">Answer:</span>\r\n			</div>\r\n			<div class=\"a-fixed-left-grid-col a-col-right\">\r\n				<span>It turns off during the day</span>&nbsp;<br />\r\n<span class=\"a-color-tertiary\" style=\"color:#767676 !important;\">By Datalink on June 12, 2017</span><span class=\"askInlineAnswers\" id=\"Tx3Q91521N0C6CI\">\r\n				<div id=\"askInlineAnswersPage-Tx3Q91521N0C6CI-1\" class=\"a-section a-spacing-none\">\r\n					<div class=\"a-section a-spacing-none a-spacing-top-small\">\r\n						<span>I hope you are asking the same thing in this question. During daylight hours, the solar battery recharges. The lights during daylight do not come on. At night, they light up. There is an on/off switch on the battery to keep the lights from coming on at night if you do not want the lights to be on at night.</span>&nbsp;<br />\r\n<span class=\"a-color-tertiary\" style=\"color:#767676 !important;\">By Sheri B Lodel on June 12, 2017</span>\r\n					</div>\r\n					<div class=\"a-section a-spacing-none a-spacing-top-small\">\r\n						<span>You can turn off but auto they will one on at dusk off at dawn</span>&nbsp;<br />\r\n<span class=\"a-color-tertiary\" style=\"color:#767676 !important;\">By Limee49 on June 12, 2017</span>\r\n					</div>\r\n				</div>\r\n				<div id=\"askInlineAnswersPage-Tx3Q91521N0C6CI-2\" class=\"a-section a-spacing-none\">\r\n					<div class=\"a-section a-spacing-none a-spacing-top-small\">\r\n						<span>this is solar so it charges during day and runs till energy is depleted has 3 modes for lights but no worries about leaving it on its automatic turn it on and at dusk it comes on</span>&nbsp;<br />\r\n<span class=\"a-color-tertiary\" style=\"color:#767676 !important;\">By linda c on June 12, 2017</span>\r\n					</div>\r\n					<div class=\"a-section a-spacing-none a-spacing-top-small\">\r\n						<span>As long as the button stays on, they will automatically turn on at dusk &amp; off at dawn</span>&nbsp;<br />\r\n<span class=\"a-color-tertiary\" style=\"color:#767676 !important;\">By Redbear on June 12, 2017</span>\r\n					</div>\r\n				</div>\r\n</span>\r\n			</div>\r\n		</div>\r\n	</div>\r\n</div>', '40 LED Cool White Solar Butterfly String Lights | Butterfly Decorative Fairy Lighting for Bedroom - Qedertek', 'butterfly world christmas lights,butterfly decorative lights,butterfly fairy lights for bedroom,solar butterfly string lights,cool white led butterfly string lights', 'Wanna to shop butterfly decorative lights online, Qedertek is a professional solar butterfly string lights supplier,40 LED cool white led butterfly fairy lights, 8 different modes, solar powered, eco-friendly,would be your best choice.', 'https://www.amazon.com/dp/B01I32EAOS/', '', '0', '0.00', 'http://images.qedertek.com/597078658d47c', '{\"59707865b2f96\":\"http:\\/\\/images.qedertek.com\\/59707865b2f96\",\"59707865c2616\":\"http:\\/\\/images.qedertek.com\\/59707865c2616\",\"59707865e8c5e\":\"http:\\/\\/images.qedertek.com\\/59707865e8c5e\",\"5970786607adc\":\"http:\\/\\/images.qedertek.com\\/5970786607adc\",\"5970786625059\":\"http:\\/\\/images.qedertek.com\\/5970786625059\",\"5970786637da2\":\"http:\\/\\/images.qedertek.com\\/5970786637da2\"}', '0', '0', '1', '0.00', '1', '1500543078', '1500543078', '', '0');
INSERT INTO `qe_product` VALUES ('70', '2', 'Solar Butterfly String Party Lights 40 LED Multi-Color', '<div class=\"celwidget aplus-module 3p-module-b\" style=\"color:#111111;font-family:&quot;font-size:13px;background-color:#FFFFFF;\">\r\n	<div class=\"aplus-3p-fixed-width\">\r\n		<h3 class=\"a-spacing-mini\" style=\"margin-left:0px;font-size:17px;\">\r\n			Qedertek Butterfly Solar String Lights, 24.6ft 40 LED Waterproof Fairy Lights\r\n		</h3>\r\n<img alt=\"\" src=\"https://m.media-amazon.com/images/S/aplus-seller-content-images-us-east-1/ATVPDKIKX0DER/A231TAZUOKNIOW/B01I32E5J8/2rd52649SduF._UX970_TTW__.jpg\" class=\"a-spacing-base\" />\r\n		<p class=\"a-spacing-base\">\r\n			<span class=\"a-text-bold\" style=\"font-weight:700 !important;\">Product&nbsp;Features</span><br />\r\n<br />\r\nSolar&nbsp;Powered&nbsp;String&nbsp;Lights,&nbsp;no&nbsp;utility&nbsp;electricity&nbsp;costs,&nbsp;low consumpstion.<br />\r\n<br />\r\nAuto&nbsp;On&amp;Auto&nbsp;Off:&nbsp;under&nbsp;“On”&nbsp;state,&nbsp;the&nbsp;lights&nbsp;turns&nbsp;off&nbsp;automatically&nbsp;when&nbsp;the&nbsp;solar&nbsp;panel&nbsp;is&nbsp;on&nbsp;a&nbsp;bright&nbsp;environment&nbsp;and&nbsp;turn&nbsp;on&nbsp;automatically&nbsp;at&nbsp;dark.<br />\r\nEasy&nbsp;Operate&nbsp;Solar&nbsp;Lights:&nbsp;Just&nbsp;push&nbsp;between&nbsp;the&nbsp;power&nbsp;button&nbsp;and&nbsp;the&nbsp;mode&nbsp;button&nbsp;to&nbsp;turn&nbsp;the&nbsp;lights&nbsp;string&nbsp;on/off,&nbsp;or&nbsp;choose&nbsp;modes.<br />\r\n<br />\r\nMultiple&nbsp;Modes&nbsp;Solar&nbsp;Outdoor&nbsp;Lights:&nbsp;Modes&nbsp;include&nbsp;steady&nbsp;on&nbsp;and&nbsp;7&nbsp;flashing&nbsp;modes,&nbsp;just&nbsp;select&nbsp;your&nbsp;favorite&nbsp;mode!<br />\r\n<br />\r\n<span class=\"a-text-bold\" style=\"font-weight:700 !important;\">Warm&nbsp;Tips</span><br />\r\nIt&nbsp;is&nbsp;suggested&nbsp;that&nbsp;the&nbsp;solar&nbsp;panel&nbsp;be&nbsp;fully&nbsp;charged&nbsp;for&nbsp;8hrs&nbsp;at&nbsp;the&nbsp;first&nbsp;use.<br />\r\n<br />\r\nPlease&nbsp;put&nbsp;down&nbsp;the&nbsp;front&nbsp;surface&nbsp;of&nbsp;the&nbsp;solar&nbsp;panel&nbsp;covered&nbsp;it&nbsp;up&nbsp;at&nbsp;night,&nbsp;avoiding&nbsp;it&nbsp;sensor&nbsp;the&nbsp;car&nbsp;light&nbsp;or&nbsp;street&nbsp;light&nbsp;around&nbsp;and&nbsp;auto&nbsp;off.<br />\r\nWhen&nbsp;lights&nbsp;are&nbsp;at&nbsp;off&nbsp;state,&nbsp;they&nbsp;are&nbsp;clear&nbsp;color,&nbsp;only&nbsp;when&nbsp;turned&nbsp;on&nbsp;it\'s&nbsp;colorful.\r\n		</p>\r\n	</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div class=\"celwidget aplus-module 3p-module-c\" style=\"color:#111111;font-family:&quot;font-size:13px;background-color:#FFFFFF;\">\r\n	<div class=\"aplus-3p-fixed-width\">\r\n		<h3 class=\"a-spacing-mini\" style=\"margin-left:0px;font-size:17px;\">\r\n			LED Butterfly Lights\r\n		</h3>\r\n		<div class=\"a-row\">\r\n			<div class=\"a-column a-span4 a-spacing-base\">\r\n				<img alt=\"\" src=\"https://m.media-amazon.com/images/S/aplus-seller-content-images-us-east-1/ATVPDKIKX0DER/A231TAZUOKNIOW/B01I32E5J8/tMd4OZSgT9Ko._UX300_TTW__.jpg\" />\r\n			</div>\r\n			<p>\r\n				<p>\r\n					<span class=\"a-text-bold\" style=\"font-weight:700 !important;\">Specifications&nbsp;</span><br />\r\nLight color: Multi-Color<br />\r\nLED Quantity: 40 LED&nbsp;<br />\r\nRechargeable: Ni-MH AA Battery: 1.2V 600mA&nbsp;<br />\r\nSwitch: Power ON/OFF, MODE&nbsp;<br />\r\nLighting Mode: Steady On and 7 Blinking modes&nbsp;<br />\r\nSolar Panel: 2V 100mA&nbsp;<br />\r\nCharging Time: 6 hours&nbsp;<br />\r\nLight Length: 24.6ft (7.5m)&nbsp;<br />\r\nLength between 2 blubs: 0.5ft (0.15m)&nbsp;<br />\r\nLength from Solar panel to first stake: 4.9ft(1.5m)&nbsp;<br />\r\nSolar panel with ground stake (8in) for easily positioning&nbsp;\r\n				</p>\r\n				<p>\r\n					<span style=\"font-size:17px;\">Colorful Solar Outdoor Lights</span>\r\n				</p>\r\n			</p>\r\n		</div>\r\n	</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div class=\"celwidget aplus-module 3p-module-c\" style=\"color:#111111;font-family:&quot;font-size:13px;background-color:#FFFFFF;\">\r\n	<div class=\"aplus-3p-fixed-width\">\r\n		<div class=\"a-row\">\r\n			<div class=\"a-column a-span4 a-spacing-base\">\r\n				<img alt=\"\" src=\"https://m.media-amazon.com/images/S/aplus-seller-content-images-us-east-1/ATVPDKIKX0DER/A231TAZUOKNIOW/B01I32E5J8/cmGcZzg5Sfm3._UX300_TTW__.jpg\" />\r\n			</div>\r\n			<div class=\"a-column a-span8 a-spacing-base a-span-last\">\r\n				<p>\r\n					<span class=\"a-text-bold\" style=\"font-weight:700 !important;\">Multi&nbsp;Color&nbsp;Fairy&nbsp;Lights</span><br />\r\nRed/Green/Warm&nbsp;White/Purple<br />\r\nColorful&nbsp;Led&nbsp;butterfly&nbsp;light&nbsp;up&nbsp;on&nbsp;a&nbsp;string<br />\r\nBuilt&nbsp;up&nbsp;an&nbsp;interesting,&nbsp;joyful&nbsp;world&nbsp;for&nbsp;you<br />\r\nIgnite&nbsp;your&nbsp;enthusiasm!<br />\r\n<br />\r\n<br />\r\n<span class=\"a-text-bold\" style=\"font-weight:700 !important;\">Package&nbsp;include&nbsp;</span><br />\r\n1&nbsp;x&nbsp;Qedertek&nbsp;Solar&nbsp;String&nbsp;Lights&nbsp;&nbsp;<br />\r\n1&nbsp;x&nbsp;Solar&nbsp;Panel&nbsp;with&nbsp;Ground&nbsp;Stake&nbsp;&nbsp;<br />\r\n1&nbsp;x&nbsp;User&nbsp;Instruction\r\n				</p>\r\n			</div>\r\n		</div>\r\n	</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div class=\"celwidget aplus-module 3p-module-d\" style=\"color:#111111;font-family:&quot;font-size:13px;background-color:#FFFFFF;\">\r\n	<div class=\"aplus-3p-fixed-width\">\r\n		<h3 class=\"a-spacing-mini\" style=\"margin-left:0px;font-size:17px;\">\r\n			Special butterfly led lights, ideal decorations for wedding, cafe, porch, patio, garden, lawn, party and more\r\n		</h3>\r\n		<div class=\"a-row\">\r\n			<div class=\"a-column a-span4 a-spacing-base\">\r\n				<img alt=\"\" src=\"https://m.media-amazon.com/images/S/aplus-seller-content-images-us-east-1/ATVPDKIKX0DER/A231TAZUOKNIOW/B01I32E5J8/CSPTPgVSqG1._UX300_TTW__.jpg\" class=\"a-spacing-base\" />\r\n			</div>\r\n			<div class=\"a-column a-span4 a-spacing-base\">\r\n				<img alt=\"\" src=\"https://m.media-amazon.com/images/S/aplus-seller-content-images-us-east-1/ATVPDKIKX0DER/A231TAZUOKNIOW/B01I32E5J8/zmMyodiTm2M._UX300_TTW__.jpg\" class=\"a-spacing-base\" />\r\n			</div>\r\n			<div class=\"a-column a-span4 a-spacing-base a-span-last\">\r\n				<img alt=\"\" src=\"https://m.media-amazon.com/images/S/aplus-seller-content-images-us-east-1/ATVPDKIKX0DER/A231TAZUOKNIOW/B01I32E5J8/ySL3EunRWep._UX300_TTW__.jpg\" class=\"a-spacing-base\" />\r\n			</div>\r\n		</div>\r\n	</div>\r\n</div>', '<ul class=\"a-unordered-list a-vertical a-spacing-none\" style=\"color:#949494;font-family:&quot;font-size:13px;background-color:#FFFFFF;\">\r\n	<li>\r\n		<span class=\"a-list-item\" style=\"color:#111111;\">LIGHTING SENSOR TECHNOLOGY - Solar panels and rechargeable battery, charge under sunshine and turn on automatically at dusk</span>\r\n	</li>\r\n	<li>\r\n		<span class=\"a-list-item\" style=\"color:#111111;\">SUPER LONG WORKING TIME - Up to 8 hours of continuous lighting with a single battery fully charged</span>\r\n	</li>\r\n	<li>\r\n		<span class=\"a-list-item\" style=\"color:#111111;\">2 SWITCH BUTTONS - Power ON/OFF &amp; Mode switches (8 different modes), easily operate &amp; install</span>\r\n	</li>\r\n	<li>\r\n		<span class=\"a-list-item\" style=\"color:#111111;\">WATERPROOF LIGHTS - Can withstand all kinds of weather, including heavy rain and snow, perfect for Indoor and outdoor decorations</span>\r\n	</li>\r\n	<li>\r\n		<span class=\"a-list-item\" style=\"color:#111111;\">SUITABLE FOR ALL DECORATIONS - These wonderful string lights illuminate during night, creating warm and charming atmosphere in your gardens, patio, lawn, porch, gate, yard, etc</span>\r\n	</li>\r\n</ul>', '<div id=\"question-Tx11KNV57FVP0YE\" class=\"a-fixed-left-grid a-spacing-small\" style=\"margin:0px;padding:0px;font-family:verdana, arial, helvetica, sans-serif;color:#111111;font-size:13px;background-color:#FFFFFF;\">\r\n	<div class=\"a-fixed-left-grid-inner\" style=\"margin:0px;padding:0px 0px 0px 100px;\">\r\n		<div class=\"a-fixed-left-grid-col a-col-left\" style=\"margin:0px 0px 0px -100px;padding:0px;\">\r\n			<span class=\"a-text-bold\" style=\"font-weight:700 !important;\">Question:</span>\r\n		</div>\r\n		<div class=\"a-fixed-left-grid-col a-col-right\" style=\"margin:0px;padding:0px;\">\r\n			So far I have not gotten them to turn on. I hung them indoors and placed the solar panel at the window. Can they only be used outside?\r\n		</div>\r\n	</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div class=\"a-fixed-left-grid a-spacing-base\" style=\"margin:0px;padding:0px;font-family:verdana, arial, helvetica, sans-serif;color:#111111;font-size:13px;background-color:#FFFFFF;\">\r\n	<div class=\"a-fixed-left-grid-inner\" style=\"margin:0px;padding:0px 0px 0px 100px;\">\r\n		<div class=\"a-fixed-left-grid-col a-col-left\" style=\"margin:0px 0px 0px -100px;padding:0px;\">\r\n			<span class=\"a-text-bold\" style=\"font-weight:700 !important;\">Answer:</span>\r\n		</div>\r\n		<div class=\"a-fixed-left-grid-col a-col-right\" style=\"margin:0px;padding:0px;\">\r\n			<span>They don\'t work indoors because I tried that first. Once I put them outside in the sun on my porch they turn on automatically at dusk every nite. I love them very pretty.</span>&nbsp;<br />\r\n<span class=\"a-color-tertiary\" style=\"color:#767676 !important;\">By colleen w on May 7, 2017</span><span class=\"askInlineAnswers\" id=\"Tx11KNV57FVP0YE\">\r\n			<div id=\"askInlineAnswersPage-Tx11KNV57FVP0YE-1\" class=\"a-section a-spacing-none\" style=\"margin:0px;padding:0px;\">\r\n				<div class=\"a-section a-spacing-none a-spacing-top-small\" style=\"margin:0px;padding:0px;\">\r\n					<span class=\"askExpanderContainer askExpanderExpanded\">They are solar powered, but if you put the solar panel at the widow, it should work, but you\'d better make sure that the lights in your room do not illuminate the solar panel(solar panel should be covered), cause the solar panel is light sensor, if it were light up at night, the lights strands will not work. Hope this help, thanks!&nbsp;</span><br />\r\n<span class=\"a-color-tertiary\" style=\"color:#767676 !important;\">By Holigoo Direct&nbsp;on May 12, 2017</span>\r\n				</div>\r\n				<div class=\"a-section a-spacing-none a-spacing-top-small\" style=\"margin:0px;padding:0px;\">\r\n					<span>Mine are outside and so fine</span>&nbsp;<br />\r\n<span class=\"a-color-tertiary\" style=\"color:#767676 !important;\">By Amazon Customer on May 7, 2017</span>\r\n				</div>\r\n			</div>\r\n			<div id=\"askInlineAnswersPage-Tx11KNV57FVP0YE-2\" class=\"a-section a-spacing-none\" style=\"margin:0px;padding:0px;\">\r\n				<div class=\"a-section a-spacing-none a-spacing-top-small\" style=\"margin:0px;padding:0px;\">\r\n					<span>no, they can be used indoors and outdoors. There is a switch on the bottom of the solar panel part to turn on</span>&nbsp;<br />\r\n<span class=\"a-color-tertiary\" style=\"color:#767676 !important;\">By Sheri B Lodel on May 7, 2017</span>\r\n				</div>\r\n				<div class=\"a-section a-spacing-none a-spacing-top-small\" style=\"margin:0px;padding:0px;\">\r\n					<span>Mine work indoors, but only if it is almost completely dark, otherwise they shut off after a few seconds.</span>&nbsp;<br />\r\n<span class=\"a-color-tertiary\" style=\"color:#767676 !important;\">By L. Hamilton on May 7, 2017</span>\r\n				</div>\r\n			</div>\r\n</span>\r\n		</div>\r\n	</div>\r\n	<div id=\"question-Tx307GRHY6LIRI9\" class=\"a-fixed-left-grid a-spacing-small\" style=\"margin:0px;padding:0px;\">\r\n		<div class=\"a-fixed-left-grid-inner\" style=\"margin:0px;padding:0px 0px 0px 100px;\">\r\n			<div class=\"a-fixed-left-grid-col a-col-left\" style=\"margin:0px 0px 0px -100px;padding:0px;\">\r\n				<span class=\"a-text-bold\" style=\"font-weight:700 !important;\">Question:</span>\r\n			</div>\r\n			<div class=\"a-fixed-left-grid-col a-col-right\" style=\"margin:0px;padding:0px;\">\r\n				Is the solar panel waterproof like it says the lights are?\r\n			</div>\r\n		</div>\r\n	</div>\r\n	<div class=\"a-fixed-left-grid a-spacing-base\" style=\"margin:0px;padding:0px;\">\r\n		<div class=\"a-fixed-left-grid-inner\" style=\"margin:0px;padding:0px 0px 0px 100px;\">\r\n			<div class=\"a-fixed-left-grid-col a-col-left\" style=\"margin:0px 0px 0px -100px;padding:0px;\">\r\n				<span class=\"a-text-bold\" style=\"font-weight:700 !important;\">Answer:</span>\r\n			</div>\r\n			<div class=\"a-fixed-left-grid-col a-col-right\" style=\"margin:0px;padding:0px;\">\r\n				<span>I have 3 mounted to the roof over my patio. They are exposed to all the elements, so yes.</span>&nbsp;<br />\r\n<span class=\"a-color-tertiary\" style=\"color:#767676 !important;\">By G. Hults on May 14, 2017</span><span class=\"askInlineAnswers\" id=\"Tx307GRHY6LIRI9\">\r\n				<div id=\"askInlineAnswersPage-Tx307GRHY6LIRI9-1\" class=\"a-section a-spacing-none\" style=\"margin:0px;padding:0px;\">\r\n					<div class=\"a-section a-spacing-none a-spacing-top-small\" style=\"margin:0px;padding:0px;\">\r\n						<span>Yes mine are outside have been in heavy rains. It is an ambiance of light . I have the all clear ones I have had many compliments on them.</span>&nbsp;<br />\r\n<span class=\"a-color-tertiary\" style=\"color:#767676 !important;\">By Limee49 on May 14, 2017</span>\r\n					</div>\r\n				</div>\r\n</span>\r\n			</div>\r\n		</div>\r\n	</div>\r\n	<div id=\"question-Tx3Q91521N0C6CI\" class=\"a-fixed-left-grid a-spacing-small\" style=\"margin:0px;padding:0px;\">\r\n		<div class=\"a-fixed-left-grid-inner\" style=\"margin:0px;padding:0px 0px 0px 100px;\">\r\n			<div class=\"a-fixed-left-grid-col a-col-left\" style=\"margin:0px 0px 0px -100px;padding:0px;\">\r\n				<span class=\"a-text-bold\" style=\"font-weight:700 !important;\">Question:</span>\r\n			</div>\r\n			<div class=\"a-fixed-left-grid-col a-col-right\" style=\"margin:0px;padding:0px;\">\r\n				Is their an automatic feature on these lights or do they automatically shut off during the day if you leave on?\r\n			</div>\r\n		</div>\r\n	</div>\r\n	<div class=\"a-fixed-left-grid a-spacing-base\" style=\"margin:0px;padding:0px;\">\r\n		<div class=\"a-fixed-left-grid-inner\" style=\"margin:0px;padding:0px 0px 0px 100px;\">\r\n			<div class=\"a-fixed-left-grid-col a-col-left\" style=\"margin:0px 0px 0px -100px;padding:0px;\">\r\n				<span class=\"a-text-bold\" style=\"font-weight:700 !important;\">Answer:</span>\r\n			</div>\r\n			<div class=\"a-fixed-left-grid-col a-col-right\" style=\"margin:0px;padding:0px;\">\r\n				<span>It turns off during the day</span>&nbsp;<br />\r\n<span class=\"a-color-tertiary\" style=\"color:#767676 !important;\">By Datalink on June 12, 2017</span><span class=\"askInlineAnswers\" id=\"Tx3Q91521N0C6CI\">\r\n				<div id=\"askInlineAnswersPage-Tx3Q91521N0C6CI-1\" class=\"a-section a-spacing-none\" style=\"margin:0px;padding:0px;\">\r\n					<div class=\"a-section a-spacing-none a-spacing-top-small\" style=\"margin:0px;padding:0px;\">\r\n						<span>I hope you are asking the same thing in this question. During daylight hours, the solar battery recharges. The lights during daylight do not come on. At night, they light up. There is an on/off switch on the battery to keep the lights from coming on at night if you do not want the lights to be on at night.</span>&nbsp;<br />\r\n<span class=\"a-color-tertiary\" style=\"color:#767676 !important;\">By Sheri B Lodel on June 12, 2017</span>\r\n					</div>\r\n					<div class=\"a-section a-spacing-none a-spacing-top-small\" style=\"margin:0px;padding:0px;\">\r\n						<span>You can turn off but auto they will one on at dusk off at dawn</span>&nbsp;<br />\r\n<span class=\"a-color-tertiary\" style=\"color:#767676 !important;\">By Limee49 on June 12, 2017</span>\r\n					</div>\r\n				</div>\r\n				<div id=\"askInlineAnswersPage-Tx3Q91521N0C6CI-2\" class=\"a-section a-spacing-none\" style=\"margin:0px;padding:0px;\">\r\n					<div class=\"a-section a-spacing-none a-spacing-top-small\" style=\"margin:0px;padding:0px;\">\r\n						<span>this is solar so it charges during day and runs till energy is depleted has 3 modes for lights but no worries about leaving it on its automatic turn it on and at dusk it comes on</span>&nbsp;<br />\r\n<span class=\"a-color-tertiary\" style=\"color:#767676 !important;\">By linda c on June 12, 2017</span>\r\n					</div>\r\n					<div class=\"a-section a-spacing-none a-spacing-top-small\" style=\"margin:0px;padding:0px;\">\r\n						<span>As long as the button stays on, they will automatically turn on at dusk &amp; off at dawn</span>&nbsp;<br />\r\n<span class=\"a-color-tertiary\" style=\"color:#767676 !important;\">By Redbear on June 12, 2017</span>\r\n					</div>\r\n				</div>\r\n</span>\r\n			</div>\r\n		</div>\r\n	</div>\r\n</div>', 'Multi-Color Party Lights: 40 LED Fairy Butterflies Lighting, Party String Lights Decoration - Qedertek', 'fairy butterflies,fairy lights decoration,butterfly lighting,butterfly party lights,multi-color butterfly fairy lights', 'The solar string lights, 40 LED, butterfly special designed, multi-color. using solar string lights,no utility electricity costs, a smart way to save money, Great to decorate our patio, Also good for holiday celebration decoration.', 'https://www.amazon.com/dp/B01I32E5J8/', '', '0', '0.00', 'http://images.qedertek.com/59707a2bae969', '{\"59707a2bc0455\":\"http:\\/\\/images.qedertek.com\\/59707a2bc0455\",\"59707a2bdbeb1\":\"http:\\/\\/images.qedertek.com\\/59707a2bdbeb1\",\"59707a2bee286\":\"http:\\/\\/images.qedertek.com\\/59707a2bee286\",\"59707a2c288e3\":\"http:\\/\\/images.qedertek.com\\/59707a2c288e3\",\"59707a2c3b5ec\":\"http:\\/\\/images.qedertek.com\\/59707a2c3b5ec\",\"59707a2c4fbac\":\"http:\\/\\/images.qedertek.com\\/59707a2c4fbac\"}', '0', '0', '1', '0.00', '1', '1500543532', '1500543532', '', '0');
INSERT INTO `qe_product` VALUES ('71', '2', 'Solar String Lights Butterfly Lighting 40 LED Warm White', '<div class=\"disclaim\" style=\"font-size:10px;color:#888888;margin:0px 0px 1em;font-family:verdana, arial, helvetica, sans-serif;background-color:#FFFFFF;\">\r\n	Color Name:<span style=\"font-weight:700;\">Warm White</span>\r\n</div>\r\n<p style=\"margin-left:1em;color:#333333;font-family:&quot;font-size:small;background-color:#FFFFFF;\">\r\n	<span style=\"font-weight:700;\">Features</span><br />\r\nPowered by solar, no utility electricity costs, eco-friendly<br />\r\nSpecial butterfly appearance makes your environment looks fantastic, specially suitable for Christmas, Halloween and parties decorations<br />\r\nAutomatic design: Under “ON” state, the lights turns off automatically when the solar panel is on a bright environment and turn on automatically at dark&nbsp;<br />\r\nEasy to operate: 2 switches (ON/OFF), Mode (STEADY ON/FLASHING)<br />\r\n<br />\r\n<span style=\"font-weight:700;\">Specifications</span>&nbsp;<br />\r\nLight color: Warm white&nbsp;<br />\r\nLED Quantity: 40 LED&nbsp;<br />\r\nRechargeable: Ni-MH AA Battery: 1.2V 600mA&nbsp;<br />\r\nSwitch: Power ON/OFF, MODE&nbsp;<br />\r\nLighting Mode: Steady On and 7 Blinking modes&nbsp;<br />\r\nSolar Panel: 2V 100mA&nbsp;<br />\r\nCharging Time: 6 hours&nbsp;<br />\r\nLight Length: 24.6ft (7.5m)&nbsp;<br />\r\nLength between 2 blubs: 0.5ft (0.15m)&nbsp;<br />\r\nLength from Solar panel to first stake: 4.9ft(1.5m)&nbsp;<br />\r\nSolar panel with ground stake (8in) for easily positioning&nbsp;<br />\r\n<br />\r\n<span style=\"font-weight:700;\">Warm tips</span>&nbsp;<br />\r\nIt is suggested that the solar panel be fully charged for 8hrs at the first use.&nbsp;<br />\r\n<br />\r\n<span style=\"font-weight:700;\">Package include</span>&nbsp;<br />\r\n1 x Qedertek Solar String Lights&nbsp;&nbsp;<br />\r\n1 x Solar Panel with Ground Stake&nbsp;&nbsp;<br />\r\n1 x User Instruction\r\n</p>', '<ul class=\"a-unordered-list a-vertical a-spacing-none\" style=\"color:#949494;font-family:&quot;font-size:13px;background-color:#FFFFFF;\">\r\n	<li>\r\n		<span class=\"a-list-item\" style=\"color:#111111;\">LIGHTING SENSOR TECHNOLOGY - Solar panels and rechargeable battery, charge under sunshine and turn on at dusk automatically</span>\r\n	</li>\r\n	<li>\r\n		<span class=\"a-list-item\" style=\"color:#111111;\">SUPER LONG WORKING TIME - Illuminates up to 8 hours at night if the panel absorbs enough sunshine during the day</span>\r\n	</li>\r\n	<li>\r\n		<span class=\"a-list-item\" style=\"color:#111111;\">2 SWITCH BUTTONS - Power ON/OFF&amp;Mode switches (8 different modes)</span>\r\n	</li>\r\n	<li>\r\n		<span class=\"a-list-item\" style=\"color:#111111;\">WATERPROOF LIGHTS - Can withstand all kinds of weather, including heavy rain and snow, perfect for indoor and outdoor decorations</span>\r\n	</li>\r\n	<li>\r\n		<span class=\"a-list-item\" style=\"color:#111111;\">SUITABLE FOR ALL DECORATIONS - These wonderful string lights illuminate during night, adding warm and charming atmosphere to your gardens, patio, lawn, porch, gate, yard, etc</span>\r\n	</li>\r\n</ul>', '<div id=\"question-Tx11KNV57FVP0YE\" class=\"a-fixed-left-grid a-spacing-small\" style=\"margin:0px;padding:0px;font-family:verdana, arial, helvetica, sans-serif;color:#111111;font-size:13px;background-color:#FFFFFF;\">\r\n	<div class=\"a-fixed-left-grid-inner\" style=\"margin:0px;padding:0px 0px 0px 100px;\">\r\n		<div class=\"a-fixed-left-grid-col a-col-left\" style=\"margin:0px 0px 0px -100px;padding:0px;\">\r\n			<span class=\"a-text-bold\" style=\"font-weight:700 !important;\">Question:</span>\r\n		</div>\r\n		<div class=\"a-fixed-left-grid-col a-col-right\" style=\"margin:0px;padding:0px;\">\r\n			So far I have not gotten them to turn on. I hung them indoors and placed the solar panel at the window. Can they only be used outside?\r\n		</div>\r\n	</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div class=\"a-fixed-left-grid a-spacing-base\" style=\"margin:0px;padding:0px;font-family:verdana, arial, helvetica, sans-serif;color:#111111;font-size:13px;background-color:#FFFFFF;\">\r\n	<div class=\"a-fixed-left-grid-inner\" style=\"margin:0px;padding:0px 0px 0px 100px;\">\r\n		<div class=\"a-fixed-left-grid-col a-col-left\" style=\"margin:0px 0px 0px -100px;padding:0px;\">\r\n			<span class=\"a-text-bold\" style=\"font-weight:700 !important;\">Answer:</span>\r\n		</div>\r\n		<div class=\"a-fixed-left-grid-col a-col-right\" style=\"margin:0px;padding:0px;\">\r\n			<span>They don\'t work indoors because I tried that first. Once I put them outside in the sun on my porch they turn on automatically at dusk every nite. I love them very pretty.</span>&nbsp;<br />\r\n<span class=\"a-color-tertiary\" style=\"color:#767676 !important;\">By colleen w on May 7, 2017</span><span class=\"askInlineAnswers\" id=\"Tx11KNV57FVP0YE\">\r\n			<div id=\"askInlineAnswersPage-Tx11KNV57FVP0YE-1\" class=\"a-section a-spacing-none\" style=\"margin:0px;padding:0px;\">\r\n				<div class=\"a-section a-spacing-none a-spacing-top-small\" style=\"margin:0px;padding:0px;\">\r\n					<span class=\"askExpanderContainer askExpanderExpanded\">They are solar powered, but if you put the solar panel at the widow, it should work, but you\'d better make sure that the lights in your room do not illuminate the solar panel(solar panel should be covered), cause the solar panel is light sensor, if it were light up at night, the lights strands will not work. Hope this help, thanks!&nbsp;</span><br />\r\n<span class=\"a-color-tertiary\" style=\"color:#767676 !important;\">By Holigoo Direct&nbsp;on May 12, 2017</span>\r\n				</div>\r\n				<div class=\"a-section a-spacing-none a-spacing-top-small\" style=\"margin:0px;padding:0px;\">\r\n					<span>Mine are outside and so fine</span>&nbsp;<br />\r\n<span class=\"a-color-tertiary\" style=\"color:#767676 !important;\">By Amazon Customer on May 7, 2017</span>\r\n				</div>\r\n			</div>\r\n			<div id=\"askInlineAnswersPage-Tx11KNV57FVP0YE-2\" class=\"a-section a-spacing-none\" style=\"margin:0px;padding:0px;\">\r\n				<div class=\"a-section a-spacing-none a-spacing-top-small\" style=\"margin:0px;padding:0px;\">\r\n					<span>no, they can be used indoors and outdoors. There is a switch on the bottom of the solar panel part to turn on</span>&nbsp;<br />\r\n<span class=\"a-color-tertiary\" style=\"color:#767676 !important;\">By Sheri B Lodel on May 7, 2017</span>\r\n				</div>\r\n				<div class=\"a-section a-spacing-none a-spacing-top-small\" style=\"margin:0px;padding:0px;\">\r\n					<span>Mine work indoors, but only if it is almost completely dark, otherwise they shut off after a few seconds.</span>&nbsp;<br />\r\n<span class=\"a-color-tertiary\" style=\"color:#767676 !important;\">By L. Hamilton on May 7, 2017</span>\r\n				</div>\r\n			</div>\r\n</span>\r\n		</div>\r\n	</div>\r\n	<div id=\"question-Tx307GRHY6LIRI9\" class=\"a-fixed-left-grid a-spacing-small\" style=\"margin:0px;padding:0px;\">\r\n		<div class=\"a-fixed-left-grid-inner\" style=\"margin:0px;padding:0px 0px 0px 100px;\">\r\n			<div class=\"a-fixed-left-grid-col a-col-left\" style=\"margin:0px 0px 0px -100px;padding:0px;\">\r\n				<span class=\"a-text-bold\" style=\"font-weight:700 !important;\">Question:</span>\r\n			</div>\r\n			<div class=\"a-fixed-left-grid-col a-col-right\" style=\"margin:0px;padding:0px;\">\r\n				Is the solar panel waterproof like it says the lights are?\r\n			</div>\r\n		</div>\r\n	</div>\r\n	<div class=\"a-fixed-left-grid a-spacing-base\" style=\"margin:0px;padding:0px;\">\r\n		<div class=\"a-fixed-left-grid-inner\" style=\"margin:0px;padding:0px 0px 0px 100px;\">\r\n			<div class=\"a-fixed-left-grid-col a-col-left\" style=\"margin:0px 0px 0px -100px;padding:0px;\">\r\n				<span class=\"a-text-bold\" style=\"font-weight:700 !important;\">Answer:</span>\r\n			</div>\r\n			<div class=\"a-fixed-left-grid-col a-col-right\" style=\"margin:0px;padding:0px;\">\r\n				<span>I have 3 mounted to the roof over my patio. They are exposed to all the elements, so yes.</span>&nbsp;<br />\r\n<span class=\"a-color-tertiary\" style=\"color:#767676 !important;\">By G. Hults on May 14, 2017</span><span class=\"askInlineAnswers\" id=\"Tx307GRHY6LIRI9\">\r\n				<div id=\"askInlineAnswersPage-Tx307GRHY6LIRI9-1\" class=\"a-section a-spacing-none\" style=\"margin:0px;padding:0px;\">\r\n					<div class=\"a-section a-spacing-none a-spacing-top-small\" style=\"margin:0px;padding:0px;\">\r\n						<span>Yes mine are outside have been in heavy rains. It is an ambiance of light . I have the all clear ones I have had many compliments on them.</span>&nbsp;<br />\r\n<span class=\"a-color-tertiary\" style=\"color:#767676 !important;\">By Limee49 on May 14, 2017</span>\r\n					</div>\r\n				</div>\r\n</span>\r\n			</div>\r\n		</div>\r\n	</div>\r\n	<div id=\"question-Tx3Q91521N0C6CI\" class=\"a-fixed-left-grid a-spacing-small\" style=\"margin:0px;padding:0px;\">\r\n		<div class=\"a-fixed-left-grid-inner\" style=\"margin:0px;padding:0px 0px 0px 100px;\">\r\n			<div class=\"a-fixed-left-grid-col a-col-left\" style=\"margin:0px 0px 0px -100px;padding:0px;\">\r\n				<span class=\"a-text-bold\" style=\"font-weight:700 !important;\">Question:</span>\r\n			</div>\r\n			<div class=\"a-fixed-left-grid-col a-col-right\" style=\"margin:0px;padding:0px;\">\r\n				Is their an automatic feature on these lights or do they automatically shut off during the day if you leave on?\r\n			</div>\r\n		</div>\r\n	</div>\r\n	<div class=\"a-fixed-left-grid a-spacing-base\" style=\"margin:0px;padding:0px;\">\r\n		<div class=\"a-fixed-left-grid-inner\" style=\"margin:0px;padding:0px 0px 0px 100px;\">\r\n			<div class=\"a-fixed-left-grid-col a-col-left\" style=\"margin:0px 0px 0px -100px;padding:0px;\">\r\n				<span class=\"a-text-bold\" style=\"font-weight:700 !important;\">Answer:</span>\r\n			</div>\r\n			<div class=\"a-fixed-left-grid-col a-col-right\" style=\"margin:0px;padding:0px;\">\r\n				<span>It turns off during the day</span>&nbsp;<br />\r\n<span class=\"a-color-tertiary\" style=\"color:#767676 !important;\">By Datalink on June 12, 2017</span><span class=\"askInlineAnswers\" id=\"Tx3Q91521N0C6CI\">\r\n				<div id=\"askInlineAnswersPage-Tx3Q91521N0C6CI-1\" class=\"a-section a-spacing-none\" style=\"margin:0px;padding:0px;\">\r\n					<div class=\"a-section a-spacing-none a-spacing-top-small\" style=\"margin:0px;padding:0px;\">\r\n						<span>I hope you are asking the same thing in this question. During daylight hours, the solar battery recharges. The lights during daylight do not come on. At night, they light up. There is an on/off switch on the battery to keep the lights from coming on at night if you do not want the lights to be on at night.</span>&nbsp;<br />\r\n<span class=\"a-color-tertiary\" style=\"color:#767676 !important;\">By Sheri B Lodel on June 12, 2017</span>\r\n					</div>\r\n					<div class=\"a-section a-spacing-none a-spacing-top-small\" style=\"margin:0px;padding:0px;\">\r\n						<span>You can turn off but auto they will one on at dusk off at dawn</span>&nbsp;<br />\r\n<span class=\"a-color-tertiary\" style=\"color:#767676 !important;\">By Limee49 on June 12, 2017</span>\r\n					</div>\r\n				</div>\r\n				<div id=\"askInlineAnswersPage-Tx3Q91521N0C6CI-2\" class=\"a-section a-spacing-none\" style=\"margin:0px;padding:0px;\">\r\n					<div class=\"a-section a-spacing-none a-spacing-top-small\" style=\"margin:0px;padding:0px;\">\r\n						<span>this is solar so it charges during day and runs till energy is depleted has 3 modes for lights but no worries about leaving it on its automatic turn it on and at dusk it comes on</span>&nbsp;<br />\r\n<span class=\"a-color-tertiary\" style=\"color:#767676 !important;\">By linda c on June 12, 2017</span>\r\n					</div>\r\n					<div class=\"a-section a-spacing-none a-spacing-top-small\" style=\"margin:0px;padding:0px;\">\r\n						<span>As long as the button stays on, they will automatically turn on at dusk &amp; off at dawn</span>&nbsp;<br />\r\n<span class=\"a-color-tertiary\" style=\"color:#767676 !important;\">By Redbear on June 12, 2017</span>\r\n					</div>\r\n				</div>\r\n</span>\r\n			</div>\r\n		</div>\r\n	</div>\r\n</div>', 'Lighting Decor,40 LED Warm White Butterfly String Lights,Solar Light Strings - Qedertek', 'butterfly solar lights,butterfly light strings,warm white butterfly light strings,solar butterfly string lighting', 'This warm white lighting strings, 40 LED, solar powered, cute butterfly appearance designed, widely use for holiday parties, Christmas and Halloween decorations, also great for children\'s room decorating.', 'https://www.amazon.com/dp/B01I32E8KE/', '', '0', '0.00', 'http://images.qedertek.com/59707b2a12900', '{\"59707b2a2fc66\":\"http:\\/\\/images.qedertek.com\\/59707b2a2fc66\",\"59707b2a3f466\":\"http:\\/\\/images.qedertek.com\\/59707b2a3f466\",\"59707b2a517c1\":\"http:\\/\\/images.qedertek.com\\/59707b2a517c1\",\"59707b2a65faf\":\"http:\\/\\/images.qedertek.com\\/59707b2a65faf\",\"59707b2a78aa9\":\"http:\\/\\/images.qedertek.com\\/59707b2a78aa9\"}', '0', '0', '1', '0.00', '1', '1500543786', '1500543786', '', '0');
INSERT INTO `qe_product` VALUES ('72', '2', 'Solar Bell String Fairy Lights 40 LED Decorative Lighting Pink', '<div class=\"disclaim\" style=\"font-size:10px;color:#888888;margin:0px 0px 1em;font-family:verdana, arial, helvetica, sans-serif;background-color:#FFFFFF;\">\r\n	Color Name:<span style=\"font-weight:700;\">Pink</span>\r\n</div>\r\n<p style=\"margin-left:1em;color:#333333;font-family:&quot;font-size:small;background-color:#FFFFFF;\">\r\n	<span style=\"font-weight:700;\">Features</span>&nbsp;<br />\r\nSolar powered string lights, electicity utility cost, environment-friendly&nbsp;<br />\r\nSolar Panel charges sunlight in the daylight and store the energy in the batteries to power the lights at night&nbsp;<br />\r\nIP65 Waterproof, suitable for indoor and outdoor decoration&nbsp;<br />\r\nSpecial jingle bell design LED lights bring you a fresh and pleasant atmosphere at night&nbsp;<br />\r\nFlexible string lights allows you to DIY many decorations scene such as Christmas party, bar, restaurant, etc.&nbsp;<br />\r\n<br />\r\n<span style=\"font-weight:700;\">Specifications</span>&nbsp;<br />\r\nLight color: Pink&nbsp;<br />\r\nSetting: Indoor/Outdoor&nbsp;<br />\r\nLED Quantity: 40 LED&nbsp;<br />\r\nSolar Panel: 2V/100mA&nbsp;<br />\r\nBattery type: Rechargeable 600mAH NI-MH Battery&nbsp;<br />\r\nLight source: LED&nbsp;<br />\r\nSwitch: ON/OFF, MODE&nbsp;<br />\r\nWorking mode: Flash/Steady on&nbsp;<br />\r\nCharging time: 6-8hrs&nbsp;<br />\r\nLight length: 24ft(7.3m)&nbsp;<br />\r\nLength between 2 blubs:0.49ft(0.15m)&nbsp;<br />\r\nLength from Solar panel to first stake: 4.9ft(1.5m)&nbsp;<br />\r\n<br />\r\n<span style=\"font-weight:700;\">What\'s in the box</span>&nbsp;<br />\r\n1 x Qedertek 40 LED Bell Solar String Lights&nbsp;<br />\r\n1 x Solar Panel with Ground Stake&nbsp;<br />\r\n1 x User Instruction\r\n</p>', '<ul class=\"a-unordered-list a-vertical a-spacing-none\" style=\"color:#949494;font-family:&quot;font-size:13px;background-color:#FFFFFF;\">\r\n	<li>\r\n		<span class=\"a-list-item\" style=\"color:#111111;\">Cute bell shape string lights light up at night, ideal for decorating your garden, patio, lawn, porches, doors, patios, etc.</span>\r\n	</li>\r\n	<li>\r\n		<span class=\"a-list-item\" style=\"color:#111111;\">Solar operated, Powered by solar energy with built-in NI-MH AA rechargeable battery solar panel, energy saving and eco-friendly</span>\r\n	</li>\r\n	<li>\r\n		<span class=\"a-list-item\" style=\"color:#111111;\">Lighting sensor technology, the string lights will automatically turn on at dusk and turn off at dawn</span>\r\n	</li>\r\n	<li>\r\n		<span class=\"a-list-item\" style=\"color:#111111;\">Super Long Working Time, Up to 8 hours of continuous lighting when it is fully charged</span>\r\n	</li>\r\n	<li>\r\n		<span class=\"a-list-item\" style=\"color:#111111;\">Two buttons controll design, Power ON/OFF and MODE switch, easy operation</span>\r\n	</li>\r\n</ul>', '', '40 LED Bell Decorative Lighting | Pink Solar Fairy Lights Living Room, Bedroom - Qedertek', 'fairy lights living room,decorative fairy lights bedroom,pink fairy lights,solar led fairy lights pink,40 led bell decorative lighting', 'Wanna to shop living room, bedroom fairy lights online, Qedertek is a professional decorative string lights supplier, solar powered 40 led pink bell decorative lighting would be your best choice.', 'https://www.amazon.com/dp/B01I32EF7U/', '', '0', '0.00', 'http://images.qedertek.com/59707e1e94b6f', '{\"59707e1f2da22\":\"http:\\/\\/images.qedertek.com\\/59707e1f2da22\",\"59707e1f495b5\":\"http:\\/\\/images.qedertek.com\\/59707e1f495b5\",\"59707e1f6555c\":\"http:\\/\\/images.qedertek.com\\/59707e1f6555c\",\"59707e1f7731c\":\"http:\\/\\/images.qedertek.com\\/59707e1f7731c\",\"59707e1f8a0cd\":\"http:\\/\\/images.qedertek.com\\/59707e1f8a0cd\"}', '0', '0', '1', '0.00', '1', '1500544543', '1500544543', '', '0');
INSERT INTO `qe_product` VALUES ('73', '4', 'Battery Operated String Lights 50 LED 8 Modes Multi Color', '<div class=\"disclaim\" style=\"font-size:10px;color:#888888;margin:0px 0px 1em;font-family:verdana, arial, helvetica, sans-serif;background-color:#FFFFFF;\">\r\n	Color Name:<span style=\"font-weight:700;\">Multi color</span> \r\n</div>\r\n<p style=\"margin-left:1em;color:#333333;font-family:&quot;font-size:small;background-color:#FFFFFF;\">\r\n	<span style=\"font-weight:700;\">Qedertek is a brand registered in USA which is specialized in LED products.</span><br />\r\n<span style=\"font-weight:700;\">Products Features:&nbsp;</span><br />\r\n1. perfectly consistent with a variety of decoration, creating a starry fairy scene.&nbsp;<br />\r\n2. High-brightness string light, but not dazzling.&nbsp;<br />\r\n3. Safe, power-saving and low cost.&nbsp;<br />\r\n4. Waterproof, Suitable for indoor and outdoor, A perfect decoration for Valentine\'s Day, Christmas, Party, Wedding, etc.&nbsp;<br />\r\n5. Timer includes eight modes: Combination(In turn change the mode between 2-8),In Waves, Sequential, Slo Glo, Chasing/Flash, Slow Fade, Twinkle/Flash, Steady On, And all modes have a time control function 6 hours \"\"ON\"\" and 18 hours \"\"OFF\"\".&nbsp;<br />\r\n<br />\r\n<span style=\"font-weight:700;\">Specification:&nbsp;</span><br />\r\n1. Light color:Multi Color&nbsp;<br />\r\n2. Battery: 3 x C size 1.5 V (not included)&nbsp;<br />\r\n3. Cable length: 4m/13.1ft, lead length 30cm/1ft, lamp spacing 7.7cm/0.25ft&nbsp;<br />\r\n4. Working time: Steady state can work a month, LED total working time more than 10,000 hours&nbsp;<br />\r\n6. LED quantity: 50pcs, 50 LED at 7.7CM/0.25ft spacing&nbsp;<br />\r\n7. Light modes: 8 models Eight kinds of mode automatically transform(Need to press the switch by hand to convert one light mode; you can press it several times for which mode you want).\r\n</p>', '<ul class=\"a-unordered-list a-vertical a-spacing-none\" style=\"color:#949494;font-family:&quot;font-size:13px;background-color:#FFFFFF;\">\r\n	<li>\r\n		<span class=\"a-list-item\" style=\"color:#111111;\">No power cord or socket required. Battery operated (not included) LED string lights allow you to decorate indoor/outdoor without any household power supply.</span> \r\n	</li>\r\n	<li>\r\n		<span class=\"a-list-item\" style=\"color:#111111;\">8 Setting controller with memory chip includes:Combination, In Waves,Sequential,Slo Glo,Chasing / Flash,Slow Fade, Twinkle / Flash, Steady On.</span> \r\n	</li>\r\n	<li>\r\n		<span class=\"a-list-item\" style=\"color:#111111;\">Total length 4m/13.1ft, lead length 30cm/1ft, lamp spacing 7.7cm/0.25ft.</span> \r\n	</li>\r\n	<li>\r\n		<span class=\"a-list-item\" style=\"color:#111111;\">Perfect decoration for Valentine\'s Day, Christmas, Party and other celebration occasions, it can be easily put or hung on walls, windows, doors, floors, trees, grasses etc.</span> \r\n	</li>\r\n	<li>\r\n		<span class=\"a-list-item\" style=\"color:#111111;\">Any quality problems about the product, please contact us first.</span> \r\n	</li>\r\n</ul>', '<div id=\"question-Tx18C7QALKOYPA8\" class=\"a-fixed-left-grid a-spacing-small\" style=\"color:#111111;font-family:verdana, arial, helvetica, sans-serif;font-size:13px;background-color:#FFFFFF;\">\r\n	<div class=\"a-fixed-left-grid-inner\" style=\"padding:0px 0px 0px 100px;\">\r\n		<div class=\"a-fixed-left-grid-col a-col-left\" style=\"margin-left:-100px;\">\r\n			<span class=\"a-text-bold\" style=\"font-weight:700 !important;\">Question:</span> \r\n		</div>\r\n		<div class=\"a-fixed-left-grid-col a-col-right\">\r\n			Is this item available in clear lights\r\n		</div>\r\n	</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div class=\"a-fixed-left-grid a-spacing-base\" style=\"color:#111111;font-family:verdana, arial, helvetica, sans-serif;font-size:13px;background-color:#FFFFFF;\">\r\n	<div class=\"a-fixed-left-grid-inner\" style=\"padding:0px 0px 0px 100px;\">\r\n		<div class=\"a-fixed-left-grid-col a-col-left\" style=\"margin-left:-100px;\">\r\n			<span class=\"a-text-bold\" style=\"font-weight:700 !important;\">Answer:</span> \r\n		</div>\r\n		<div class=\"a-fixed-left-grid-col a-col-right\">\r\n			<span>Yes, available in different styles and colors. Simply click on \"Qedertek\" under the product name, or search amazon for \"Qedertek\" and you will see they have a multitude of options.</span>&nbsp;<br />\r\n<span class=\"a-color-tertiary\" style=\"color:#767676 !important;\">By Amazon Customer on December 7, 2016</span> \r\n		</div>\r\n	</div>\r\n	<div id=\"question-Tx1MVINKELXKYGS\" class=\"a-fixed-left-grid a-spacing-small\" style=\"color:#111111;font-family:verdana, arial, helvetica, sans-serif;font-size:13px;background-color:#FFFFFF;\">\r\n		<div class=\"a-fixed-left-grid-inner\" style=\"padding:0px 0px 0px 100px;\">\r\n			<div class=\"a-fixed-left-grid-col a-col-left\" style=\"margin-left:-100px;\">\r\n				<span class=\"a-text-bold\" style=\"font-weight:700 !important;\">Question:</span> \r\n			</div>\r\n			<div class=\"a-fixed-left-grid-col a-col-right\">\r\n				How many actual bulbs are there?\r\n			</div>\r\n		</div>\r\n	</div>\r\n	<div class=\"a-fixed-left-grid a-spacing-base\" style=\"color:#111111;font-family:verdana, arial, helvetica, sans-serif;font-size:13px;background-color:#FFFFFF;\">\r\n		<div class=\"a-fixed-left-grid-inner\" style=\"padding:0px 0px 0px 100px;\">\r\n			<div class=\"a-fixed-left-grid-col a-col-left\" style=\"margin-left:-100px;\">\r\n				<span class=\"a-text-bold\" style=\"font-weight:700 !important;\">Answer:</span> \r\n			</div>\r\n			<div class=\"a-fixed-left-grid-col a-col-right\">\r\n				<span>Fifty</span>&nbsp;<br />\r\n<span class=\"a-color-tertiary\" style=\"color:#767676 !important;\">By Derrek on October 26, 2016</span><span class=\"askInlineAnswers\" id=\"Tx1MVINKELXKYGS\"> \r\n				<div id=\"askInlineAnswersPage-Tx1MVINKELXKYGS-1\" class=\"a-section a-spacing-none\">\r\n					<div class=\"a-section a-spacing-none a-spacing-top-small\">\r\n						<span>Hi! There are 50 bulbs on it. They are actually super bright! :)</span>&nbsp;<br />\r\n<span class=\"a-color-tertiary\" style=\"color:#767676 !important;\">By desiree jones on October 26, 2016</span> \r\n					</div>\r\n				</div>\r\n</span> \r\n			</div>\r\n		</div>\r\n	</div>\r\n	<div id=\"question-Tx1NKAQE0R98DQB\" class=\"a-fixed-left-grid a-spacing-small\" style=\"color:#111111;font-family:verdana, arial, helvetica, sans-serif;font-size:13px;background-color:#FFFFFF;\">\r\n		<div class=\"a-fixed-left-grid-inner\" style=\"padding:0px 0px 0px 100px;\">\r\n			<div class=\"a-fixed-left-grid-col a-col-left\" style=\"margin-left:-100px;\">\r\n				<span class=\"a-text-bold\" style=\"font-weight:700 !important;\">Question:</span> \r\n			</div>\r\n			<div class=\"a-fixed-left-grid-col a-col-right\">\r\n				Do these lights turn off automatically? The other battery operated lights I had turned off automatically several hours later like an auto timer.\r\n			</div>\r\n		</div>\r\n	</div>\r\n	<div class=\"a-fixed-left-grid a-spacing-base\" style=\"color:#111111;font-family:verdana, arial, helvetica, sans-serif;font-size:13px;background-color:#FFFFFF;\">\r\n		<div class=\"a-fixed-left-grid-inner\" style=\"padding:0px 0px 0px 100px;\">\r\n			<div class=\"a-fixed-left-grid-col a-col-left\" style=\"margin-left:-100px;\">\r\n				<span class=\"a-text-bold\" style=\"font-weight:700 !important;\">Answer:</span> \r\n			</div>\r\n			<div class=\"a-fixed-left-grid-col a-col-right\">\r\n				<span>yes they do</span>&nbsp;<br />\r\n<span class=\"a-color-tertiary\" style=\"color:#767676 !important;\">By Ruth H. on November 3, 2016</span><span class=\"askInlineAnswers\" id=\"Tx1NKAQE0R98DQB\"> \r\n				<div id=\"askInlineAnswersPage-Tx1NKAQE0R98DQB-1\" class=\"a-section a-spacing-none\">\r\n					<div class=\"a-section a-spacing-none a-spacing-top-small\">\r\n						<span>Not that I know of. They have a button that turns them on and off. I had them on for about 3 hours and they didn\'t shut off.</span>&nbsp;<br />\r\n<span class=\"a-color-tertiary\" style=\"color:#767676 !important;\">By Right? on November 3, 2016</span> \r\n					</div>\r\n					<div class=\"a-section a-spacing-none a-spacing-top-small\">\r\n						<span>I thought the battery had died 2-3 hours in, but I believe that is exactly what it was. Turned them back on and it kept on working!</span>&nbsp;<br />\r\n<span class=\"a-color-tertiary\" style=\"color:#767676 !important;\">By ARincon64 on November 4, 2016</span> \r\n					</div>\r\n					<div class=\"a-section a-spacing-none a-spacing-top-small\">\r\n						<span>Yes they do 6 hours in</span>&nbsp;<br />\r\n<span class=\"a-color-tertiary\" style=\"color:#767676 !important;\">By Donna on November 30, 2016</span> \r\n					</div>\r\n				</div>\r\n</span> \r\n			</div>\r\n		</div>\r\n	</div>\r\n	<div id=\"question-Tx1V9LAKDWSB6US\" class=\"a-fixed-left-grid a-spacing-small\" style=\"color:#111111;font-family:verdana, arial, helvetica, sans-serif;font-size:13px;background-color:#FFFFFF;\">\r\n		<div class=\"a-fixed-left-grid-inner\" style=\"padding:0px 0px 0px 100px;\">\r\n			<div class=\"a-fixed-left-grid-col a-col-left\" style=\"margin-left:-100px;\">\r\n				<span class=\"a-text-bold\" style=\"font-weight:700 !important;\">Question:</span> \r\n			</div>\r\n			<div class=\"a-fixed-left-grid-col a-col-right\">\r\n				What color bulbs are included in this multi set?\r\n			</div>\r\n		</div>\r\n	</div>\r\n	<div class=\"a-fixed-left-grid a-spacing-base\" style=\"color:#111111;font-family:verdana, arial, helvetica, sans-serif;font-size:13px;background-color:#FFFFFF;\">\r\n		<div class=\"a-fixed-left-grid-inner\" style=\"padding:0px 0px 0px 100px;\">\r\n			<div class=\"a-fixed-left-grid-col a-col-left\" style=\"margin-left:-100px;\">\r\n				<span class=\"a-text-bold\" style=\"font-weight:700 !important;\">Answer:</span> \r\n			</div>\r\n			<div class=\"a-fixed-left-grid-col a-col-right\">\r\n				<span>The bulbs are blue,red,green,purple and orange. All very pretty.</span>&nbsp;<br />\r\n<span class=\"a-color-tertiary\" style=\"color:#767676 !important;\">By Gari Cominiello on November 25, 2016</span> \r\n			</div>\r\n		</div>\r\n	</div>\r\n	<div id=\"question-Tx201I0VDYSEPEY\" class=\"a-fixed-left-grid a-spacing-small\" style=\"color:#111111;font-family:verdana, arial, helvetica, sans-serif;font-size:13px;background-color:#FFFFFF;\">\r\n		<div class=\"a-fixed-left-grid-inner\" style=\"padding:0px 0px 0px 100px;\">\r\n			<div class=\"a-fixed-left-grid-col a-col-left\" style=\"margin-left:-100px;\">\r\n				<span class=\"a-text-bold\" style=\"font-weight:700 !important;\">Question:</span> \r\n			</div>\r\n			<div class=\"a-fixed-left-grid-col a-col-right\">\r\n				Are the lights glass bulbs? Or, plastic?\r\n			</div>\r\n		</div>\r\n	</div>\r\n	<div class=\"a-fixed-left-grid a-spacing-base\" style=\"color:#111111;font-family:verdana, arial, helvetica, sans-serif;font-size:13px;background-color:#FFFFFF;\">\r\n		<div class=\"a-fixed-left-grid-inner\" style=\"padding:0px 0px 0px 100px;\">\r\n			<div class=\"a-fixed-left-grid-col a-col-left\" style=\"margin-left:-100px;\">\r\n				<span class=\"a-text-bold\" style=\"font-weight:700 !important;\">Answer:</span> \r\n			</div>\r\n			<div class=\"a-fixed-left-grid-col a-col-right\">\r\n				<span>Plastic I believe- we put them on a tree outside and they look very nice</span>&nbsp;<br />\r\n<span class=\"a-color-tertiary\" style=\"color:#767676 !important;\">By Bonnie A. on December 20, 2016</span><span class=\"askInlineAnswers\" id=\"Tx201I0VDYSEPEY\"> \r\n				<div id=\"askInlineAnswersPage-Tx201I0VDYSEPEY-1\" class=\"a-section a-spacing-none\">\r\n					<div class=\"a-section a-spacing-none a-spacing-top-small\">\r\n						<span>Plastic</span>&nbsp;<br />\r\n<span class=\"a-color-tertiary\" style=\"color:#767676 !important;\">By sinnin13 on December 20, 2016</span> \r\n					</div>\r\n					<div class=\"a-section a-spacing-none a-spacing-top-small\">\r\n						<span>Dear Grace, thank you for your question. The lights are all LED lights, and the bulbs are plastic material.</span>&nbsp;<br />\r\n<span class=\"a-color-tertiary\" style=\"color:#767676 !important;\">By Icicle Direct&nbsp;on December 21, 2016</span> \r\n					</div>\r\n				</div>\r\n</span> \r\n			</div>\r\n		</div>\r\n	</div>\r\n	<div id=\"question-Tx20OYSM3A0Z0C6\" class=\"a-fixed-left-grid a-spacing-small\" style=\"color:#111111;font-family:verdana, arial, helvetica, sans-serif;font-size:13px;background-color:#FFFFFF;\">\r\n		<div class=\"a-fixed-left-grid-inner\" style=\"padding:0px 0px 0px 100px;\">\r\n			<div class=\"a-fixed-left-grid-col a-col-left\" style=\"margin-left:-100px;\">\r\n				<span class=\"a-text-bold\" style=\"font-weight:700 !important;\">Question:</span> \r\n			</div>\r\n			<div class=\"a-fixed-left-grid-col a-col-right\">\r\n				Do any of the modes offer various bulbs twinkling on and off at different times,using in a custom jewelry box &amp; need effect of twinkling stars?\r\n			</div>\r\n		</div>\r\n	</div>\r\n	<div class=\"a-fixed-left-grid a-spacing-base\" style=\"color:#111111;font-family:verdana, arial, helvetica, sans-serif;font-size:13px;background-color:#FFFFFF;\">\r\n		<div class=\"a-fixed-left-grid-inner\" style=\"padding:0px 0px 0px 100px;\">\r\n			<div class=\"a-fixed-left-grid-col a-col-left\" style=\"margin-left:-100px;\">\r\n				<span class=\"a-text-bold\" style=\"font-weight:700 !important;\">Answer:</span> \r\n			</div>\r\n			<div class=\"a-fixed-left-grid-col a-col-right\">\r\n				<span>There are different modes however there is no timer or anything.. you would need to set it to the twinkle you want. Really happy with the purchase myself though! I use them in the office at my cubicle :)</span>&nbsp;<br />\r\n<span class=\"a-color-tertiary\" style=\"color:#767676 !important;\">By Brittany Hilliard on May 7, 2017</span> \r\n			</div>\r\n		</div>\r\n	</div>\r\n	<div id=\"question-Tx2UI3DXK4TOOHK\" class=\"a-fixed-left-grid a-spacing-small\" style=\"color:#111111;font-family:verdana, arial, helvetica, sans-serif;font-size:13px;background-color:#FFFFFF;\">\r\n		<div class=\"a-fixed-left-grid-inner\" style=\"padding:0px 0px 0px 100px;\">\r\n			<div class=\"a-fixed-left-grid-col a-col-left\" style=\"margin-left:-100px;\">\r\n				<span class=\"a-text-bold\" style=\"font-weight:700 !important;\">Question:</span> \r\n			</div>\r\n			<div class=\"a-fixed-left-grid-col a-col-right\">\r\n				Does the mode stay on after they turn off or do you need to reset it every day?\r\n			</div>\r\n		</div>\r\n	</div>\r\n	<div class=\"a-fixed-left-grid a-spacing-base\" style=\"color:#111111;font-family:verdana, arial, helvetica, sans-serif;font-size:13px;background-color:#FFFFFF;\">\r\n		<div class=\"a-fixed-left-grid-inner\" style=\"padding:0px 0px 0px 100px;\">\r\n			<div class=\"a-fixed-left-grid-col a-col-left\" style=\"margin-left:-100px;\">\r\n				<span class=\"a-text-bold\" style=\"font-weight:700 !important;\">Answer:</span> \r\n			</div>\r\n			<div class=\"a-fixed-left-grid-col a-col-right\">\r\n				<span>They shuffle through modes.. one of the modes is \"off\"</span>&nbsp;<br />\r\n<span class=\"a-color-tertiary\" style=\"color:#767676 !important;\">By Brittany Hilliard on December 30, 2016</span><span class=\"askInlineAnswers\" id=\"Tx2UI3DXK4TOOHK\"> \r\n				<div id=\"askInlineAnswersPage-Tx2UI3DXK4TOOHK-1\" class=\"a-section a-spacing-none\">\r\n					<div class=\"a-section a-spacing-none a-spacing-top-small\">\r\n						<span>There are several settings, all you have to do is press the button to select the mode. If you want mode 3 press 3 times off is like 8</span>&nbsp;<br />\r\n<span class=\"a-color-tertiary\" style=\"color:#767676 !important;\">By Old in Manhattan on December 30, 2016</span> \r\n					</div>\r\n					<div class=\"a-section a-spacing-none a-spacing-top-small\">\r\n						<span>Once you set the Timer mode, it will come on each day at that time.</span>&nbsp;<br />\r\n<span class=\"a-color-tertiary\" style=\"color:#767676 !important;\">By A Fan on January 3, 2017</span> \r\n					</div>\r\n				</div>\r\n</span> \r\n			</div>\r\n		</div>\r\n	</div>\r\n	<div id=\"question-Tx2V64EIOP97WHS\" class=\"a-fixed-left-grid a-spacing-small\" style=\"color:#111111;font-family:verdana, arial, helvetica, sans-serif;font-size:13px;background-color:#FFFFFF;\">\r\n		<div class=\"a-fixed-left-grid-inner\" style=\"padding:0px 0px 0px 100px;\">\r\n			<div class=\"a-fixed-left-grid-col a-col-left\" style=\"margin-left:-100px;\">\r\n				<span class=\"a-text-bold\" style=\"font-weight:700 !important;\">Question:</span> \r\n			</div>\r\n			<div class=\"a-fixed-left-grid-col a-col-right\">\r\n				Does this set of lights have a timer or night sensor ?\r\n			</div>\r\n		</div>\r\n	</div>\r\n	<div class=\"a-fixed-left-grid a-spacing-base\" style=\"color:#111111;font-family:verdana, arial, helvetica, sans-serif;font-size:13px;background-color:#FFFFFF;\">\r\n		<div class=\"a-fixed-left-grid-inner\" style=\"padding:0px 0px 0px 100px;\">\r\n			<div class=\"a-fixed-left-grid-col a-col-left\" style=\"margin-left:-100px;\">\r\n				<span class=\"a-text-bold\" style=\"font-weight:700 !important;\">Answer:</span> \r\n			</div>\r\n			<div class=\"a-fixed-left-grid-col a-col-right\">\r\n				<span>Yes what ever time u set it on it goes on every day at the same time then goes f after about 4 to six hours</span>&nbsp;<br />\r\n<span class=\"a-color-tertiary\" style=\"color:#767676 !important;\">By Donna on November 12, 2016</span><span class=\"askInlineAnswers\" id=\"Tx2V64EIOP97WHS\"> \r\n				<div id=\"askInlineAnswersPage-Tx2V64EIOP97WHS-1\" class=\"a-section a-spacing-none\">\r\n					<div class=\"a-section a-spacing-none a-spacing-top-small\">\r\n						<span>Hi Claudia, as far as a timer or night sensor, I\'ve not noticed one but it has 8 different light patterns you can choose from. Hope this helps.</span>&nbsp;<br />\r\n<span class=\"a-color-tertiary\" style=\"color:#767676 !important;\">By desiree jones on October 12, 2016</span> \r\n					</div>\r\n					<div class=\"a-section a-spacing-none a-spacing-top-small\">\r\n						<span>Thank you for your question. For your information: It is not the light sensor string lights and doesn\'t havea timer. But the timer of the lights can be controled by yourself. There are tow buttons of ON/OFF and MODES, the working time of the lights depends on the modes and the battery you chooes.</span>&nbsp;<br />\r\n<span class=\"a-color-tertiary\" style=\"color:#767676 !important;\">By Icicle Direct&nbsp;on October 12, 2016</span> \r\n					</div>\r\n				</div>\r\n</span> \r\n			</div>\r\n		</div>\r\n	</div>\r\n	<div id=\"question-Tx2WGD5GPZJIL35\" class=\"a-fixed-left-grid a-spacing-small\" style=\"color:#111111;font-family:verdana, arial, helvetica, sans-serif;font-size:13px;background-color:#FFFFFF;\">\r\n		<div class=\"a-fixed-left-grid-inner\" style=\"padding:0px 0px 0px 100px;\">\r\n			<div class=\"a-fixed-left-grid-col a-col-left\" style=\"margin-left:-100px;\">\r\n				<span class=\"a-text-bold\" style=\"font-weight:700 !important;\">Question:</span> \r\n			</div>\r\n			<div class=\"a-fixed-left-grid-col a-col-right\">\r\n				Would these lights be safe to wrap around a sweater to wear?\r\n			</div>\r\n		</div>\r\n	</div>\r\n	<div class=\"a-fixed-left-grid a-spacing-base\" style=\"color:#111111;font-family:verdana, arial, helvetica, sans-serif;font-size:13px;background-color:#FFFFFF;\">\r\n		<div class=\"a-fixed-left-grid-inner\" style=\"padding:0px 0px 0px 100px;\">\r\n			<div class=\"a-fixed-left-grid-col a-col-left\" style=\"margin-left:-100px;\">\r\n				<span class=\"a-text-bold\" style=\"font-weight:700 !important;\">Answer:</span> \r\n			</div>\r\n			<div class=\"a-fixed-left-grid-col a-col-right\">\r\n				<span>Absolutely safe. Very low voltage but very bright colors</span>&nbsp;<br />\r\n<span class=\"a-color-tertiary\" style=\"color:#767676 !important;\">By gerald evans on November 28, 2016</span><span class=\"askInlineAnswers\" id=\"Tx2WGD5GPZJIL35\"> \r\n				<div id=\"askInlineAnswersPage-Tx2WGD5GPZJIL35-1\" class=\"a-section a-spacing-none\">\r\n					<div class=\"a-section a-spacing-none a-spacing-top-small\">\r\n						<span>Should be ok, they do not get hot</span>&nbsp;<br />\r\n<span class=\"a-color-tertiary\" style=\"color:#767676 !important;\">By Jane Lantz on November 29, 2016</span> \r\n					</div>\r\n				</div>\r\n</span> \r\n			</div>\r\n		</div>\r\n	</div>\r\n	<div id=\"question-Tx3211XWO7IK3UG\" class=\"a-fixed-left-grid a-spacing-small\" style=\"color:#111111;font-family:verdana, arial, helvetica, sans-serif;font-size:13px;background-color:#FFFFFF;\">\r\n		<div class=\"a-fixed-left-grid-inner\" style=\"padding:0px 0px 0px 100px;\">\r\n			<div class=\"a-fixed-left-grid-col a-col-left\" style=\"margin-left:-100px;\">\r\n				<span class=\"a-text-bold\" style=\"font-weight:700 !important;\">Question:</span> \r\n			</div>\r\n			<div class=\"a-fixed-left-grid-col a-col-right\">\r\n				Can the battery pack be put on the ground outside? How do these lights work outdoors?\r\n			</div>\r\n		</div>\r\n	</div>\r\n	<div class=\"a-fixed-left-grid a-spacing-base\" style=\"color:#111111;font-family:verdana, arial, helvetica, sans-serif;font-size:13px;background-color:#FFFFFF;\">\r\n		<div class=\"a-fixed-left-grid-inner\" style=\"padding:0px 0px 0px 100px;\">\r\n			<div class=\"a-fixed-left-grid-col a-col-left\" style=\"margin-left:-100px;\">\r\n				<span class=\"a-text-bold\" style=\"font-weight:700 !important;\">Answer:</span> \r\n			</div>\r\n			<div class=\"a-fixed-left-grid-col a-col-right\">\r\n				<span>Yes, the case is fairly well sealed, should be ok outside. They work the same outdoors as indoors, turn them on anywhere you\'d like!</span>&nbsp;<br />\r\n<span class=\"a-color-tertiary\" style=\"color:#767676 !important;\">By Amazon Customer on December 7, 2016</span><span class=\"askInlineAnswers\" id=\"Tx3211XWO7IK3UG\"> \r\n				<div id=\"askInlineAnswersPage-Tx3211XWO7IK3UG-1\" class=\"a-section a-spacing-none\">\r\n					<div class=\"a-section a-spacing-none a-spacing-top-small\">\r\n						<span>It is a plastic box that snaps shut. Not sure how water resistant it is, but it should be fine under a eve or overhang</span>&nbsp;<br />\r\n<span class=\"a-color-tertiary\" style=\"color:#767676 !important;\">By Mark on December 8, 2016</span> \r\n					</div>\r\n				</div>\r\n</span> \r\n			</div>\r\n		</div>\r\n	</div>\r\n	<div id=\"question-Tx33OJG8K4XJFJM\" class=\"a-fixed-left-grid a-spacing-small\" style=\"color:#111111;font-family:verdana, arial, helvetica, sans-serif;font-size:13px;background-color:#FFFFFF;\">\r\n		<div class=\"a-fixed-left-grid-inner\" style=\"padding:0px 0px 0px 100px;\">\r\n			<div class=\"a-fixed-left-grid-col a-col-left\" style=\"margin-left:-100px;\">\r\n				<span class=\"a-text-bold\" style=\"font-weight:700 !important;\">Question:</span> \r\n			</div>\r\n			<div class=\"a-fixed-left-grid-col a-col-right\">\r\n				What is the length of each bulb? I\'m looking for something tiny. Thanks.\r\n			</div>\r\n		</div>\r\n	</div>\r\n	<div class=\"a-fixed-left-grid a-spacing-base\" style=\"color:#111111;font-family:verdana, arial, helvetica, sans-serif;font-size:13px;background-color:#FFFFFF;\">\r\n		<div class=\"a-fixed-left-grid-inner\" style=\"padding:0px 0px 0px 100px;\">\r\n			<div class=\"a-fixed-left-grid-col a-col-left\" style=\"margin-left:-100px;\">\r\n				<span class=\"a-text-bold\" style=\"font-weight:700 !important;\">Answer:</span> \r\n			</div>\r\n			<div class=\"a-fixed-left-grid-col a-col-right\">\r\n				<span>They are the same length as what you would get on a regular strand of lights.</span>&nbsp;<br />\r\n<span class=\"a-color-tertiary\" style=\"color:#767676 !important;\">By Kathleen Steel on December 8, 2016</span> \r\n			</div>\r\n		</div>\r\n	</div>\r\n	<div id=\"question-Tx37GNCG3T7HQ68\" class=\"a-fixed-left-grid a-spacing-small\" style=\"color:#111111;font-family:verdana, arial, helvetica, sans-serif;font-size:13px;background-color:#FFFFFF;\">\r\n		<div class=\"a-fixed-left-grid-inner\" style=\"padding:0px 0px 0px 100px;\">\r\n			<div class=\"a-fixed-left-grid-col a-col-left\" style=\"margin-left:-100px;\">\r\n				<span class=\"a-text-bold\" style=\"font-weight:700 !important;\">Question:</span> \r\n			</div>\r\n			<div class=\"a-fixed-left-grid-col a-col-right\">\r\n				Does the timmer last 6 solid hrs? How long does a battery last, if on every day?\r\n			</div>\r\n		</div>\r\n	</div>\r\n	<div class=\"a-fixed-left-grid a-spacing-base\" style=\"color:#111111;font-family:verdana, arial, helvetica, sans-serif;font-size:13px;background-color:#FFFFFF;\">\r\n		<div class=\"a-fixed-left-grid-inner\" style=\"padding:0px 0px 0px 100px;\">\r\n			<div class=\"a-fixed-left-grid-col a-col-left\" style=\"margin-left:-100px;\">\r\n				<span class=\"a-text-bold\" style=\"font-weight:700 !important;\">Answer:</span> \r\n			</div>\r\n			<div class=\"a-fixed-left-grid-col a-col-right\">\r\n				<span>Yes! Kept them on my desk on and running constantly Monday-Friday 9-5 all through the holiday season and the battery still hasn\'t died. They hang in my room now:)</span>&nbsp;<br />\r\n<span class=\"a-color-tertiary\" style=\"color:#767676 !important;\">By Brittany Hilliard on March 11, 2017</span><span class=\"askInlineAnswers\" id=\"Tx37GNCG3T7HQ68\"> \r\n				<div id=\"askInlineAnswersPage-Tx37GNCG3T7HQ68-1\" class=\"a-section a-spacing-none\">\r\n					<div class=\"a-section a-spacing-none a-spacing-top-small\">\r\n						<span>I turned them on everyday for a month about 4 hrs and the batteries lasted the whole time</span>&nbsp;<br />\r\n<span class=\"a-color-tertiary\" style=\"color:#767676 !important;\">By Margaret Hicks on February 4, 2017</span> \r\n					</div>\r\n					<div class=\"a-section a-spacing-none a-spacing-top-small\">\r\n						<span>Yes it does. Not exactly sure, had them up for Christmas and battery was still working when I took them down.</span>&nbsp;<br />\r\n<span class=\"a-color-tertiary\" style=\"color:#767676 !important;\">By sinnin13 on February 3, 2017</span> \r\n					</div>\r\n				</div>\r\n</span> \r\n			</div>\r\n		</div>\r\n	</div>\r\n</div>', 'Multi Color 50 LED Battery String Lights | 8 Modes Outdoor Christmas Fairy Lights for Xmas Tree Decor - Qedertek', 'outdoor christmas decorations battery operated,multi color led battery operated lights,battery operated multi color fairy lights,battery operated outdoor string lights', 'Search for battery operated decor lights，you are just right here, Qedertek multi color 50 LED fairy lights, powered by 3 x C size Battery, 8 lighting modes optional, widely use for daily holiday, garden adding atmosphere even perfect for Xmas Tree decor.', 'https://www.amazon.com/dp/B01JRQECF6/', '', '0', '0.00', 'http://images.qedertek.com/5970819eed59d', '{\"597081a08a0d8\":\"http:\\/\\/images.qedertek.com\\/597081a08a0d8\",\"597081a0b012b\":\"http:\\/\\/images.qedertek.com\\/597081a0b012b\",\"597081a0d08b8\":\"http:\\/\\/images.qedertek.com\\/597081a0d08b8\",\"597081a103038\":\"http:\\/\\/images.qedertek.com\\/597081a103038\",\"597081a1188ff\":\"http:\\/\\/images.qedertek.com\\/597081a1188ff\"}', '0', '0', '1', '0.00', '1', '1500545441', '1500545851', '', '0');
INSERT INTO `qe_product` VALUES ('74', '4', 'Battery Powered 50 LED 8 Modes String Lights Warm White', '<div class=\"disclaim\" style=\"font-size:10px;color:#888888;margin:0px 0px 1em;font-family:verdana, arial, helvetica, sans-serif;background-color:#FFFFFF;\">\r\n	Color Name:<span style=\"font-weight:700;\">Warm White</span>\r\n</div>\r\n<p style=\"margin-left:1em;color:#333333;font-family:&quot;font-size:small;background-color:#FFFFFF;\">\r\n	\"&nbsp;<span style=\"font-weight:700;\">Qedertek is a brand registered in USA which is specialized in LED products.&nbsp;</span><br />\r\n<span style=\"font-weight:700;\">Products Features:&nbsp;</span><br />\r\n1. perfectly consistent with a variety of decoration, creating a starry fairy scene.&nbsp;<br />\r\n2. High-brightness string light, but not dazzling.&nbsp;<br />\r\n3. Safe, power-saving and low cost.&nbsp;<br />\r\n4. Waterproof, Suitable for indoor and outdoor, A perfect decoration for Valentine\'s Day, Christmas, Party, Wedding, etc.&nbsp;<br />\r\n5. Timer includes eight modes: Combination(In turn change the mode between 2-8),In Waves, Sequential, Slo Glo, Chasing/Flash, Slow Fade, Twinkle/Flash, Steady On, And all modes have a time control function 6 hours \"\"ON\"\" and 18 hours \"\"OFF\"\".&nbsp;<br />\r\n<span style=\"font-weight:700;\">Specification:&nbsp;</span><br />\r\n1. Light color:Warm White&nbsp;<br />\r\n2. Battery: 3 x C size 1.5 V (not included)&nbsp;<br />\r\n3. Cable length: 4m/13.1ft, lead length 30cm/1ft, lamp spacing 7.7cm/0.25ft&nbsp;<br />\r\n4. Working time: Steady state can work a month, LED total working time more than 10,000 hours&nbsp;<br />\r\n6. LED quantity: 50pcs, 50 LED at 7.7CM/0.25ft spacing&nbsp;<br />\r\n7. Light modes: 8 models Eight kinds of mode automatically transform(Need to press the switch by hand to convert one light mode; you can press it several times for which mode you want).\"\r\n</p>', '<ul class=\"a-unordered-list a-vertical a-spacing-none\" style=\"color:#949494;font-family:&quot;font-size:13px;background-color:#FFFFFF;\">\r\n	<li>\r\n		<span class=\"a-list-item\" style=\"color:#111111;\">No power cord or socket required. Battery operated (not included) LED string lights allow you to decorate indoor/outdoor without any household power supply.</span>\r\n	</li>\r\n	<li>\r\n		<span class=\"a-list-item\" style=\"color:#111111;\">8 Setting controller with memory chip includes:Combination，In Waves,Sequential,Slo Glo,Chasing/Flash,Slow Fade, Twinkle/Flash, Steady On.</span>\r\n	</li>\r\n	<li>\r\n		<span class=\"a-list-item\" style=\"color:#111111;\">Total length 4m/13.1ft, lead length 30cm/1ft, lamp spacing 7.7cm/0.25ft.</span>\r\n	</li>\r\n	<li>\r\n		<span class=\"a-list-item\" style=\"color:#111111;\">Perfect decoration for Valentine\'s Day, Christmas, Party and other celebration occasions, it can be easily put or hung on walls, windows, doors, floors, trees, grasses etc.</span>\r\n	</li>\r\n	<li>\r\n		<span class=\"a-list-item\" style=\"color:#111111;\">Any quality problems about the product, please contact us first.</span>\r\n	</li>\r\n</ul>', '<div id=\"question-Tx18C7QALKOYPA8\" class=\"a-fixed-left-grid a-spacing-small\" style=\"color:#111111;font-family:verdana, arial, helvetica, sans-serif;font-size:13px;background-color:#FFFFFF;\">\r\n	<div class=\"a-fixed-left-grid-inner\" style=\"padding:0px 0px 0px 100px;\">\r\n		<div class=\"a-fixed-left-grid-col a-col-left\" style=\"margin-left:-100px;\">\r\n			<span class=\"a-text-bold\" style=\"font-weight:700 !important;\">Question:</span>\r\n		</div>\r\n		<div class=\"a-fixed-left-grid-col a-col-right\">\r\n			Is this item available in clear lights\r\n		</div>\r\n	</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div class=\"a-fixed-left-grid a-spacing-base\" style=\"color:#111111;font-family:verdana, arial, helvetica, sans-serif;font-size:13px;background-color:#FFFFFF;\">\r\n	<div class=\"a-fixed-left-grid-inner\" style=\"padding:0px 0px 0px 100px;\">\r\n		<div class=\"a-fixed-left-grid-col a-col-left\" style=\"margin-left:-100px;\">\r\n			<span class=\"a-text-bold\" style=\"font-weight:700 !important;\">Answer:</span>\r\n		</div>\r\n		<div class=\"a-fixed-left-grid-col a-col-right\">\r\n			Yes, available in different styles and colors. Simply click on \"Qedertek\" under the product name, or search amazon for \"Qedertek\" and you will see they have a multitude of options.&nbsp;<br />\r\n<span class=\"a-color-tertiary\" style=\"color:#767676 !important;\">By Amazon Customer on December 7, 2016</span>\r\n		</div>\r\n	</div>\r\n	<div id=\"question-Tx1MVINKELXKYGS\" class=\"a-fixed-left-grid a-spacing-small\">\r\n		<div class=\"a-fixed-left-grid-inner\" style=\"padding:0px 0px 0px 100px;\">\r\n			<div class=\"a-fixed-left-grid-col a-col-left\" style=\"margin-left:-100px;\">\r\n				<span class=\"a-text-bold\" style=\"font-weight:700 !important;\">Question:</span>\r\n			</div>\r\n			<div class=\"a-fixed-left-grid-col a-col-right\">\r\n				How many actual bulbs are there?\r\n			</div>\r\n		</div>\r\n	</div>\r\n	<div class=\"a-fixed-left-grid a-spacing-base\">\r\n		<div class=\"a-fixed-left-grid-inner\" style=\"padding:0px 0px 0px 100px;\">\r\n			<div class=\"a-fixed-left-grid-col a-col-left\" style=\"margin-left:-100px;\">\r\n				<span class=\"a-text-bold\" style=\"font-weight:700 !important;\">Answer:</span>\r\n			</div>\r\n			<div class=\"a-fixed-left-grid-col a-col-right\">\r\n				Fifty&nbsp;<br />\r\n<span class=\"a-color-tertiary\" style=\"color:#767676 !important;\">By Derrek on October 26, 2016</span><span class=\"askInlineAnswers\" id=\"Tx1MVINKELXKYGS\">\r\n				<div id=\"askInlineAnswersPage-Tx1MVINKELXKYGS-1\" class=\"a-section a-spacing-none\">\r\n					<div class=\"a-section a-spacing-none a-spacing-top-small\">\r\n						Hi! There are 50 bulbs on it. They are actually super bright! :)&nbsp;<br />\r\n<span class=\"a-color-tertiary\" style=\"color:#767676 !important;\">By desiree jones on October 26, 2016</span>\r\n					</div>\r\n				</div>\r\n</span>\r\n			</div>\r\n		</div>\r\n	</div>\r\n	<div id=\"question-Tx1NKAQE0R98DQB\" class=\"a-fixed-left-grid a-spacing-small\">\r\n		<div class=\"a-fixed-left-grid-inner\" style=\"padding:0px 0px 0px 100px;\">\r\n			<div class=\"a-fixed-left-grid-col a-col-left\" style=\"margin-left:-100px;\">\r\n				<span class=\"a-text-bold\" style=\"font-weight:700 !important;\">Question:</span>\r\n			</div>\r\n			<div class=\"a-fixed-left-grid-col a-col-right\">\r\n				Do these lights turn off automatically? The other battery operated lights I had turned off automatically several hours later like an auto timer.\r\n			</div>\r\n		</div>\r\n	</div>\r\n	<div class=\"a-fixed-left-grid a-spacing-base\">\r\n		<div class=\"a-fixed-left-grid-inner\" style=\"padding:0px 0px 0px 100px;\">\r\n			<div class=\"a-fixed-left-grid-col a-col-left\" style=\"margin-left:-100px;\">\r\n				<span class=\"a-text-bold\" style=\"font-weight:700 !important;\">Answer:</span>\r\n			</div>\r\n			<div class=\"a-fixed-left-grid-col a-col-right\">\r\n				yes they do&nbsp;<br />\r\n<span class=\"a-color-tertiary\" style=\"color:#767676 !important;\">By Ruth H. on November 3, 2016</span><span class=\"askInlineAnswers\" id=\"Tx1NKAQE0R98DQB\">\r\n				<div id=\"askInlineAnswersPage-Tx1NKAQE0R98DQB-1\" class=\"a-section a-spacing-none\">\r\n					<div class=\"a-section a-spacing-none a-spacing-top-small\">\r\n						Not that I know of. They have a button that turns them on and off. I had them on for about 3 hours and they didn\'t shut off.&nbsp;<br />\r\n<span class=\"a-color-tertiary\" style=\"color:#767676 !important;\">By Right? on November 3, 2016</span>\r\n					</div>\r\n					<div class=\"a-section a-spacing-none a-spacing-top-small\">\r\n						I thought the battery had died 2-3 hours in, but I believe that is exactly what it was. Turned them back on and it kept on working!&nbsp;<br />\r\n<span class=\"a-color-tertiary\" style=\"color:#767676 !important;\">By ARincon64 on November 4, 2016</span>\r\n					</div>\r\n					<div class=\"a-section a-spacing-none a-spacing-top-small\">\r\n						Yes they do 6 hours in&nbsp;<br />\r\n<span class=\"a-color-tertiary\" style=\"color:#767676 !important;\">By Donna on November 30, 2016</span>\r\n					</div>\r\n				</div>\r\n</span>\r\n			</div>\r\n		</div>\r\n	</div>\r\n	<div id=\"question-Tx1V9LAKDWSB6US\" class=\"a-fixed-left-grid a-spacing-small\">\r\n		<div class=\"a-fixed-left-grid-inner\" style=\"padding:0px 0px 0px 100px;\">\r\n			<div class=\"a-fixed-left-grid-col a-col-left\" style=\"margin-left:-100px;\">\r\n				<span class=\"a-text-bold\" style=\"font-weight:700 !important;\">Question:</span>\r\n			</div>\r\n			<div class=\"a-fixed-left-grid-col a-col-right\">\r\n				What color bulbs are included in this multi set?\r\n			</div>\r\n		</div>\r\n	</div>\r\n	<div class=\"a-fixed-left-grid a-spacing-base\">\r\n		<div class=\"a-fixed-left-grid-inner\" style=\"padding:0px 0px 0px 100px;\">\r\n			<div class=\"a-fixed-left-grid-col a-col-left\" style=\"margin-left:-100px;\">\r\n				<span class=\"a-text-bold\" style=\"font-weight:700 !important;\">Answer:</span>\r\n			</div>\r\n			<div class=\"a-fixed-left-grid-col a-col-right\">\r\n				The bulbs are blue,red,green,purple and orange. All very pretty.&nbsp;<br />\r\n<span class=\"a-color-tertiary\" style=\"color:#767676 !important;\">By Gari Cominiello on November 25, 2016</span>\r\n			</div>\r\n		</div>\r\n	</div>\r\n	<div id=\"question-Tx201I0VDYSEPEY\" class=\"a-fixed-left-grid a-spacing-small\">\r\n		<div class=\"a-fixed-left-grid-inner\" style=\"padding:0px 0px 0px 100px;\">\r\n			<div class=\"a-fixed-left-grid-col a-col-left\" style=\"margin-left:-100px;\">\r\n				<span class=\"a-text-bold\" style=\"font-weight:700 !important;\">Question:</span>\r\n			</div>\r\n			<div class=\"a-fixed-left-grid-col a-col-right\">\r\n				Are the lights glass bulbs? Or, plastic?\r\n			</div>\r\n		</div>\r\n	</div>\r\n	<div class=\"a-fixed-left-grid a-spacing-base\">\r\n		<div class=\"a-fixed-left-grid-inner\" style=\"padding:0px 0px 0px 100px;\">\r\n			<div class=\"a-fixed-left-grid-col a-col-left\" style=\"margin-left:-100px;\">\r\n				<span class=\"a-text-bold\" style=\"font-weight:700 !important;\">Answer:</span>\r\n			</div>\r\n			<div class=\"a-fixed-left-grid-col a-col-right\">\r\n				Plastic I believe- we put them on a tree outside and they look very nice&nbsp;<br />\r\n<span class=\"a-color-tertiary\" style=\"color:#767676 !important;\">By Bonnie A. on December 20, 2016</span><span class=\"askInlineAnswers\" id=\"Tx201I0VDYSEPEY\">\r\n				<div id=\"askInlineAnswersPage-Tx201I0VDYSEPEY-1\" class=\"a-section a-spacing-none\">\r\n					<div class=\"a-section a-spacing-none a-spacing-top-small\">\r\n						Plastic&nbsp;<br />\r\n<span class=\"a-color-tertiary\" style=\"color:#767676 !important;\">By sinnin13 on December 20, 2016</span>\r\n					</div>\r\n					<div class=\"a-section a-spacing-none a-spacing-top-small\">\r\n						Dear Grace, thank you for your question. The lights are all LED lights, and the bulbs are plastic material.&nbsp;<br />\r\n<span class=\"a-color-tertiary\" style=\"color:#767676 !important;\">By Icicle Direct&nbsp;on December 21, 2016</span>\r\n					</div>\r\n				</div>\r\n</span>\r\n			</div>\r\n		</div>\r\n	</div>\r\n	<div id=\"question-Tx20OYSM3A0Z0C6\" class=\"a-fixed-left-grid a-spacing-small\">\r\n		<div class=\"a-fixed-left-grid-inner\" style=\"padding:0px 0px 0px 100px;\">\r\n			<div class=\"a-fixed-left-grid-col a-col-left\" style=\"margin-left:-100px;\">\r\n				<span class=\"a-text-bold\" style=\"font-weight:700 !important;\">Question:</span>\r\n			</div>\r\n			<div class=\"a-fixed-left-grid-col a-col-right\">\r\n				Do any of the modes offer various bulbs twinkling on and off at different times,using in a custom jewelry box &amp; need effect of twinkling stars?\r\n			</div>\r\n		</div>\r\n	</div>\r\n	<div class=\"a-fixed-left-grid a-spacing-base\">\r\n		<div class=\"a-fixed-left-grid-inner\" style=\"padding:0px 0px 0px 100px;\">\r\n			<div class=\"a-fixed-left-grid-col a-col-left\" style=\"margin-left:-100px;\">\r\n				<span class=\"a-text-bold\" style=\"font-weight:700 !important;\">Answer:</span>\r\n			</div>\r\n			<div class=\"a-fixed-left-grid-col a-col-right\">\r\n				There are different modes however there is no timer or anything.. you would need to set it to the twinkle you want. Really happy with the purchase myself though! I use them in the office at my cubicle :)&nbsp;<br />\r\n<span class=\"a-color-tertiary\" style=\"color:#767676 !important;\">By Brittany Hilliard on May 7, 2017</span>\r\n			</div>\r\n		</div>\r\n	</div>\r\n	<div id=\"question-Tx2UI3DXK4TOOHK\" class=\"a-fixed-left-grid a-spacing-small\">\r\n		<div class=\"a-fixed-left-grid-inner\" style=\"padding:0px 0px 0px 100px;\">\r\n			<div class=\"a-fixed-left-grid-col a-col-left\" style=\"margin-left:-100px;\">\r\n				<span class=\"a-text-bold\" style=\"font-weight:700 !important;\">Question:</span>\r\n			</div>\r\n			<div class=\"a-fixed-left-grid-col a-col-right\">\r\n				Does the mode stay on after they turn off or do you need to reset it every day?\r\n			</div>\r\n		</div>\r\n	</div>\r\n	<div class=\"a-fixed-left-grid a-spacing-base\">\r\n		<div class=\"a-fixed-left-grid-inner\" style=\"padding:0px 0px 0px 100px;\">\r\n			<div class=\"a-fixed-left-grid-col a-col-left\" style=\"margin-left:-100px;\">\r\n				<span class=\"a-text-bold\" style=\"font-weight:700 !important;\">Answer:</span>\r\n			</div>\r\n			<div class=\"a-fixed-left-grid-col a-col-right\">\r\n				They shuffle through modes.. one of the modes is \"off\"&nbsp;<br />\r\n<span class=\"a-color-tertiary\" style=\"color:#767676 !important;\">By Brittany Hilliard on December 30, 2016</span><span class=\"askInlineAnswers\" id=\"Tx2UI3DXK4TOOHK\">\r\n				<div id=\"askInlineAnswersPage-Tx2UI3DXK4TOOHK-1\" class=\"a-section a-spacing-none\">\r\n					<div class=\"a-section a-spacing-none a-spacing-top-small\">\r\n						There are several settings, all you have to do is press the button to select the mode. If you want mode 3 press 3 times off is like 8&nbsp;<br />\r\n<span class=\"a-color-tertiary\" style=\"color:#767676 !important;\">By Old in Manhattan on December 30, 2016</span>\r\n					</div>\r\n					<div class=\"a-section a-spacing-none a-spacing-top-small\">\r\n						Once you set the Timer mode, it will come on each day at that time.&nbsp;<br />\r\n<span class=\"a-color-tertiary\" style=\"color:#767676 !important;\">By A Fan on January 3, 2017</span>\r\n					</div>\r\n				</div>\r\n</span>\r\n			</div>\r\n		</div>\r\n	</div>\r\n	<div id=\"question-Tx2V64EIOP97WHS\" class=\"a-fixed-left-grid a-spacing-small\">\r\n		<div class=\"a-fixed-left-grid-inner\" style=\"padding:0px 0px 0px 100px;\">\r\n			<div class=\"a-fixed-left-grid-col a-col-left\" style=\"margin-left:-100px;\">\r\n				<span class=\"a-text-bold\" style=\"font-weight:700 !important;\">Question:</span>\r\n			</div>\r\n			<div class=\"a-fixed-left-grid-col a-col-right\">\r\n				Does this set of lights have a timer or night sensor ?\r\n			</div>\r\n		</div>\r\n	</div>\r\n	<div class=\"a-fixed-left-grid a-spacing-base\">\r\n		<div class=\"a-fixed-left-grid-inner\" style=\"padding:0px 0px 0px 100px;\">\r\n			<div class=\"a-fixed-left-grid-col a-col-left\" style=\"margin-left:-100px;\">\r\n				<span class=\"a-text-bold\" style=\"font-weight:700 !important;\">Answer:</span>\r\n			</div>\r\n			<div class=\"a-fixed-left-grid-col a-col-right\">\r\n				Yes what ever time u set it on it goes on every day at the same time then goes f after about 4 to six hours&nbsp;<br />\r\n<span class=\"a-color-tertiary\" style=\"color:#767676 !important;\">By Donna on November 12, 2016</span><span class=\"askInlineAnswers\" id=\"Tx2V64EIOP97WHS\">\r\n				<div id=\"askInlineAnswersPage-Tx2V64EIOP97WHS-1\" class=\"a-section a-spacing-none\">\r\n					<div class=\"a-section a-spacing-none a-spacing-top-small\">\r\n						Hi Claudia, as far as a timer or night sensor, I\'ve not noticed one but it has 8 different light patterns you can choose from. Hope this helps.&nbsp;<br />\r\n<span class=\"a-color-tertiary\" style=\"color:#767676 !important;\">By desiree jones on October 12, 2016</span>\r\n					</div>\r\n					<div class=\"a-section a-spacing-none a-spacing-top-small\">\r\n						Thank you for your question. For your information: It is not the light sensor string lights and doesn\'t havea timer. But the timer of the lights can be controled by yourself. There are tow buttons of ON/OFF and MODES, the working time of the lights depends on the modes and the battery you chooes.&nbsp;<br />\r\n<span class=\"a-color-tertiary\" style=\"color:#767676 !important;\">By Icicle Direct&nbsp;on October 12, 2016</span>\r\n					</div>\r\n				</div>\r\n</span>\r\n			</div>\r\n		</div>\r\n	</div>\r\n	<div id=\"question-Tx2WGD5GPZJIL35\" class=\"a-fixed-left-grid a-spacing-small\">\r\n		<div class=\"a-fixed-left-grid-inner\" style=\"padding:0px 0px 0px 100px;\">\r\n			<div class=\"a-fixed-left-grid-col a-col-left\" style=\"margin-left:-100px;\">\r\n				<span class=\"a-text-bold\" style=\"font-weight:700 !important;\">Question:</span>\r\n			</div>\r\n			<div class=\"a-fixed-left-grid-col a-col-right\">\r\n				Would these lights be safe to wrap around a sweater to wear?\r\n			</div>\r\n		</div>\r\n	</div>\r\n	<div class=\"a-fixed-left-grid a-spacing-base\">\r\n		<div class=\"a-fixed-left-grid-inner\" style=\"padding:0px 0px 0px 100px;\">\r\n			<div class=\"a-fixed-left-grid-col a-col-left\" style=\"margin-left:-100px;\">\r\n				<span class=\"a-text-bold\" style=\"font-weight:700 !important;\">Answer:</span>\r\n			</div>\r\n			<div class=\"a-fixed-left-grid-col a-col-right\">\r\n				Absolutely safe. Very low voltage but very bright colors&nbsp;<br />\r\n<span class=\"a-color-tertiary\" style=\"color:#767676 !important;\">By gerald evans on November 28, 2016</span><span class=\"askInlineAnswers\" id=\"Tx2WGD5GPZJIL35\">\r\n				<div id=\"askInlineAnswersPage-Tx2WGD5GPZJIL35-1\" class=\"a-section a-spacing-none\">\r\n					<div class=\"a-section a-spacing-none a-spacing-top-small\">\r\n						Should be ok, they do not get hot&nbsp;<br />\r\n<span class=\"a-color-tertiary\" style=\"color:#767676 !important;\">By Jane Lantz on November 29, 2016</span>\r\n					</div>\r\n				</div>\r\n</span>\r\n			</div>\r\n		</div>\r\n	</div>\r\n	<div id=\"question-Tx3211XWO7IK3UG\" class=\"a-fixed-left-grid a-spacing-small\">\r\n		<div class=\"a-fixed-left-grid-inner\" style=\"padding:0px 0px 0px 100px;\">\r\n			<div class=\"a-fixed-left-grid-col a-col-left\" style=\"margin-left:-100px;\">\r\n				<span class=\"a-text-bold\" style=\"font-weight:700 !important;\">Question:</span>\r\n			</div>\r\n			<div class=\"a-fixed-left-grid-col a-col-right\">\r\n				Can the battery pack be put on the ground outside? How do these lights work outdoors?\r\n			</div>\r\n		</div>\r\n	</div>\r\n	<div class=\"a-fixed-left-grid a-spacing-base\">\r\n		<div class=\"a-fixed-left-grid-inner\" style=\"padding:0px 0px 0px 100px;\">\r\n			<div class=\"a-fixed-left-grid-col a-col-left\" style=\"margin-left:-100px;\">\r\n				<span class=\"a-text-bold\" style=\"font-weight:700 !important;\">Answer:</span>\r\n			</div>\r\n			<div class=\"a-fixed-left-grid-col a-col-right\">\r\n				Yes, the case is fairly well sealed, should be ok outside. They work the same outdoors as indoors, turn them on anywhere you\'d like!&nbsp;<br />\r\n<span class=\"a-color-tertiary\" style=\"color:#767676 !important;\">By Amazon Customer on December 7, 2016</span><span class=\"askInlineAnswers\" id=\"Tx3211XWO7IK3UG\">\r\n				<div id=\"askInlineAnswersPage-Tx3211XWO7IK3UG-1\" class=\"a-section a-spacing-none\">\r\n					<div class=\"a-section a-spacing-none a-spacing-top-small\">\r\n						It is a plastic box that snaps shut. Not sure how water resistant it is, but it should be fine under a eve or overhang&nbsp;<br />\r\n<span class=\"a-color-tertiary\" style=\"color:#767676 !important;\">By Mark on December 8, 2016</span>\r\n					</div>\r\n				</div>\r\n</span>\r\n			</div>\r\n		</div>\r\n	</div>\r\n	<div id=\"question-Tx33OJG8K4XJFJM\" class=\"a-fixed-left-grid a-spacing-small\">\r\n		<div class=\"a-fixed-left-grid-inner\" style=\"padding:0px 0px 0px 100px;\">\r\n			<div class=\"a-fixed-left-grid-col a-col-left\" style=\"margin-left:-100px;\">\r\n				<span class=\"a-text-bold\" style=\"font-weight:700 !important;\">Question:</span>\r\n			</div>\r\n			<div class=\"a-fixed-left-grid-col a-col-right\">\r\n				What is the length of each bulb? I\'m looking for something tiny. Thanks.\r\n			</div>\r\n		</div>\r\n	</div>\r\n	<div class=\"a-fixed-left-grid a-spacing-base\">\r\n		<div class=\"a-fixed-left-grid-inner\" style=\"padding:0px 0px 0px 100px;\">\r\n			<div class=\"a-fixed-left-grid-col a-col-left\" style=\"margin-left:-100px;\">\r\n				<span class=\"a-text-bold\" style=\"font-weight:700 !important;\">Answer:</span>\r\n			</div>\r\n			<div class=\"a-fixed-left-grid-col a-col-right\">\r\n				They are the same length as what you would get on a regular strand of lights.&nbsp;<br />\r\n<span class=\"a-color-tertiary\" style=\"color:#767676 !important;\">By Kathleen Steel on December 8, 2016</span>\r\n			</div>\r\n		</div>\r\n	</div>\r\n	<div id=\"question-Tx37GNCG3T7HQ68\" class=\"a-fixed-left-grid a-spacing-small\">\r\n		<div class=\"a-fixed-left-grid-inner\" style=\"padding:0px 0px 0px 100px;\">\r\n			<div class=\"a-fixed-left-grid-col a-col-left\" style=\"margin-left:-100px;\">\r\n				<span class=\"a-text-bold\" style=\"font-weight:700 !important;\">Question:</span>\r\n			</div>\r\n			<div class=\"a-fixed-left-grid-col a-col-right\">\r\n				Does the timmer last 6 solid hrs? How long does a battery last, if on every day?\r\n			</div>\r\n		</div>\r\n	</div>\r\n	<div class=\"a-fixed-left-grid a-spacing-base\">\r\n		<div class=\"a-fixed-left-grid-inner\" style=\"padding:0px 0px 0px 100px;\">\r\n			<div class=\"a-fixed-left-grid-col a-col-left\" style=\"margin-left:-100px;\">\r\n				<span class=\"a-text-bold\" style=\"font-weight:700 !important;\">Answer:</span>\r\n			</div>\r\n			<div class=\"a-fixed-left-grid-col a-col-right\">\r\n				Yes! Kept them on my desk on and running constantly Monday-Friday 9-5 all through the holiday season and the battery still hasn\'t died. They hang in my room now:)&nbsp;<br />\r\n<span class=\"a-color-tertiary\" style=\"color:#767676 !important;\">By Brittany Hilliard on March 11, 2017</span><span class=\"askInlineAnswers\" id=\"Tx37GNCG3T7HQ68\">\r\n				<div id=\"askInlineAnswersPage-Tx37GNCG3T7HQ68-1\" class=\"a-section a-spacing-none\">\r\n					<div class=\"a-section a-spacing-none a-spacing-top-small\">\r\n						I turned them on everyday for a month about 4 hrs and the batteries lasted the whole time&nbsp;<br />\r\n<span class=\"a-color-tertiary\" style=\"color:#767676 !important;\">By Margaret Hicks on February 4, 2017</span>\r\n					</div>\r\n					<div class=\"a-section a-spacing-none a-spacing-top-small\">\r\n						Yes it does. Not exactly sure, had them up for Christmas and battery was still working when I took them down.&nbsp;<br />\r\n<span class=\"a-color-tertiary\" style=\"color:#767676 !important;\">By sinnin13 on February 3, 2017</span>\r\n					</div>\r\n				</div>\r\n</span>\r\n			</div>\r\n		</div>\r\n	</div>\r\n</div>', 'Battery String Lights: High-brightness 50 LED 8 Modes Warm White Holiday Lighting String Decor - Qedertek', 'warm white battery operated hanging lights,battery operated decorative lights,fairy lights battery operated outdoor,50 LED battery string lights', 'Wanna to shop battery decorative lights online, Qedertek is a professional battery powered fairy lights supplier,high-brightness, 50 LED, 8 lighting modes warm white ones would be you best choice.', 'https://www.amazon.com/dp/B01JRPDB7M/', '', '0', '0.00', 'http://images.qedertek.com/5970835bc33b5', '{\"5970835be5dce\":\"http:\\/\\/images.qedertek.com\\/5970835be5dce\",\"5970835c12067\":\"http:\\/\\/images.qedertek.com\\/5970835c12067\",\"5