erent mode selection vary a lot. The longest life we tested is about one months.</span>&nbsp;<br />\r\n<span class=\"a-color-tertiary\" style=\"color:#767676 !important;\">By Icicle Direct&nbsp;on December 12, 2016</span> \r\n				</div>\r\n			</div>\r\n</span> \r\n		</div>\r\n	</div>\r\n	<div id=\"question-Tx2RHCL7RRXDQKB\" class=\"a-fixed-left-grid a-spacing-small\" style=\"margin:0px;padding:0px;\">\r\n		<div class=\"a-fixed-left-grid-inner\" style=\"margin:0px;padding:0px 0px 0px 100px;\">\r\n			<div class=\"a-fixed-left-grid-col a-col-left\" style=\"margin:0px 0px 0px -100px;padding:0px;\">\r\n				<span class=\"a-text-bold\" style=\"font-weight:700 !important;\">Question:</span> \r\n			</div>\r\n			<div class=\"a-fixed-left-grid-col a-col-right\" style=\"margin:0px;padding:0px;\">\r\n				Where can I get batteries to operate these lights\r\n			</div>\r\n		</div>\r\n	</div>\r\n	<div class=\"a-fixed-left-grid a-spacing-base\" style=\"margin:0px;padding:0px;\">\r\n		<div class=\"a-fixed-left-grid-inner\" style=\"margin:0px;padding:0px 0px 0px 100px;\">\r\n			<div class=\"a-fixed-left-grid-col a-col-left\" style=\"margin:0px 0px 0px -100px;padding:0px;\">\r\n				<span class=\"a-text-bold\" style=\"font-weight:700 !important;\">Answer:</span> \r\n			</div>\r\n			<div class=\"a-fixed-left-grid-col a-col-right\" style=\"margin:0px;padding:0px;\">\r\n				<span>C batteries are sold at most grocery and convenience stores.</span>&nbsp;<br />\r\n<span class=\"a-color-tertiary\" style=\"color:#767676 !important;\">By Jacqueline Boline on December 9, 2016</span><span class=\"askInlineAnswers\" id=\"Tx2RHCL7RRXDQKB\"> \r\n				<div id=\"askInlineAnswersPage-Tx2RHCL7RRXDQKB-1\" class=\"a-section a-spacing-none\" style=\"margin:0px;padding:0px;\">\r\n					<div class=\"a-section a-spacing-none a-spacing-top-small\" style=\"margin:0px;padding:0px;\">\r\n						<span>I buy all of my batteries at Sams Club. Best prices.</span>&nbsp;<br />\r\n<span class=\"a-color-tertiary\" style=\"color:#767676 !important;\">By Janice E Fletcher on December 9, 2016</span> \r\n					</div>\r\n					<div class=\"a-section a-spacing-none a-spacing-top-small\" style=\"margin:0px;padding:0px;\">\r\n						<span>Anywhere that sells batteries.</span>&nbsp;<br />\r\n<span class=\"a-color-tertiary\" style=\"color:#767676 !important;\">By Someguy on December 9, 2016</span> \r\n					</div>\r\n					<div class=\"a-section a-spacing-none a-spacing-top-small\" style=\"margin:0px;padding:0px;\">\r\n						<span>Three C size batteries. The lights work great. About 7 or so flash patterns.</span>&nbsp;<br />\r\n<span class=\"a-color-tertiary\" style=\"color:#767676 !important;\">By Rideabike on December 9, 2016</span> \r\n					</div>\r\n				</div>\r\n</span> \r\n			</div>\r\n		</div>\r\n	</div>\r\n	<div id=\"question-Tx35TMGHM3SC522\" class=\"a-fixed-left-grid a-spacing-small\" style=\"margin:0px;padding:0px;\">\r\n		<div class=\"a-fixed-left-grid-inner\" style=\"margin:0px;padding:0px 0px 0px 100px;\">\r\n			<div class=\"a-fixed-left-grid-col a-col-left\" style=\"margin:0px 0px 0px -100px;padding:0px;\">\r\n				<span class=\"a-text-bold\" style=\"font-weight:700 !important;\">Question:</span> \r\n			</div>\r\n			<div class=\"a-fixed-left-grid-col a-col-right\" style=\"margin:0px;padding:0px;\">\r\n				The description says timer, does it have a timer and if so how long does it stay on each night? Also, does it come on automatically each night?\r\n			</div>\r\n		</div>\r\n	</div>\r\n	<div class=\"a-fixed-left-grid a-spacing-base\" style=\"margin:0px;padding:0px;\">\r\n		<div class=\"a-fixed-left-grid-inner\" style=\"margin:0px;padding:0px 0px 0px 100px;\">\r\n			<div class=\"a-fixed-left-grid-col a-col-left\" style=\"margin:0px 0px 0px -100px;padding:0px;\">\r\n				<span class=\"a-text-bold\" style=\"font-weight:700 !important;\">Answer:</span> \r\n			</div>\r\n			<div class=\"a-fixed-left-grid-col a-col-right\" style=\"margin:0px;padding:0px;\">\r\n				<span>It\'s really just an automatic shut-off. After you turn it on, it turns itself off after 6 hours. It doesn\'t turn itself on at all - you need to do that each time.</span>&nbsp;<br />\r\n<span class=\"a-color-tertiary\" style=\"color:#767676 !important;\">By Joel L Coleman on November 11, 2016</span><span class=\"askInlineAnswers\" id=\"Tx35TMGHM3SC522\"> \r\n				<div id=\"askInlineAnswersPage-Tx35TMGHM3SC522-1\" class=\"a-section a-spacing-none\" style=\"margin:0px;padding:0px;\">\r\n					<div class=\"a-section a-spacing-none a-spacing-top-small\" style=\"margin:0px;padding:0px;\">\r\n						<span>Yes. I have 12 strings of these and, after turning them on once to the \"steady\" light setting, they come on for 6 hours automatically at the same time each night. I\'m wondering if the first person who answered these either has a defective set or a different set from the one in this listing.</span>&nbsp;<br />\r\n<span class=\"a-color-tertiary\" style=\"color:#767676 !important;\">By Joseph A. Kijewski on December 19, 2016</span> \r\n					</div>\r\n				</div>\r\n</span> \r\n			</div>\r\n		</div>\r\n	</div>\r\n	<div id=\"question-TxDJYR276I9FO7\" class=\"a-fixed-left-grid a-spacing-small\" style=\"margin:0px;padding:0px;\">\r\n		<div class=\"a-fixed-left-grid-inner\" style=\"margin:0px;padding:0px 0px 0px 100px;\">\r\n			<div class=\"a-fixed-left-grid-col a-col-left\" style=\"margin:0px 0px 0px -100px;padding:0px;\">\r\n				<span class=\"a-text-bold\" style=\"font-weight:700 !important;\">Question:</span> \r\n			</div>\r\n			<div class=\"a-fixed-left-grid-col a-col-right\" style=\"margin:0px;padding:0px;\">\r\n				Are you sure they cannot be set for 6 hours on and 18 off and come on automatically with the timer??\r\n			</div>\r\n		</div>\r\n	</div>\r\n	<div class=\"a-fixed-left-grid a-spacing-base\" style=\"margin:0px;padding:0px;\">\r\n		<div class=\"a-fixed-left-grid-inner\" style=\"margin:0px;padding:0px 0px 0px 100px;\">\r\n			<div class=\"a-fixed-left-grid-col a-col-left\" style=\"margin:0px 0px 0px -100px;padding:0px;\">\r\n				<span class=\"a-text-bold\" style=\"font-weight:700 !important;\">Answer:</span> \r\n			</div>\r\n			<div class=\"a-fixed-left-grid-col a-col-right\" style=\"margin:0px;padding:0px;\">\r\n				<span>Yes they can be. You can choose to turn them on manually or use the timer. Various settings for the light show too. I love mine. And the fact that they use C size batteries means they last much longer than those with AA size.</span>&nbsp;<br />\r\n<span class=\"a-color-tertiary\" style=\"color:#767676 !important;\">By C. Gibson on November 21, 2016</span><span class=\"askInlineAnswers\" id=\"TxDJYR276I9FO7\"> \r\n				<div id=\"askInlineAnswersPage-TxDJYR276I9FO7-1\" class=\"a-section a-spacing-none\" style=\"margin:0px;padding:0px;\">\r\n					<div class=\"a-section a-spacing-none a-spacing-top-small\" style=\"margin:0px;padding:0px;\">\r\n						<span>They go on for about six hours and then switch off for about 18. Not sure of exact times.</span>&nbsp;<br />\r\n<span class=\"a-color-tertiary\" style=\"color:#767676 !important;\">By Robin Cooper on November 22, 2016</span> \r\n					</div>\r\n					<div class=\"a-section a-spacing-none a-spacing-top-small\" style=\"margin:0px;padding:0px;\">\r\n						<span>My experience with twelve strings of these is the same as the other responders -- 6 hours on / 18 hours off, and then they turn themselves on again and the cycle repeats.</span>&nbsp;<br />\r\n<span class=\"a-color-tertiary\" style=\"color:#767676 !important;\">By Joseph A. Kijewski on December 19, 2016</span> \r\n					</div>\r\n				</div>\r\n</span> \r\n			</div>\r\n		</div>\r\n	</div>\r\n</div>', '50 LED Battery Operated String Lights with Timer | Cool White Outdoor Bbattery Xmas Lights   - Qedertek', 'fairy lights battery operated outdoor,outdoor battery xmas lights,50 led battery operated fairy lights,cool white led battery operated lights,battery string lights with timer', 'Wanna to shop battery string lights with Timer online, Qedertek is a professional led battery operated lights supplier, Qedertek cool white 50 led battery operated fairy lights, would be you best choice.', 'https://www.amazon.com/dp/B01JRWGC26/', '', '0', '0.00', 'http://images.qedertek.com/5971bf92972b6', '{\"5971bf92e8287\":\"http:\\/\\/images.qedertek.com\\/5971bf92e8287\",\"5971bf9314ba7\":\"http:\\/\\/images.qedertek.com\\/5971bf9314ba7\",\"5971bf9359768\":\"http:\\/\\/images.qedertek.com\\/5971bf9359768\",\"5971bf93d21db\":\"http:\\/\\/images.qedertek.com\\/5971bf93d21db\",\"5971bf93ee3d8\":\"http:\\/\\/images.qedertek.com\\/5971bf93ee3d8\"}', '0', '0', '1', '0.00', '1', '1500626604', '1500626836', '', '0');
INSERT INTO `qe_product` VALUES ('85', '2', 'Solar 120 LED Starry String Copper Wire Lights Warm white', '<div class=\"disclaim\" style=\"font-size:10px;color:#888888;margin:0px 0px 1em;font-family:verdana, arial, helvetica, sans-serif;background-color:#FFFFFF;\">\r\n	Color Name:<span style=\"font-weight:700;\">Warm White</span>\r\n</div>\r\n<p style=\"margin-left:1em;color:#333333;font-family:&quot;font-size:small;background-color:#FFFFFF;\">\r\n	<span style=\"font-weight:700;\">Features&nbsp;</span><br />\r\nSolar Powered LED, No utility energy costs&nbsp;<br />\r\n120 individual Super Bright LED lights for a special night lighting effect<br />\r\nLights turn on automatically in darkness&nbsp;<br />\r\nUp to 12 hours of continuous lighting with one single charge&nbsp;<br />\r\n<br />\r\n<span style=\"font-weight:700;\">Specification</span>&nbsp;<br />\r\nBrand: Icicle&nbsp;<br />\r\nLight color: Warm White&nbsp;<br />\r\nLED Quantity: 120 LED&nbsp;<br />\r\nRechargeable Battery: 1.2V 1000MA&nbsp;<br />\r\nSwitch: Power ON/OFF and MODE&nbsp;<br />\r\nLighting Mode: Constant ON / Flashing&nbsp;<br />\r\nSolar Panel: 2V 150mA&nbsp;<br />\r\nCharging Time: 6 hours&nbsp;<br />\r\nTotal Length: 26.24ft (8m)&nbsp;<br />\r\nblubs spacing: 1.96inch (5cm)&nbsp;<br />\r\nLength from Solar panel to first stake:6.56ft (2m)&nbsp;<br />\r\nSolar panel with ground stake for easy setting&nbsp;<br />\r\n<br />\r\n<span style=\"font-weight:700;\">How the solar panel works?</span>&nbsp;<br />\r\n1. During the daytime, solar panel converses solar energy and converts it to electrical power stored in the rechargeable battery.&nbsp;<br />\r\n2. The battery release the energy as lighting power when it\'s dark enough.&nbsp;<br />\r\n3. There is a rechargeable battery in solar box, which is durable, can be easily replaced.&nbsp;<br />\r\n4. When you find your lighting effective time is getting too short or dimming, it is recommended that you replace the battery.&nbsp;<br />\r\n<br />\r\n<span style=\"font-weight:700;\">What\'s in the Box?&nbsp;</span><br />\r\n1 x Icicle 120 LED Solar String Lights.&nbsp;<br />\r\n1 x 0.4in (20cm) Ground Stake.&nbsp;<br />\r\n1 x Solar Panel.&nbsp;<br />\r\n1 x User Manual.\r\n</p>', '<ul class=\"a-unordered-list a-vertical a-spacing-none\" style=\"color:#949494;font-family:&quot;font-size:13px;background-color:#FFFFFF;\">\r\n	<li>\r\n		<span class=\"a-list-item\" style=\"color:#111111;\">Solar Powered &amp; Durable -- Flexible Copper Wire Lights - can be easily bended and molded into to any shapes you desire.</span>\r\n	</li>\r\n	<li>\r\n		<span class=\"a-list-item\" style=\"color:#111111;\">Easy to Use -- 2 buttons to control. One for power on/off, and another for 2 modes to choose steady/flashing. Put under sunlight during the day, and it begins to light up at night automatically when power on.</span>\r\n	</li>\r\n	<li>\r\n		<span class=\"a-list-item\" style=\"color:#111111;\">Waterproof -- the lights are suitable for Indoor and Outdoor decorations, because of the lights and the solar panel are both waterproof.</span>\r\n	</li>\r\n	<li>\r\n		<span class=\"a-list-item\" style=\"color:#111111;\">Special Decoration Effects -- live, Love, Create, add a warm and charming atmosphere for your Christmas decorations,home, patio, lawn, garden, shop, bar, café, restaurant, balcony, walkways, pergola canopy, and more.</span>\r\n	</li>\r\n	<li>\r\n		<span class=\"a-list-item\" style=\"color:#111111;\">Note -- The solar panel must remain directly exposed to sunshine for a whole day to conserve sufficient solar power before first use.</span>\r\n	</li>\r\n</ul>', '<div id=\"question-Tx2HUDUCT5BSJ69\" class=\"a-fixed-left-grid a-spacing-small\" style=\"color:#111111;font-family:verdana, arial, helvetica, sans-serif;font-size:13px;background-color:#FFFFFF;\">\r\n	<div class=\"a-fixed-left-grid-inner\" style=\"padding:0px 0px 0px 100px;\">\r\n		<div class=\"a-fixed-left-grid-col a-col-left\" style=\"margin-left:-100px;\">\r\n			<span class=\"a-text-bold\" style=\"font-weight:700 !important;\">Question:</span> \r\n		</div>\r\n		<div class=\"a-fixed-left-grid-col a-col-right\">\r\n			Mine used to work fine but stopped working all of a sudden. It\'s veen over 5 days I let the panels charge the sunlight and still nothing.\r\n		</div>\r\n	</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div class=\"a-fixed-left-grid a-spacing-base\" style=\"color:#111111;font-family:verdana, arial, helvetica, sans-serif;font-size:13px;background-color:#FFFFFF;\">\r\n	<div class=\"a-fixed-left-grid-inner\" style=\"padding:0px 0px 0px 100px;\">\r\n		<div class=\"a-fixed-left-grid-col a-col-left\" style=\"margin-left:-100px;\">\r\n			<span class=\"a-text-bold\" style=\"font-weight:700 !important;\">Answer:</span> \r\n		</div>\r\n		<div class=\"a-fixed-left-grid-col a-col-right\">\r\n			<span>I\'m not sure why your\'s not working, but I had mine for about 2-3 months now and it\'s been working fine.</span>&nbsp;<br />\r\n<span class=\"a-color-tertiary\" style=\"color:#767676 !important;\">By Amazon Customer on November 7, 2016</span><span class=\"askInlineAnswers\" id=\"Tx2HUDUCT5BSJ69\"> \r\n			<div id=\"askInlineAnswersPage-Tx2HUDUCT5BSJ69-1\" class=\"a-section a-spacing-none\">\r\n				<div class=\"a-section a-spacing-none a-spacing-top-small\">\r\n					<span>Works great...super bright...</span>&nbsp;<br />\r\n<span class=\"a-color-tertiary\" style=\"color:#767676 !important;\">By Jeanine Pinkman on November 7, 2016</span> \r\n				</div>\r\n				<div class=\"a-section a-spacing-none a-spacing-top-small\">\r\n					<span>check if there is cut in your wiring</span>&nbsp;<br />\r\n<span class=\"a-color-tertiary\" style=\"color:#767676 !important;\">By Magda on November 2, 2016</span> \r\n				</div>\r\n				<div class=\"a-section a-spacing-none a-spacing-top-small\">\r\n					<span>I bought 2. Less than a week out in the cold, one stopped working. The solar panel and the battery works. I suspect the small board inside couldn\'t survive the cold.</span>&nbsp;<br />\r\n<span class=\"a-color-tertiary\" style=\"color:#767676 !important;\">By R/C-Solar-Guy on December 11, 2016</span> \r\n				</div>\r\n			</div>\r\n</span> \r\n		</div>\r\n	</div>\r\n	<div id=\"question-Tx13UES1T37MO5O\" class=\"a-fixed-left-grid a-spacing-small\" style=\"color:#111111;font-family:verdana, arial, helvetica, sans-serif;font-size:13px;background-color:#FFFFFF;\">\r\n		<div class=\"a-fixed-left-grid-inner\" style=\"padding:0px 0px 0px 100px;\">\r\n			<div class=\"a-fixed-left-grid-col a-col-left\" style=\"margin-left:-100px;\">\r\n				<span class=\"a-text-bold\" style=\"font-weight:700 !important;\">Question:</span>\r\n			</div>\r\n			<div class=\"a-fixed-left-grid-col a-col-right\">\r\n				Can I wrap clear tape around the wire to combine two sets of lights together?\r\n			</div>\r\n		</div>\r\n	</div>\r\n	<div class=\"a-fixed-left-grid a-spacing-base\" style=\"color:#111111;font-family:verdana, arial, helvetica, sans-serif;font-size:13px;background-color:#FFFFFF;\">\r\n		<div class=\"a-fixed-left-grid-inner\" style=\"padding:0px 0px 0px 100px;\">\r\n			<div class=\"a-fixed-left-grid-col a-col-left\" style=\"margin-left:-100px;\">\r\n				<span class=\"a-text-bold\" style=\"font-weight:700 !important;\">Answer:</span>\r\n			</div>\r\n			<div class=\"a-fixed-left-grid-col a-col-right\">\r\n				<span>I would just make a small hook in the end of each wire to hock them together.</span>&nbsp;<br />\r\n<span class=\"a-color-tertiary\" style=\"color:#767676 !important;\">By Daniel J. Kauffman on November 14, 2016</span><span class=\"askInlineAnswers\" id=\"Tx13UES1T37MO5O\">\r\n				<div id=\"askInlineAnswersPage-Tx13UES1T37MO5O-1\" class=\"a-section a-spacing-none\">\r\n					<div class=\"a-section a-spacing-none a-spacing-top-small\">\r\n						<span>sure ...no reason why you couldnt</span>&nbsp;<br />\r\n<span class=\"a-color-tertiary\" style=\"color:#767676 !important;\">By Q on November 14, 2016</span>\r\n					</div>\r\n					<div class=\"a-section a-spacing-none a-spacing-top-small\">\r\n						<span>Yes</span>&nbsp;<br />\r\n<span class=\"a-color-tertiary\" style=\"color:#767676 !important;\">By Kate Larkin on November 14, 2016</span>\r\n					</div>\r\n					<div class=\"a-section a-spacing-none a-spacing-top-small\">\r\n						<span>Yes. I am really happy with the lights</span>&nbsp;<br />\r\n<span class=\"a-color-tertiary\" style=\"color:#767676 !important;\">By Amazon Customer on November 14, 2016</span>\r\n					</div>\r\n				</div>\r\n</span>\r\n			</div>\r\n		</div>\r\n	</div>\r\n	<div id=\"question-Tx268HIDYB8IERY\" class=\"a-fixed-left-grid a-spacing-small\" style=\"color:#111111;font-family:verdana, arial, helvetica, sans-serif;font-size:13px;background-color:#FFFFFF;\">\r\n		<div class=\"a-fixed-left-grid-inner\" style=\"padding:0px 0px 0px 100px;\">\r\n			<div class=\"a-fixed-left-grid-col a-col-left\" style=\"margin-left:-100px;\">\r\n				<span class=\"a-text-bold\" style=\"font-weight:700 !important;\">Question:</span>\r\n			</div>\r\n			<div class=\"a-fixed-left-grid-col a-col-right\">\r\n				Can these be used with a timer?\r\n			</div>\r\n		</div>\r\n	</div>\r\n	<div class=\"a-fixed-left-grid a-spacing-base\" style=\"color:#111111;font-family:verdana, arial, helvetica, sans-serif;font-size:13px;background-color:#FFFFFF;\">\r\n		<div class=\"a-fixed-left-grid-inner\" style=\"padding:0px 0px 0px 100px;\">\r\n			<div class=\"a-fixed-left-grid-col a-col-left\" style=\"margin-left:-100px;\">\r\n				<span class=\"a-text-bold\" style=\"font-weight:700 !important;\">Answer:</span>\r\n			</div>\r\n			<div class=\"a-fixed-left-grid-col a-col-right\">\r\n				<span>no they go on at dusk and stay on for 3 -4 hr only</span>&nbsp;<br />\r\n<span class=\"a-color-tertiary\" style=\"color:#767676 !important;\">By Magda on December 14, 2016</span><span class=\"askInlineAnswers\" id=\"Tx268HIDYB8IERY\">\r\n				<div id=\"askInlineAnswersPage-Tx268HIDYB8IERY-1\" class=\"a-section a-spacing-none\">\r\n					<div class=\"a-section a-spacing-none a-spacing-top-small\">\r\n						<span>Dear Jessica, thank you for your question. The lights don\'t have the timer sensor, but it has a light sensor, if your lights are full charged, it will automatically turn on at dusk and off at dawn, so you just need to turn on it all the time.</span>&nbsp;<br />\r\n<span class=\"a-color-tertiary\" style=\"color:#767676 !important;\">By Icicle Direct on December 14, 2016</span>\r\n					</div>\r\n					<div class=\"a-section a-spacing-none a-spacing-top-small\">\r\n						<span>No timer... there\'s just an off and on switch..</span>&nbsp;<br />\r\n<span class=\"a-color-tertiary\" style=\"color:#767676 !important;\">By Beth on December 13, 2016</span>\r\n					</div>\r\n					<div class=\"a-section a-spacing-none a-spacing-top-small\">\r\n						<span>Solar lights cannot be used with a timer since timers plug into AC but they go on automatically and shut off when it\'s daylight or they run out of juice</span>&nbsp;<br />\r\n<span class=\"a-color-tertiary\" style=\"color:#767676 !important;\">By LANI on December 13, 2016</span>\r\n					</div>\r\n				</div>\r\n</span>\r\n			</div>\r\n		</div>\r\n	</div>\r\n<br />\r\n</div>', '120 LED Starry Solar String Lights | Christmas Fairy Copper Wire Lights - Qedertek', 'Starry string lights, 120 led solar string lights, solar Christmas lights,copper wire lights,Christmas decorated lights', '120 led solar flexible copper wire lights, Perfect to add a warm and charming atmosphere for your Christmas decorations,home, patio, lawn, garden, shop, bar, café, restaurant.', 'https://www.amazon.com//dp/B013DOXVYG/', '', '0', '0.00', 'http://images.qedertek.com/5975a83fbeeca', '{\"5975a83fedc72\":\"http:\\/\\/images.qedertek.com\\/5975a83fedc72\",\"5975a8401a25c\":\"http:\\/\\/images.qedertek.com\\/5975a8401a25c\",\"5975a8403b306\":\"http:\\/\\/images.qedertek.com\\/5975a8403b306\",\"5975a84050540\":\"http:\\/\\/images.qedertek.com\\/5975a84050540\",\"5975a8407251b\":\"http:\\/\\/images.qedertek.com\\/5975a8407251b\"}', '0', '0', '1', '0.00', '1', '1500883008', '1500883008', '', '0');
INSERT INTO `qe_product` VALUES ('86', '7', 'Ultrasonic 100ml Essential Oil Diffusers(Smooth Surface)', '<span style=\"font-weight:700;color:#333333;font-family:&quot;font-size:small;background-color:#FFFFFF;\">Qedertek is a brand registered in USA which is specialized in LED products.</span><br />\r\n<span style=\"font-weight:700;color:#333333;font-family:&quot;font-size:small;background-color:#FFFFFF;\">Functions:&nbsp;</span><span style=\"color:#333333;font-family:&quot;font-size:small;background-color:#FFFFFF;\"></span><br />\r\n<span style=\"color:#333333;font-family:&quot;font-size:small;background-color:#FFFFFF;\">Refresh skin, keep it healthy and moist&nbsp;</span><br />\r\n<span style=\"color:#333333;font-family:&quot;font-size:small;background-color:#FFFFFF;\">Humidify the air&nbsp;</span><br />\r\n<span style=\"color:#333333;font-family:&quot;font-size:small;background-color:#FFFFFF;\">Aroma therapy, relieve stress&nbsp;</span><br />\r\n<span style=\"color:#333333;font-family:&quot;font-size:small;background-color:#FFFFFF;\">Reduce headaches&nbsp;</span><br />\r\n<span style=\"color:#333333;font-family:&quot;font-size:small;background-color:#FFFFFF;\">Contribute to more restful sleep&nbsp;</span><br />\r\n<span style=\"color:#333333;font-family:&quot;font-size:small;background-color:#FFFFFF;\">Ease cold and flu symptoms&nbsp;</span><br />\r\n<span style=\"color:#333333;font-family:&quot;font-size:small;background-color:#FFFFFF;\">Alleviate allergies&nbsp;</span><br />\r\n<br />\r\n<br />\r\n<span style=\"font-weight:700;color:#333333;font-family:&quot;font-size:small;background-color:#FFFFFF;\">Specifications:&nbsp;</span><span style=\"color:#333333;font-family:&quot;font-size:small;background-color:#FFFFFF;\"></span><br />\r\n<span style=\"color:#333333;font-family:&quot;font-size:small;background-color:#FFFFFF;\">Material: Upper parts PP&nbsp;</span><br />\r\n<span style=\"color:#333333;font-family:&quot;font-size:small;background-color:#FFFFFF;\">Capac