an style=\"color:#333333;font-family:&quot;font-size:small;background-color:#FFFFFF;\">Note: Oil is not included in this package&nbsp;</span>', '<ul class=\"a-unordered-list a-vertical a-spacing-none\" style=\"margin-left:18px;color:#949494;font-family:&quot;font-size:13px;background-color:#FFFFFF;\">\r\n	<li>\r\n		<span class=\"a-list-item\" style=\"color:#111111;\">Fill the space with a lovely fragrance and at the same time humidify the air surrounding you. Fragrance can melt away your stress and relieve you from stressful and tiring day, also perfect for masking odors such as the smells of smoking and stale sweat. Mist humidifier can increase moisture in the air to prevent your skin from being dry.</span>\r\n	</li>\r\n	<li>\r\n		<span class=\"a-list-item\" style=\"color:#111111;\">Super Quiet Ultrasonic Operation- Extremely quiet and pleasant, no noise, heat or vibration, allowing for a deep relaxing sleep. Great for bedrooms, bathrooms, massage rooms, spas, etc. Can be placed on your nightstand, on the desk in the office, etc.</span>\r\n	</li>\r\n	<li>\r\n		<span class=\"a-list-item\" style=\"color:#111111;\">Shuts Off Automatically if the water runs out, very safe and easy to use, just fill with warm tap water and add a few drops of your favorite essential oil. (Measuring cup is included). No Need for filters or distilled water.</span>\r\n	</li>\r\n	<li>\r\n		<span class=\"a-list-item\" style=\"color:#111111;\">LED Light Modes: 7 Mood Lights automatically change from one color to the next, or you can choose one light you like and set it to be steady on. If no need for light, you can turn it off and just let the mist on. Color including: Green, Dark blue, Red, Yellow, Pink, Light blue, White</span>\r\n	</li>\r\n	<li>\r\n		<span class=\"a-list-item\" style=\"color:#111111;\">Mist Working Modes: Intermittent Mist (30 seconds on/30 seconds off), Continuous Mist, Lights only. Working Time: 3 hours in continuous mist mode, 7 hours in intermittent mist mode. Content: 100ml, Material: PP Hard plastic, BPA Free.</span>\r\n	</li>\r\n</ul>', '<div id=\"question-Tx1XQWU783CK2NJ\" class=\"a-fixed-left-grid a-spacing-small\" style=\"color:#111111;font-family:verdana, arial, helvetica, sans-serif;font-size:13px;background-color:#FFFFFF;\">\r\n	<div class=\"a-fixed-left-grid-inner\" style=\"padding:0px 0px 0px 100px;\">\r\n		<div class=\"a-fixed-left-grid-col a-col-left\" style=\"margin-left:-100px;\">\r\n			<span class=\"a-text-bold\" style=\"font-weight:700 !important;\">Question:</span> \r\n		</div>\r\n		<div class=\"a-fixed-left-grid-col a-col-right\">\r\n			Can this diffuser be used without the light changing color or be turned off?\r\n		</div>\r\n	</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div class=\"a-fixed-left-grid a-spacing-base\" style=\"color:#111111;font-family:verdana, arial, helvetica, sans-serif;font-size:13px;background-color:#FFFFFF;\">\r\n	<div class=\"a-fixed-left-grid-inner\" style=\"padding:0px 0px 0px 100px;\">\r\n		<div class=\"a-fixed-left-grid-col a-col-left\" style=\"margin-left:-100px;\">\r\n			<span class=\"a-text-bold\" style=\"font-weight:700 !important;\">Answer:</span> \r\n		</div>\r\n		<div class=\"a-fixed-left-grid-col a-col-right\">\r\n			<span>Yes</span>&nbsp;<br />\r\n<span class=\"a-color-tertiary\" style=\"color:#767676 !important;\">By Kelly S. on April 27, 2017</span><span class=\"askInlineAnswers\" id=\"Tx1XQWU783CK2NJ\"> \r\n			<div id=\"askInlineAnswersPage-Tx1XQWU783CK2NJ-1\" class=\"a-section a-spacing-none\">\r\n				<div class=\"a-section a-spacing-none a-spacing-top-small\">\r\n					<span>Yes, you can run the diffuser without the light.</span>&nbsp;<br />\r\n<span class=\"a-color-tertiary\" style=\"color:#767676 !important;\">By Amber Todd on March 27, 2017</span> \r\n				</div>\r\n				<div class=\"a-section a-spacing-none a-spacing-top-small\">\r\n					<span>It can be used with or without the light. There is a button for each.</span>&nbsp;<br />\r\n<span class=\"a-color-tertiary\" style=\"color:#767676 !impor