t-family:verdana, arial, helvetica, sans-serif;font-size:13px;background-color:#FFFFFF;\">\r\n		<div class=\"a-fixed-left-grid-inner\" style=\"padding:0px 0px 0px 100px;\">\r\n			<div class=\"a-fixed-left-grid-col a-col-left\" style=\"margin-left:-100px;\">\r\n				<span class=\"a-text-bold\" style=\"font-weight:700 !important;\">Question:</span>\r\n			</div>\r\n			<div class=\"a-fixed-left-grid-col a-col-right\">\r\n				Can this be plugged into an outlet?\r\n			</div>\r\n		</div>\r\n	</div>\r\n	<div class=\"a-fixed-left-grid a-spacing-base\" style=\"color:#111111;font-family:verdana, arial, helvetica, sans-serif;font-size:13px;background-color:#FFFFFF;\">\r\n		<div class=\"a-fixed-left-grid-inner\" style=\"padding:0px 0px 0px 100px;\">\r\n			<div class=\"a-fixed-left-grid-col a-col-left\" style=\"margin-left:-100px;\">\r\n				<span class=\"a-text-bold\" style=\"font-weight:700 !important;\">Answer:</span>\r\n			</div>\r\n			<div class=\"a-fixed-left-grid-col a-col-right\">\r\n				<span>Yep</span>&nbsp;<br />\r\n<span class=\"a-color-tertiary\" style=\"color:#767676 !important;\">By Amber Todd on May 16, 2017</span>\r\n			</div>\r\n		</div>\r\n	</div>\r\n	<div id=\"question-TxW2ZU19LPEAZ2\" class=\"a-fixed-left-grid a-spacing-small\" style=\"color:#111111;font-family:verdana, arial, helvetica, sans-serif;font-size:13px;background-color:#FFFFFF;\">\r\n		<div class=\"a-fixed-left-grid-inner\" style=\"padding:0px 0px 0px 100px;\">\r\n			<div class=\"a-fixed-left-grid-col a-col-left\" style=\"margin-left:-100px;\">\r\n				<span class=\"a-text-bold\" style=\"font-weight:700 !important;\">Question:</span>\r\n			</div>\r\n			<div class=\"a-fixed-left-grid-col a-col-right\">\r\n				Would this be useful just as a humidifier, without the oils?\r\n			</div>\r\n		</div>\r\n	</div>\r\n	<div class=\"a-fixed-left-grid a-spacing-base\" style=\"color:#111111;font-family:verdana, arial, helvetica, sans-serif;font-size:13px;background-color:#FFFFFF;\">\r\n		<div class=\"a-fixed-left-grid-inner\" style=\"padding:0px 0px 0px 100px;\">\r\n			<div class=\"a-fixed-left-grid-col a-col-left\" style=\"margin-left:-100px;\">\r\n				<span class=\"a-text-bold\" style=\"font-weight:700 !important;\">Answer:</span>\r\n			</div>\r\n			<div class=\"a-fixed-left-grid-col a-col-right\">\r\n				<span>Dear Kristin, thank you for your question. This item can be uesd as both humidifier and diffuser, if you don\'t put the oil into the water tenk, it can be used as a cool mist humidifier;and if you put the oil into the water tenk, it can be used as a diffuser.</span><br />\r\n<span class=\"a-color-tertiary\" style=\"color:#767676 !important;\">By Icicle Direct&nbsp;on December 29, 2016</span><span class=\"askInlineAnswers\" id=\"TxW2ZU19LPEAZ2\">\r\n				<div id=\"askInlineAnswersPage-TxW2ZU19LPEAZ2-1\" class=\"a-section a-spacing-none\">\r\n					<div class=\"a-section a-spacing-none a-spacing-top-small\">\r\n						<span>It does not hold alot of water, but it could be used without the oils to put a little moisture in the air.</span>&nbsp;<br />\r\n<span class=\"a-color-tertiary\" style=\"color:#767676 !important;\">By ThriftyTori on December 31, 2016</span>\r\n					</div>\r\n				</div>\r\n</span>\r\n			</div>\r\n		</div>\r\n	</div>\r\n</div>', '100ml Ultrasonic Essential Oil Diffusers | Portable Ultrasonic Aromatherapy Diffusers, Features Adjustable Mist Mode，7 Colors Light Changing, Waterless Auto Shut-off - Qedertek', 'best essential oils humidifiers,advanced aromatherapy essential oil diffusers,100ml ultrasonic essential oil diffusers,portable ultrasonic aromatherapy diffusers', 'If you are looking for best essential oils humidifiers，don\'t miss this 100ml ultrasonic essential oil diffusers，features adjustable mist mode, 7 Colors light changing and waterless auto shut-off multi-functions, perfect for bedrooms, bathrooms, massage ro', 'https://www.amazon.com/dp/B01JRTUNJW/', '', '0', '0.00', 'http://images.qedertek.com/5975aba890968', '{\"5975aba8b6343\":\"http:\\/\\/