d)&nbsp;<br />\r\nTotal Length: 3.2m/10.4ft&nbsp;<br />\r\nBulb Spacing: 15.24cm/6inch&nbsp;<br />\r\nLead Cable: 30.48cm/12inch&nbsp;<br />\r\n<br />\r\n<br />\r\n<span class=\"a-text-bold\" style=\"font-weight:700 !important;\">What\'s in the Box:</span>&nbsp;<br />\r\n1 x 20 LED Battery Rose Flower String Light\r\n							</p>\r\n						</div>\r\n					</div>\r\n				</div>\r\n			</div>\r\n			<div class=\"celwidget aplus-module 3p-module-d\" style=\"color:#111111;font-family:&quot;font-size:13px;background-color:#FFFFFF;\">\r\n				<div class=\"aplus-3p-fixed-width\">\r\n					<h3 class=\"a-spacing-mini\" style=\"margin-left:0px;font-size:17px;\">\r\n						Elegant Decorative Lights for wedding, bedroom, party, home, Lawn, patio, garden and more\r\n					</h3>\r\n					<div class=\"a-row\">\r\n						<div class=\"a-column a-span4 a-spacing-base\">\r\n							<img alt=\"\" src=\"https://m.media-amazon.com/images/S/aplus-seller-content-images-us-east-1/ATVPDKIKX0DER/A231TAZUOKNIOW/B01N4L9KEC/V9fLGh7Rt6._UX300_TTW__.jpg\" class=\"a-spacing-base\" /> \r\n						</div>\r\n						<div class=\"a-column a-span4 a-spacing-base\">\r\n							<img alt=\"\" src=\"https://m.media-amazon.com/images/S/aplus-seller-content-images-us-east-1/ATVPDKIKX0DER/A231TAZUOKNIOW/B01N4L9KEC/Gmy1Vo1tT0i2._UX300_TTW__.jpg\" class=\"a-spacing-base\" /> \r\n						</div>\r\n						<div class=\"a-column a-span4 a-spacing-base a-span-last\">\r\n							<img alt=\"\" src=\"https://m.media-amazon.com/images/S/aplus-seller-content-images-us-east-1/ATVPDKIKX0DER/A231TAZUOKNIOW/B01N4L9KEC/NDCi7Wg4TfG3._UX300_TTW__.jpg\" class=\"a-spacing-base\" /> \r\n						</div>\r\n					</div>\r\n				</div>\r\n			</div>\r\n<br />\r\n		</h3>\r\n	</div>\r\n</div>', '<ul class=\"a-unordered-list a-vertical a-spacing-none\" style=\"margin-left:18px;color:#949494;font-family:&quot;font-size:13px;background-color:#FFFFFF;\">\r\n	<li>\r\n		<span class=\"a-list-item\" style=\"color:#111111;\">Mini attractive rose appearance: Light up your night, bringing warm and romatic atmosphere, a perfect decoration for room, showcase, festivals especially Valentine\'s Day,Christmas,wedding, etc.</span> \r\n	</li>\r\n	<li>\r\n		<span class=\"a-list-item\" style=\"color:#111111;\">Timer Function: Auto ON/OFF, 6 hours \"ON\" and 18 hours \"OFF\"</span> \r\n	</li>\r\n	<li>\r\n		<span class=\"a-list-item\" style=\"color:#111111;\">Battery Operated: Powered by 3 AA batteries(not included), low power consumption, high brightness, low heat generate, safe and reliable(battery box is not waterproof, for indoor decorations only)</span> \r\n	</li>\r\n	<li>\r\n		<span class=\"a-list-item\" style=\"color:#111111;\">Easy Operation: With just one-button-design, super convenient to use.</span> \r\n	</li>\r\n	<li>\r\n		<span class=\"a-list-item\" style=\"color:#111111;\">Wide Applications: Would be lovely to draped over a bed, around a mirror, or hung on walls, windows, doors, floors, ceilings and anywhere you like.</span> \r\n	</li>\r\n</ul>', '', 'Battery Powered 20 Led Rose String Lights Multi Color with Timer | Color Changing Flower Valentine\'s Day Wedding Lights - Qedertek', 'light rose flower,rose fairy lights for room decoration,rose flower fairy string lights,batter powered string flowers, rose decorative lights with timer', 'Qedertek battery powered multi color 20 Led rose string lights, comes with auto timer, features color changing flower lighting, great for room, showcase, festivals decorating, especially perfect for Valentine\'s Day, Christmas, wedding party ornament or as', 'https://www.amazon.com/dp/B01N4L9KEC/', '', '0', '0.00', 'http://images.qedertek.com/5975b23742b22', '{\"5975b23772b7e\":\"http:\\/\\/images.qedertek.com\\/5975b23772b7e\",\"5975b23789618\":\"http:\\/\\/images.qedertek.com\\/5975b23789618\",\"5975b237b6c7f\":\"http:\\/\\/images.qedertek.com\\/5975b237b6c7f\",\"5975b237d7108\":\"http:\\/\\/images.qedertek.com\\/5975b237d7108\",\"5975b23804779\":\"http:\\/\\/images.qedertek.com\\/5975b23804779\"}'