\n				<span class=\"a-text-bold\" style=\"font-weight:700 !important;\">Question:</span>\r\n			</div>\r\n			<div class=\"a-fixed-left-grid-col a-col-right\" style=\"margin:0px;padding:0px;\">\r\n				does the built in battery needs changing?\r\n			</div>\r\n		</div>\r\n	</div>\r\n	<div class=\"a-fixed-left-grid a-spacing-base\" style=\"margin:0px;padding:0px;\">\r\n		<div class=\"a-fixed-left-grid-inner\" style=\"margin:0px;padding:0px 0px 0px 100px;\">\r\n			<div class=\"a-fixed-left-grid-col a-col-left\" style=\"margin:0px 0px 0px -100px;padding:0px;\">\r\n				<span class=\"a-text-bold\" style=\"font-weight:700 !important;\">Answer:</span>\r\n			</div>\r\n			<div class=\"a-fixed-left-grid-col a-col-right\" style=\"margin:0px;padding:0px;\">\r\n				<span>Just put the device on the sun for a day before swithing it.</span>&nbsp;<br />\r\n<span class=\"a-color-tertiary\" style=\"color:#767676 !important;\">By Ephim Shirman on November 16, 2016</span>\r\n			</div>\r\n		</div>\r\n	</div>\r\n	<div id=\"question-TxSS6Z6A2ONAAT\" class=\"a-fixed-left-grid a-spacing-small\" style=\"margin:0px;padding:0px;\">\r\n		<div class=\"a-fixed-left-grid-inner\" style=\"margin:0px;padding:0px 0px 0px 100px;\">\r\n			<div class=\"a-fixed-left-grid-col a-col-left\" style=\"margin:0px 0px 0px -100px;padding:0px;\">\r\n				<span class=\"a-text-bold\" style=\"font-weight:700 !important;\">Question:</span>\r\n			</div>\r\n			<div class=\"a-fixed-left-grid-col a-col-right\" style=\"margin:0px;padding:0px;\">\r\n				Anyone know how to change the mode? Claims to have two user selectable modes, no switch.\r\n			</div>\r\n		</div>\r\n	</div>\r\n	<div class=\"a-fixed-left-grid a-spacing-base\" style=\"margin:0px;padding:0px;\">\r\n		<div class=\"a-fixed-left-grid-inner\" style=\"margin:0px;padding:0px 0px 0px 100px;\">\r\n			<div class=\"a-fixed-left-grid-col a-col-left\" style=\"margin:0px 0px 0px -100px;padding:0px;\">\r\n				<span class=\"a-text-bold\" style=\"font-weight:700 !important;\">Answer:</span>\r\n			</div>\r\n			<div class=\"a-fixed-left-grid-col a-col-right\" style=\"margin:0px;padding:0px;\">\r\n				<span>Default mode is dim after dark, second mode is full bright when motion sensor is triggered. You can\'t switch modes.</span>&nbsp;<br />\r\n<span class=\"a-color-tertiary\" style=\"color:#767676 !important;\">By L A four20 on April 11, 2017</span>\r\n			</div>\r\n		</div>\r\n	</div>\r\n</div>', '16 LED Solar Motion Light | Energy Saving IP65 Waterproof Wall Lights - Qedertek', 'security light with sensor,outdoor security lights,motion sensor security lights,led solar motion lights', 'Search for outdoor security lights，you are just right here，our 16 LED ed solar motion lights, super bright, solid construction, waterproof design widely use for garden, patio, deck, yard, pathway and driveway', 'https://www.amazon.com/dp/B01M691AVO/', '', '0', '0.00', 'http://images.qedertek.com/59897ba2d5d0a', '{\"59897ba33aa80\":\"http:\\/\\/images.qedertek.com\\/59897ba33aa80\",\"59897ba34d660\":\"http:\\/\\/images.qedertek.com\\/59897ba34d660\",\"59897ba35fd71\":\"http:\\/\\/images.qedertek.com\\/59897ba35fd71\",\"59897ba36ec01\":\"http:\\/\\/images.qedertek.com\\/59897ba36ec01\",\"59897ba3867b3\":\"http:\\/\\/images.qedertek.com\\/59897ba3867b3\"}', '0', '0', '1', '0.00', '1', '1502182307', '1502182307', '', '0');
INSERT INTO `qe_product` VALUES ('96', '11', 'Solar Garden Lawn Landscape Lights 3 Lighting Modes', '<div class=\"celwidget aplus-module 3p-module-b\" style=\"color:#111111;font-family:&quot;font-size:13px;background-color:#FFFFFF;\">\r\n	<div class=\"aplus-3p-fixed-width\">\r\n		<h3 class=\"a-spacing-mini\" style=\"margin-left:0px;font-size:17px;\">\r\n			Qedertek Solor Lawn Light, Bring Your Garden Vitality and Bring Your Life Interesting<img alt=\"\" src=\"https://m.media-amazon.com/images/S/aplus-seller-content-images-us-east-1/ATVPDKIKX0DER/A231TAZUOKNIOW/B0728GCSX4/NTy5Ez6CTvq1._UX970_TTW__.jpg\" class=\"a-spacing-base\" />\r\n		</h3>\r\n		<p class=\"a-spacing-base\">\r\n			<br />\r\n<span class=\"a-text-bold\" style=\"font-weight:700 !important;\">Features<br />\r\n<br />\r\nSolar powered landscape light</span>, no utility energy cost, energy saving, high energy conservation rate.&nbsp;<br />\r\n<br />\r\n<span class=\"a-text-bold\" style=\"font-weight:700 !important;\">Lighting sensor technology</span>, these garden lights will&nbsp;<span class=\"a-text-bold\" style=\"font-weight:700 !important;\">auto on</span>&nbsp;at dusk and&nbsp;<span class=\"a-text-bold\" style=\"font-weight:700 !important;\">auto off&nbsp;</span>at dawn<br />\r\n<br />\r\n<span class=\"a-text-bold\" style=\"font-weight:700 !important;\">RGB yard light</span>,&nbsp;<span class=\"a-text-bold\" style=\"font-weight:700 !important;\">7 colors change</span>&nbsp;with&nbsp;<span class=\"a-text-bold\" style=\"font-weight:700 !important;\">3 lighting modes</span>&nbsp;bring you rainbow&nbsp;color lights, very interesting and beautiful, will also meet you curiosity<br />\r\n<br />\r\n<span class=\"a-text-bold\" style=\"font-weight:700 !important;\">Water-resistant</span>, IP55 waterproof rating, no worry to use in outdoor when&nbsp;raining.<br />\r\n<br />\r\n<span class=\"a-text-bold\" style=\"font-weight:700 !important;\">3 ways to use</span>, insert in the ground, hang up on trees or fence or in the&nbsp;strings included to decor patio, or sit them inverted to DIY different shape&nbsp;<br />\r\nlike heart, star etc.<br />\r\n<br />\r\nSuper easy operate,&nbsp;<span class=\"a-text-bold\" style=\"font-weight:700 !important;\">2 switches control</span>, one power switch and one&nbsp;function mode switch.<br />\r\n&nbsp;\r\n		</p>\r\n	</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div class=\"celwidget aplus-module 3p-module-c\" style=\"color:#111111;font-family:&quot;font-size:13px;background-color:#FFFFFF;\">\r\n	<div class=\"aplus-3p-fixed-width\">\r\n		<h3 class=\"a-spacing-mini\" style=\"margin-left:0px;font-size:17px;\">\r\n			Solar Powered Light, Charge Sunlight at Daytime and Light Up at Night\r\n		</h3>\r\n		<div class=\"a-row\">\r\n			<div class=\"a-column a-span4 a-spacing-base\">\r\n				<img alt=\"\" src=\"https://m.media-amazon.com/images/S/aplus-seller-content-images-us-east-1/ATVPDKIKX0DER/A231TAZUOKNIOW/B0728GCSX4/4Es3a1oOQ6x._UX300_TTW__.jpg\" />\r\n			</div>\r\n			<div class=\"a-column a-span8 a-spacing-base a-span-last\">\r\n				<p>\r\n					<br />\r\n<br />\r\n<span class=\"a-text-bold\" style=\"font-weight:700 !important;\">Specifications</span>\r\n				</p>\r\n				<ul class=\"a-unordered-list a-vertical\" style=\"color:#949494;\">\r\n					<li>\r\n						<span class=\"a-list-item\" style=\"color:#111111;\">LED Color: RGB&nbsp;</span>\r\n					</li>\r\n					<li>\r\n						<span class=\"a-list-item\" style=\"color:#111111;\">Setting: Indoor/Outdoor&nbsp;</span>\r\n					</li>\r\n					<li>\r\n						<span class=\"a-list-item\" style=\"color:#111111;\">Solar Panel: 2V/30mA&nbsp;</span>\r\n					</li>\r\n					<li>\r\n						<span class=\"a-list-item\" style=\"color:#111111;\">Battery Type: 3*AA 1.2V&nbsp;200mAH Nickel-Cadmium Battery&nbsp;</span>\r\n					</li>\r\n					<li>\r\n						<span class=\"a-list-item\" style=\"color:#111111;\">Light Source: LED&nbsp;</span>\r\n					</li>\r\n					<li>\r\n						<span class=\"a-list-item\" style=\"color:#111111;\">Switch: ON/OFF, MODE&nb